{"article":[{"title":"The Hawkins","musik":"Hard rock","place":"Arboga","text":"THE HAWKINS is a 4-piece Rock'n'Roll band from Sweden. \r\n\r\nOur music goes from a blues-based, Deep Purple-like rock to a more punk-influenced history and on to an AC\/DC rocking with a sustained goal to always swing sharply!\r\n\r\nWe started The Hawkins on 1st of March 2013 and since that date, several things have happend. We have released three EP's; \"Part I: The Circus\", \"Part II: The Puppet Show\" and \"Guantanamo Bassline\". Beyond that we have played many shows in different places and venues. \r\nThe highlight for us so far was when we entered the stage at Sweden Rock Festival on the 7th of June 2014. \r\n\r\nRight now, in the summer of 2015, we have just started recording new music for an upcoming release. We are super thrilled about this release, so stay tuned!\r\n\r\n\r\nIn order to listen to our music and watch our videos, please visit one of these websites:\r\n\r\nSpotify:\r\nhttp:\/\/open.spotify.com\/album\/45BqLv9Zh6Ndasfu5zeD6Y\r\n\r\nYouTube:\r\nhttp:\/\/www.youtube.com\/user\/HawkinsTheBand\r\n\r\nTwitter:\r\nhttp:\/\/twitter.com\/thehawkinsband\r\n\r\nInstagram:\r\nhttp:\/\/instagram.com\/thehawkinsband\r\n\r\niTunes:\r\nhttps:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/artist\/the-hawkins\/id674326102\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/d5c73f2b-7135-4ba2-b64b-fdb774b0e58e_media_02 Guantanamo Bassline.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/469c231f-b141-45c2-805e-c7af21332f64_media_THE_HAWKINS_PRESSBILD.png.jpg"},{"title":"State of Grace","musik":"Pop","place":"Heby","text":"Melodic pop rock act from Heby, Sweden. Painting their music colorful with synthesizers and their well recognized energetic live performances. Tours have went through Sweden, Germany, U.S. and Canada. Their music have been used in international commercial campaigns for coca cola and their latest release featuring Like Swimming went up as number one on iTunes top 100 chart the first day. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c12dbce6-7c60-451c-ba4e-510f9c732af1_media_09 - State of Grace - Chemical (1) super compressed.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/41b960bc-a07c-48d8-9e5f-54a5dc7fe2bb_media_Kopia av Press 1 - Photo- Sebastian Niemi-Carlsson.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Jimmy Nordin","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"G\u00e4vle","text":"Jimmy Nordin Singer Songwriter from G\u00e4vle http:\/\/www.jimmynordin.se\r\nJimmy Nordin sl\u00e4ppte 2014 sin tredje skiva (Living on earth is not easy) och den resulterade i mycket fina recentioner i tidningarna. Under 2015 spelar Jimmy p\u00e5 flera festivaler runt om i sverig och m\u00e5nga ser likheter med Neil Young pga den nasala ljusa r\u00f6sten som kommer direkt fr\u00e5n sj\u00e4len. Det \u00e4r l\u00e5tar skrivna fr\u00e5n verkligheten som ber\u00f6r. Lyssna p\u00e5 Spotify eller Jimmys hemsida.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/848e5eba-10ea-46fe-aad6-6cff1b6173ef_media_05 Was I To Wasted Again.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/1e3a2674-ad99-4e19-9e63-1046530b823a_media_pressfotonr3pix1500.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"FLAT FOOT","musik":"Surfrock","place":"FALUN","text":"This is Cactus Rock!\r\nWith 5 album releases, several tours around europe and China, radio plays and fans all over the world- \r\nFlat Foot gives you this surf sounding cactus rock with a tase of both Tarrantino and Morricone!","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/462f363d-a89b-4383-b923-0ad35b5c86d5_media_Johnny Mac.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/8a2c86c4-826d-4b0e-9393-aaf967cc31b7_media_FlatFoot_Press14_FotografHel\u00e9ne_logga_liggande (2188 x 1458).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Blue Ruin","musik":"Rock","place":"Stockholm","text":"The Blue Ruin was founded by Jens and Sundus, with the aim of creating a meltdown of Goth, Psychedelia, Synth and Blues. The 3 bands members all had different roots: Alternative Voodoo-Rock was born.\r\n\r\nIn January 2013 The Blue Ruin signed with Bad Taste Records and was nominated as best new band at the Manifest Awards.\r\nIn the spring 2013 the band released their debut album The New Disorder on vinyl and cassette.\r\n\r\n\"This is an album that contains music that nobody in the world ever listened to before. One thing that makes both the band and the album so interesting is their way to dare to break new ground. Creating an almost completely own style of music.\"\r\nJonas L\u00f6\u00f6w (Rockbladet)\r\n\r\nThe band has had several gigs in Stockholm and has released 8 videos, the latest video \"Get On\" released in January 2015. In september 2014 the video Television Borderline was featured by the Promo Bay witch made the views explode on YouTube.\r\n\r\nIn January 2013 The Blue Ruin signed with Bad Taste Records and was nominated as best new band at the Manifest Awards.\r\nIn the spring 2013 the band released their debut album The New Disorder on vinyl and cassette.\r\nIn the spring of 2015, The Blue Ruin released their second album, Holy Moly Matrimony.\r\n\r\n\"Hard enough for the girls - sweet enough for the boys\"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e1ebb882-55b2-47e5-a509-79e696929152_media_The Blue Ruin - GET ON .mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/3ac80e02-a1d0-43c0-b85c-f68b300e09e8_media_The Blue Ruin lowres.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Kambodsja","musik":"Hardcore","place":"Drammen","text":"Kambodsja from Drammen is one of the most respected underground hardcore bands in Norway. With it\u00b4s raw and genre-breaking music, and explosive live shows, Kambodsja has become a favorite among critics and fans in Norway as well as Europe. The band has released three albums to rave reviews, and shared stage with bands like Satyricon, No Means No, Rumble In Rhodos, Made Out Of Babies etc.\r\n\r\nThis fall Kambodsja is releasing their most ambitious album so far. Produced, mixed and mastered by three of the most exciting names in Norway and USA. Packed with surprising hooks, blasting riffs and melodic madness. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/8422923f-8670-4e8c-b0a9-fe667820e682_media_03 Baby Knock_em Dead.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/7bf266c6-8efb-47eb-90c1-d5c9c6164a7d_media_kollasje2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Deborah Henriksson","musik":"Folk","place":"Vasteras","text":"Haunting voice and Soundscapes:\r\nSWEDEN BASED, AMERICAN BORN CELTIC\/FOLK SINGER and SONGWRITER DEBORAH HENRIKSSON presents a mix of styles within the spectrum of Celtic, folk, a hint of jazz and country.  She released her fourth album, Traces, in June 2014 and is currently recording songs for a fifth, to be released in the fall. \r\nShe has appeared in festivals in Dublin, Florida, Oregon, and numerous venues in Sweden.\r\nYou can hear Deborah on terrestrial and internet radio in Europe, the U.S., Canada, and Australia.\r\nDeborah\u2019s focus when performing is touching the listener, and making the audience feel at home in the musical stories she tells. Swedish Rootsy Magazine described it this way:  \u201c\u2026Deborah Henriksson sings with understatement, for the force of her voice is in the artistic expression, not in vocal strength.  Her diction is distinct with simple beauty.  She uses her voice like an instrument which is both a loyal subordinate to the songs but which also lifts them to heavenly heights in a clear eloquence of purity, beauty and exquisite expressiveness...\u201d  \r\nCharlie Elland of folkwords.com writes of TRACES:\u201d With strong Celtic overtones to music and voice, there\u2019s an ethereal feel that moves the songs between fragile and vulnerable towards elemental and hopeful. The more you listen to Deborah\u2019s voice the more you find yourself laying aside the weight of the day and slipping under a magical spell that quite simply makes everything better. From \u2018Trains\u2019 to \u2018Traces\u2019 through \u2018Evening Star\u2019 to \u2018Eveline\u2019 you\u2019re moving ever further into places that weave music and voice into a potion that echoes the restoring \u2018draught of forgetfulness\u2019 from Celtic myth. Listen to this and forget \u2026 everything\u201d\r\nwww.deborahhenriksson.com\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/556fc09e-a55d-464a-bbd8-96b815fe1fc2_media_Calling.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/24e98a92-1ed0-4c13-b747-8a1c9a3926cc_media_at village.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"GreenCity","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"Bremerhaven\/Germany","text":"Atmospheric, infectious, timeless:\r\n\r\nWith catchy melodies, emotional lyrics and progressive sounds GreenCity creates a matchless atmosphere among their listeners that is shaped by the creativeness of the five\r\ndedicated musicians from Bremerhaven, Germany. At their concerts the talented indie-\r\nartists are always varying and close to the audience. They don't only surprise with original\r\narrangements and memorable timbres, their live-show with it's visual elements makes sure\r\nthat a GreenCity concert will not be forgotten.\r\nTheir recently released debut-album \u201cLying in Wait\u201d is a mix of moody ballads and rocking\r\npop-songs that live through a combination of harmonic keyboard-sounds and inventive guitar-riffs. As well as on the album they don't shun to add in some calmer instrumentals to live-performances to enhance the listening experience.\r\n\r\nAll their fans agree: GreenCity are dynamic, moving and innovative.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/7c70729a-c58d-4256-8d3d-05b413134597_media_02 Barricade.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5889e47e-956e-4c49-89e4-74b38d5a8c47_media_GreenCity14_Bandfoto.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Nellie Lovett","musik":"Americana","place":"Gothenburg","text":"We want to invite you to a very special performance by the band Nellie Lovett. Since their first record, produced by Henryk Lipp in Gothenburg 2013, they\u2019re now ready to show a full concept of what a band can be- Beautiful, humoristic, magic, dark, intense, and bold. In front you will see the character of Nellie Lovett come to life in Sofia Hindhammar, with her impressive voice range and theatrical stage presence. Don\u2019t miss this wonderful mixture of americana, jazz, pop, and musical! \r\n\r\nTo follow Nellie Lovett and learn more, visit: https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nellielovettband\r\nor find us at Spotify, iTunes, Wimp, Youtube.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/73902fa7-be10-4895-9ad2-afefb6225487_media_Sign Here-RR1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/f181dff9-f987-44e9-96e4-1040c6238396_media_nl_1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Colossus","musik":"Metal","place":"Sthlm","text":"Stockholmska sludge-trion Colossus levererar ett meckigt, medryckande sv\u00e4ng med lika delar hj\u00e4rta som hj\u00e4rna. Med sin egensinnigt lekfulla och fullkomligt kompromissl\u00f6sa musik har gruppen lyckats utstaka sin egen personliga v\u00e4g i det sn\u00e5riga tr\u00e4sket av subgenrer i den tyngre h\u00e5rdrockens dom\u00e4ner och sn\u00e4rjt s\u00e5v\u00e4l kritiker som underjorden till sig.\r\n\r\nBandet har med sitt senaste sl\u00e4pp \"The Breathing World\" (2015 Perennity) \u00f6vertr\u00e4ffat sig sj\u00e4lva med ett komplext och mullrande tema-album som r\u00f6nt hyllningar v\u00e4rlden \u00f6ver och fick Mastodon att handplocka gruppen som f\u00f6rband till senaste Sverigebes\u00f6ket.\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/a8b2ceab-801b-444e-ac3f-82bf92d1a307_media_02- Darkling Root 161114 (1).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/26518c8c-d757-4231-9b67-4809567218e6_media_colossus_the-breathing-world_front_hi-res.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Billy Momo","musik":"Americana","place":"Stockholm","text":"\" Swedish music has found its proper place in my ears again thanks to Billy Momo..\" Knox Road\r\n\r\nWith a sync placement in the trailer for successful TV-series \"Better Call Saul\" (track Wishing Ain't No Sin\") and the same single aiplayed both in the US and in Sweden, things are really starting to happen for Billy Momo.  \r\n\r\nLatest album \"Drunktalk\" was released February 2015. The tight-knit nature of the band is obvious on the record. The album envelops the listener into their bizarre and intriguing world completely, telling the tales of relationships, late drunken nights, and the changes in people\u2019s lives.\r\nThe fifteen tracks exhibit vastly different personas of the band, showcasing an album that is dark, humorous, and at times profound- from the elegant, graceful, orchestral movements of first release \u2018I\u2019ve Got You\u2019, to the debauched title track \u2018Drunktalk\u2019, the ensemble retains a charm throughout that led Absolute Noise to deem the material \u2018the kind of music Beck could have done at the beginning of his career.\u2019\r\n\r\n\"Drunktalk\" is released through Hype Music UK. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/7669ac5c-cfb5-4b2f-83c9-43194178b877_media_Wishing Ain_t No Sin.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/6f3e5449-5c7b-42b8-8d29-8f4726a7de9d_media_Billy_Momo_logotype.png.jpg"},{"title":"M-Rock the band","musik":"Funk","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Emrik M-ROCK Larsson, The king of FUNK from Sweden.\r\n Former singer and bandleader of the powerhouse funk hip-hop band Stonefunkers. After ten years he\u2019s back with a fresh new album \u201cPhunk Observatory\u201d dedicated to soul, funk, boogie and hip-hop. A musical journey from the early seventies up to the present.\r\nM-ROCK the band consists of a five piece band with added\r\npercussion player, horns and rapper to create one hell of a party.\r\nGet ready for the new funk of 2015. \u2028\r\n\r\nFunklegenden fr\u00e5n Stonefunkers: Emrik M-ROCK  Larsson \u00e4r \u00e4ntligen tillbaka p\u00e5 livescenen.  Nya albumet Phunk Observatory \u00e4r fyllt av soul, funk, disco och hip-hop. Skivan \u00e4r helt enkelt den b\u00e4sta funkplatta som kommit sen Stonefunkers dagar. Detta \u00e4r musik som kn\u00e4cker, sv\u00e4nger och ger 100% livsgl\u00e4dje. Live maxar M-Rock the band p\u00e5 \u00e4nnu mer och utlovar minst 90 minutes of pure funk!\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c6fcd627-2db8-4271-8236-0f259fd73a5b_media_M-Rock - Method-to-the-madness_(Opolopo RMX)_Radio.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/6f70122d-98fb-4e9c-b959-a2607082a8a3_media_M-Rock Press Stare Web Photo Christer \u00c5kerlund.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Samuel Gajicki","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Stockholm","text":"Write a short presentation of your band here.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/b20f4d08-9a26-4e3f-a3e4-fa11523b57a6_media_Samuel Gajicki - Free Man.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0504158e-44de-444d-97cd-11bb03ea0c08_media_Samuel Gajicki.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Vindstyrka12","musik":"Rock","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Vissa s\u00e4ger att det p\u00e5minner om Th\u00e5str\u00f6m, andra Ulf Lundell och tidiga Gyllene Tider. S\u00e5ngaren och l\u00e5tskrivaren Jon Lyster s\u00e4ger att det inte finns n\u00e5gra tydliga influenser g\u00e4llande hur Vindstyrka 12 ska l\u00e5ta. Det blir vad det blir och den \u00e4nda tr\u00e5d som finns \u00e4r att texterna handlar om det som h\u00e4nder i livet runtomkring b\u00e5de dig och mig.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/d6fe030c-6677-4761-9241-1a000879f859_media_Flimrande Hja\u0308rtan.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/bb2e8cd3-eda2-4d03-bbfd-62476cacaea2_media_165472_10152348668362724_2638348035101328292_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Joe Fiddle","musik":"Folk","place":"Ume\u00e5","text":"After spending time around the world with no specific goals or ambitions, Swedish singer\/songwriter Joe Nystr\u00f6m was encouraged to start writing music of his own. It was during a roadtrip in the US 2013, Joe performed at a local bonfire in San Diego. A few months later he wrote his first song \u201cDandelions on the Street\u201d which was reviewed in the US by a journalist he met at the bonfire, comparing him with Bob Dylan's storytelling folk style. \r\n\r\nHe kept on writing music, inspired by his travels around the world and from spending time out in the wild in his hometown. Most of his lyrics are autobiographic and he describes the process of carving lyrics as \u201creally messy and different from every time\".\r\n\r\nCurrently he's working on new material for his first album.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/f45aa75a-5d10-4e1f-92ea-9399866dddc5_media_Where I'll Spend My Years.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/31bb42aa-d35a-4009-b9a8-5f045d4f73de_media_coversuper.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Pingvinorkestern","musik":"Progressive rock","place":"Malm\u00f6","text":"Pingvinorkestern fr\u00e5n Malm\u00f6 kan sin progressiva rockhistoria, men h\u00e5ller den p\u00e5 arml\u00e4ngds avst\u00e5nd. Tydlig inspiration har h\u00e4mtats fr\u00e5n genrens stora, men h\u00e4r finns \u00e4ven ett start inslag av svenskt klingande pastorala teman i musiken. Kvintetten besitter dessutom en musikalisk lekfullhet, med lika oheliga som underfundiga inslag av cirkus- och kabaretmusik, chanson, popballader, psykadelia och jazz.\r\n\r\n\"N\u00e4r det kommer till kritan \u00e4r det hur bandet f\u00f6rvaltar det progressiva arvet, deras egen musikalitet, originalitet och fantasifullhet - de inspirerade kompositionerna - som g\u00f6r det st\u00f6rsta intrycket.\" (Lars Fahlin\/tidskriften Lira 2014)\r\n\r\nBandets instrumentering best\u00e5r - ut\u00f6ver traditionell bands\u00e4ttning - \u00e4ven av bland annat vibrafon, fiol, musiks\u00e5g, mandolin, xylofon, melodika, fl\u00f6jter, tuta...\r\n\r\nLyssna p\u00e5 Spotify och gilla g\u00e4rna bandet p\u00e5 deras Facebooksida.\r\n\r\n2014 debuterade Pingvinorkestern med albumet Push, som bjuder p\u00e5 tolv egenkomponerade sp\u00e5r. Plattan har f\u00e5tt en rad lysande recensioner i internationell press och f\u00e5tt upprepade radiospelningar.\r\n\r\nN\u00e5gra recensionscitat: \r\n\r\n\u201d\u2026en av de mest sp\u00e4nnande och h\u00f6rv\u00e4rda skivor jag har snubblat \u00f6ver 2014\u201d.\r\nDaniel Reichberg\/Artrock\r\n\r\n\u201cDefinitely one of the most surprising and best albums of the year!\u201d\r\nProgisaliveandwell\r\n\r\n\u201cOne of the best Prog albums of 2014!\u201d\r\nDutch Progressive Rock Page.net\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/38079cfd-f2db-42f2-b378-43cf1dfe695d_media_Fru Elses Loppcirkus.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/fbac3515-9e56-4164-86a6-6ddfb0ea7904_media_Klaffbron m Push.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Saturday's Heroes","musik":"Punk","place":"Finsp\u00e5ng","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/437a7469-1811-474e-a706-4789831c1b2d_media_Keep Marching On.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/ec285f5a-18f7-4534-aeeb-16e89a2e443d_media_10828171_10153500020338056_3034510409813287107_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Plastic Pals","musik":"Americana","place":"Stockholm","text":"\u201dTighter than Willy Deville\u00b4s crocodile boots.\u201d\r\n(Anders Tapola, Swedish paper Sm\u00e5landsposten)\r\n\r\nMagic melodies with a dark edge. Manna from guitar heaven for friends and fans of The Long Ryders, The Dream Syndicate, Flamin\u00b4 Groovies, The Velvets and Television.\r\n\r\nStockholm\u00b4s twin guitar slingers The Plastic Pals - who\u00b4ve been coind \"Stockholm\u00b4s bes New York rock band\" - have released two albums, one EP plus the latest release the vinyl single Riding with Elvis (with a cover of Jackson 5\u00b4s I want you back as the b-side) - Riding with Elvis previously released on Elvis Presley\u00b4s 80th birthday 8 January 2015 on New York label World Wide Vibe Records.\r\n\r\nThe band have toured in the UK and New York\/New Jersey and have done tours in Sweden with the Green on Red legendaries Chris Cacavas and Dan Stuart (separate tours, that is). They have opened for The Dream Syndicate, The Fleshtones (in Copenhagen), The New Christs (in Halden, Norway), Chuck Prophet, The Nomads (in Borl\u00e4nge, Sweden) and for Steve Wynn & The Miracle 3. In 2008 The Plastic Pals were ex The Long Ryders Sid Griffin\u00b4s backing band playing a Long Ryders set at a paisley underground celebration gig in London.\r\n\r\nCurrently The Plastic Pals are working on a new album with the title Psychic Reader - slated for release in 2016.\r\n\r\nMore info:\r\nhttp:\/\/www.theplasticpals.se\r\nhttp:\/\/www.soundcloud.com\/theplasticpals\r\nhttps:\/\/www.facebook.com\/theplasticpals\r\nhttp:\/\/www.twitter.com\/theplasticpals\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/47b0d9c8-d0a2-4437-b9fa-057279855ae2_media_The Plastic Pals_Riding with Elvis.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/98ff0e67-5228-4255-929f-52749a340478_media_the plastic pals_sidewalk cafe_nyc_feb 15.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Esse Quam Videri","musik":"Folk","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Nu sl\u00e4pper EQV sitt debutalbum One way up Esse Quam Videri fr\u00e5n \u00d6rebro har spelat tillsammans i tre \u00e5r, nu sl\u00e4pps deras \r\ndebutalbum som best\u00e5r av 13 nyskrivna l\u00e5tar inspelade i bandmedlemmarnas vardagsrum. \r\nI utvecklandet av det egna soundet har musikerna inte varit r\u00e4dda f\u00f6r att ta ut sv\u00e4ngarna ordentligt. \r\nI EQV\u2019s musik blandas traditionell folkrock med lekfulla, improvisatoriska partier som doftar 60-tal. Den trest\u00e4mmiga s\u00e5ngen ger \r\nl\u00e5tarna rymd och en karakt\u00e4ristisk klang. Titelsp\u00e5ret: One way up inleder skivan med en lite galen rivstart. \r\n\r\nDet h\u00e4r albumet har f\u00e5tt v\u00e4xa fram under l\u00e5ng tid. L\u00e5tarna har f\u00e5tt mogna i replokalen och sedan st\u00f6tts och \r\nbl\u00f6tts ytterligare under inspelningen. Resultatet \u00e4r en genomarbetad och genomt\u00e4nkt skiva d\u00e4r \r\nbandmedlemmarnas engagemang \u00e5terspeglas i musiken.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/b1a55b2a-9e98-439a-bf32-8afc502e16c9_media_See Napoli Or Die - Esse Quam Videri.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/b98c3e87-64d7-4a07-bed8-b0fab1f4be24_media_0020-9505-Fotograf-Elin-Atterstig.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Bring The Mourning On","musik":"Americana","place":"Malm\u00f6","text":"\u00c4r inte biografier kanske det tr\u00e5kigaste som finns? Vi skulle kunna ber\u00e4tta om hur vi tr\u00e4ffades n\u00e4r vi var barn och hur vi h\u00e4ngt ihop sedan dess, eller hur vi tr\u00e4ffades under ett v\u00e4rdetransportr\u00e5n och skapade bandet under v\u00e5r f\u00e4ngelsetid men inget av det hade p\u00e5 n\u00e5got s\u00e4tt varit sant. Vi gillar det vi g\u00f6r och l\u00e5ter, ist\u00e4llet f\u00f6r hur vi tr\u00e4ffades, v\u00e5r musik tala f\u00f6r oss. Men om ni \u00e4nd\u00e5 vill veta n\u00e5got om oss s\u00e5 har vi beskrivit oss sj\u00e4lva p\u00e5 f\u00f6ljande s\u00e4tt:\r\n\r\nWhen four people from the dark, cold and barren Sweden come together to create, things become just that. With a strong focus to, with every note and every word, summon a long lasting feeling that leaves the listener grasping for air but still wanting more as the band delivers a wide spectrum of dark and lonesome music.\r\n\r\nOn one hand melancholy Rhodes Piano, a delayed bow on a bass, a firm accordion and a minimalistic mandolin.\r\nOn the other hand a droning bass, quick fingerpicking, a busy piano that fills the room and drums with every beat in its place, no more, no less. All rests comfortably under a warm blanket of harmonies.\r\n\r\nhttp:\/\/bringthemourningon.bandcamp.com","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/bf35abd0-9322-409f-8398-64f4befe19d1_media_Trust Me.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/61abd9cf-8ff8-4cc9-bc45-e602ec926b48_media_btmo_16heavycrop_small.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Light Screamer","musik":"Punk","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"This marks the fifth year in a row for Light Screamer at Live at Heart. Since making their live debut at Live at Heart 2011, the quartet has released one album, one EP, and just recently, one single. They've been to Austin, Texas two years in a row and played at the SXSW festival and has gotten quite a reputation for their live shows.\r\n\r\n\"An overwhelming and bordering on unpleasant experience. Perfect.\" (Totally \u00d6rebro)\r\n\r\nFor more information, visit: www.lightscreamer.net","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/791e043c-1f91-4ae2-abad-d336b0a5cb63_media_BFJ.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/1ddf3e7d-f6de-4ba8-af7c-d35a19a758a8_media__BHW6553.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"David Blair","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Berlin","text":"David Blair, is best known for his relentless smile, his stories and his energetic freestyle moves.  Recently featured on the national German TV show ZDF Morgen Magazin, he cracked the top 100 in radio charts in Germany with 'Alone Together' in 2014, has been support for the world famous band Nickelback, was a semi-finalist in Canada's Got Talent, holds 3 semi-finalist awards for the USA Billboard songwriting contest amongst others, and has played over 500 shows all over the world!\r\n\r\n\u201cFantastic! Brilliant!\u201d Hit Songwriter-Stephan Moccio (Celine Dion, Miley Cyrus, The Weeknd)\r\n\"Absolutely contagious!\" Famed Opera Star - Measha Brueggergosman\r\n\u201cHis eclectic collection of acoustic-pop songs provide an unforgettable soundtrack for any occasion.\" - Performing Songwriter Magazine, USA\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/004044c5-71a9-4828-bbeb-565fa12de582_media_David Blair - Stay In Touch - 08 Stronger Higher Faster.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/49437679-c015-407a-b987-1c2f8e3c679f_media_IMG_2474.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Bongo Club","musik":"Rock","place":"Bor\u00e5s","text":"This is not rocket science, this is rock\u2019n\u2019roll. It\u2019s about music. It\u2019s about being young and having a job you hate. It\u2019s about keeping a straight face during the working week just to let it all go on Saturday night. It\u2019s about having dreams of going somewhere with your tunes. It\u2019s about having that talent. It\u2019s about doing it. It's nothing complicated. The Bongo Club don\u2019t need computers, backtracks or DJ\u2019s to deliver hit songs and a wild performance. These youngsters just knows how to write tunes with great hooks, deadly melodies and a really tight beat. But they don\u2019t know how to save any energy what so ever when on a stage.\r\n\r\nTheir debut album \u201dBe Careful Not To Stare\u201d was released in March and now the band got the product to take the next level, to back it all up. It\u2019s indie rock and it\u2019s about music. It\u2019s about being young and it\u2019s about the weekend. It\u2019s nothing complicated.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c19f1c47-6e10-49bf-b3c0-c76ecf4ab3da_media_The Hush Hush Song.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Christoffer Skoug","musik":"Americana","place":"Stockholm","text":"Christoffer Skoug is a bluesy singer\/songwriter with a catchy and earthy sound. He has played the guitar and sung all his life and began writing songs when he was 15 years old. Christoffer released his debut album Have Guitar. Will Travel. 2011 at Universal Music Sweden and are currently working on his second album. Christoffer has also written music for two children's shows and a musical theater and has worked as a musical artist and dancer in several musicals in Stockholm, including Grease, West Side Story and The Producers. Besides being a songwriter, singer and dancer Christoffer is also a great guitarist and his music is often based on a guitar groove that creates a stable foundation for the song to rest on. The lyrics are personal and unadorned and the songs are often inspired by his own experiences. His musical influences include Dave Matthews, Ray LaMontagne, John Mayer and Tommy Emmanuel.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/52b3a7f1-359c-451a-b136-7ac1b55946bf_media_I need to cry_Christoffer Skoug.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a81f43e7-6f95-4704-a099-f1445f59e871_media_Christoffer_Skoug.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"DSH5","musik":"Folk","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"\u201dDet melodiska dragspelet, popvisorna som pendlar mellan furi\u00f6st tempo och vemodiga valsmelodier och de mer \u00e4n underh\u00e5llande texterna om alkohol, mycken saknad och lite k\u00e4rlek har ju h\u00e4mtat sina influenser i samma jord som Per Persson. Men jag tyckte mig ocks\u00e5 h\u00f6ra en \u00e4n mer adrenalinstinn, rockbaserad och r\u00f6jig livemusik som jag ig\u00e5r kv\u00e4ll hade v\u00e4ldigt sv\u00e5rt att v\u00e4rja mig emot.\u201d\r\n\r\nFr\u00e5n recension av H\u00e5kan Pettersson, 29 december 2013","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/1428ca25-8508-4711-83db-1088e678c082_media_01-Hett Blod.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5d587859-1b12-4c75-8649-e7550e2679f1_media_dsh5-bandbild-st\u00e5ende-72dpi.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Northern Indians","musik":"Americana","place":"Pite\u00e5","text":"Northern Indians bildades 2013 som ett sidoprojekt till ett annat band. N\u00e4r det andra bandet lades ner best\u00e4mde sig Josef Eriksson och John Andersson att satsat helhj\u00e4rtat p\u00e5 Northern.  \r\nI januari 2015 klev duon in i studion tillsammans med medproducenten och kompisen Jonas Eriksson och spelade in sitt debutalbum \"The Great Escape\" p\u00e5 nio dagar. En inspelning som st\u00e4mmer v\u00e4l \u00f6vers med bandets inst\u00e4llning till hur musik ska framf\u00f6ras. Okonstlat, \u00e4rligt och med l\u00e5tarna i fokus. Albumet sl\u00e4pptes 27 maj p\u00e5 labeln Rootsy.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/706bfd31-f90d-42d1-8bd5-e74b2bb3714b_media_02. On A Losing Streak.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/899b4101-73b9-4c24-b01a-aaeb61752c17_media_CD framsida.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Ad\u00e9e","musik":"Hiphop","place":"\u00d6land","text":"Ad\u00e9e is a Swedish artist and producer that stands with her feet steady on the ground, mixing soul with hip-hop in a modern and creative way. Her unique voice shines through in all her creations, leaving an unforgettable imprint on the listeners musical consciousness.\r\n\r\nThe last years have been successful for Ad\u00e9e and have given her a well known presens on the Swedish urban music scene. The release of the EP \u2019One Step Closer\u2019 in 2013 took her on the first US tour, got her honorable live performances i.e for the Swedish Royal Family and a lots of touring in Sweden.\r\n\r\nIn spring 2014 Ad\u00e9e released \u2019Woman\u2019 \u2013 the official anthem song for the worlds largest political conference on gender equality, and she performed the song live at Malm\u00f6 Arena and on national TV4. In May 2014 Ad\u00e9e released her second EP \u2019Honesty\u2019 and in September 2014 she signed with Musichelp Publishing. Ad\u00e9e continued to tour intensively during 2014, i.e Live at Heart, Rookiefestivalen and Kalmar Stadsfest where she opened for Agnes.\r\n\r\nAd\u00e9e have got a lot of attention in media, for example Scandinavian Soul, Kingsize Magazine, DN, Musikindustrin and N\u00f6jesguiden, TV4 & SVT Svergie!\r\n\r\nDuring 2015 Ad\u00e9e is working on the debut album to be released spring 2016. The first single \u2018World On Fire\u2019 was released in May by Scandinaviansoul.com. Ad\u00e9e has also toured a lot 2015, with showcases at Canadian Music Week and New Skool Rules, Netherlands and a lot of festival shows in Sweden. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/bda11357-a6b7-4cce-abed-d7cc0ac509fb_media_Woman.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/6d0f0953-30ba-40ec-968b-a8c3aff2386c_media_5DSC_5459.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Grand Trunk Travellers","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Uppsala","text":"Short version:\r\nThe musical collective, Grand Trunk Travellers, fronted by Karl-Johan Jonsson, offers evocative vintage singer\/songwriter-rock.\r\nThey have traveled around in Scandinavia and the Baltic states with their grand harmonium-organ, glockenspiel, acoustic guitars and a bunch of other instruments.\r\nThe band has 2 sold-out EPs, and their own premium coffee brand.\r\n\r\n\r\nLonger version:\r\n\r\nThe musical collective, Grand Trunk Travellers, fronted by Karl-Johan Jonsson, offers evocative vintage singer\/songwriter-rock.\r\n\r\nThe band has performed on everything from foreigner festival stages to local cafes, from private weddings to tv-shows, from someone\u2019s living-room to a staircase in Riga.\r\n\r\nThe ability to perform as full band with drums, electric guitars, and bass, or all acoustic sets with acoustic guitar, floor tom and special instruments as harmonium and glockenspiel, or a full live experience with all combined, and still sound like the same band, is probably one thing that make Grand Trunk Travellers unique.\r\n\r\nKarl-Johan is able to write songs that people love and feel addicted to. Songs that easily get stuck in people\u2019s heads for a long time. His significant voice is singing thoughtful lyrics with feeling and warmth.\r\n\r\nBoth the studio and the stage are creative environments for the band, who are constantly exploring new instruments, or new ways to use them. This band oozes creativity in its simplicity. However, they are careful not to deviate to much from their sound.\r\n\r\nMusically, the songs has been described as a blend of vintage rock, singer\/songwriter and\u2026 magical!\r\n\r\nThe band has been traveling around in Scandinavia and The Baltic States, and has performed at the historic rock club Sticky Fingers in Gothenburg, at Frizon Festival, HiJazz in their hometown Uppsala, and other clubs and cafes. They have also both performed at local tv-\/radio-shows, and contributed with a live broadcasted gig and interview at Musikhj\u00e4lpen in 2013.\r\n\r\nIn 2015, the band also launched their own premium coffee blend, in cooperation with Alings\u00e5s Kafferosteri. Since people prefer to stream the music, Grand Trunk Travellers offered the listeners another cosy experience along with the music. Coffee seemed to match the music well, and people seemed to like it a lot.\r\n\r\nNew songs are written and more music is about to be recorded. Meanwhile Karl-Johan, and the band are performing as much as they can.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/cbd2ab28-5351-4480-b64f-43494d1a9a0e_media_01 Honey 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/58c82b23-42b4-457a-881d-32841703256c_media_GTT_top_02.png.jpg"},{"title":"Simon Walther","musik":"Rock","place":"Fredrikstad, Norway","text":"Norwegian multi-instrumentalist\/singer Simon Walther, and his band, takes you on a postrock-journeythrough rolling, dreamy soundscapes where beautiful melodies meet rattling drums and skillfully played guitars.\r\n\r\nHis first solo album: Leave The Sinking Ship Behind, was released in 2012, and received unexpectedly great reviews in both Sweden and Norway. Simon also made several interviews with Norwegian newspapers.\r\n\r\nIn November of 2012 Simon Walther and his band opened up for Norwegian artist Tommy Tokyo at a sold out S:t Croix in Fredrikstad. In 2015 Simon made a reprise, but only with his acoustic guitar and new songs from his upcoming album.\r\n\r\nThe album Byen brenner, was released during a show in Oslo, May 21, 2015, preceded by the singles Blikk s\u00f8ker blikk, and title track Byen brenner.\r\n\r\nSimon Walther is all about rock-dominated, enchanting music, with a slight touch of country.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/21daf0e8-a8be-4525-a2b0-7b62f1dc7bb8_media_Simon Walther - Blikk S\u00f8ker Blikk_Digi Master v2_150414.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/fa5dba40-873e-4229-a79d-cfa32ebe95bd_media_Pressfoto_Rickard_L_Eriksson.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Beat City Tubeworks","musik":"Rock","place":"J\u00f6nk\u00f6ping","text":"Beat City Tubeworks is a Swedish (and partly British) rock'n'roll act founded in the fall of 2014 by some of the members from the now disbanded \"The Horsehead Union\" \r\nTheir music is profoundly inspired by classics like KISS, Stones, MC5 and Status Quo from the 70's heavy rock'n'roll and boogie rock scene, mixed with a hint of punky garage rock!\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/30726dab-dc81-4c50-9770-c0a430c577be_media_Rat Race.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0a4787d8-cc83-41c3-88d2-6f5032724cf0_media_Beatcity_Montage.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"John Mitchell and Sofie Jonsson","musik":"Folk","place":"S\u00e4len","text":"John Mitchell fr\u00e5n Skottland (gitarr och s\u00e5ng) och Sofie Jonsson fr\u00e5n Dalarna (fiol och s\u00e5ng) spelar folkmusik \"with a twist\". Egna s\u00e5nger och l\u00e5tar blandas med och influeras av folkmusik fr\u00e5n Skottland, Irland, USA och Sverige. St\u00e4ms\u00e5ng och m\u00e4sterligt spel.\r\n\r\n\"Folk music beyond the ordinary.\" (Sur la Route de Memphis Magazine, France)\r\n\r\nJohn och Sofie var nominerade i kategorin \u00e5rets folkmusikpris p\u00e5 Dalecarlia Music Awards 2015, samt gick till final i Manifest on Tour p\u00e5 Fasching 2015.\r\n\r\nhttp:\/\/www.johnandsofie.com\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6f52d069-c796-4edc-af24-213fafe54955_media_Leaving Carolina.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/eb50eec8-fd15-4c4c-9f79-3328ca6e4515_media_John Mitchell & Sofie Jonsson.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Louise Lem\u00f3n","musik":"Pop","place":"Barcelona\/Borl\u00e4nge\/Falun\/G\u00e4vle","text":"Write a short presentation of your band here.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9de06236-4c15-4242-99bc-cb76e739aaff_media_Soap & Honey.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Tove Ask","musik":"Pop","place":"Malm\u00f6","text":"Missa absolut inte svenska electro-pop artisten Tove Ask spelningen under Live at Heart!\r\n\r\nTove Ask som precis sl\u00e4ppt den hyllade och kritikerrosade debut EP skivan \"By Myself\" samt musikvideo p\u00e5 VEVO!\r\n\r\nLyssna in EP skivan, se musikvideon och l\u00e4s alla recensioner och intervjuer p\u00e5: \r\n\r\n>> www.toveask.com <<\r\n\r\nHoppas vi ses!!!\r\n\r\n\/Tove Ask","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/2fef1939-a1e4-46f0-a7a0-6b641ddde249_media_C:\\Users\\Thomas M\\Music\\Tove Ask - By myself (DEMO).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/3b4fffa4-3636-4ba4-b9e9-5a8aa7d34d86_media_C:\\Users\\Thomas M\\Pictures\\TOVE-ASK.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Dugglo","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Stockholm","text":"Med ena foten i USA och den andra i Stockholm \u00e4r Dugglo en singer\/songwriter med m\u00e5nga inspirationsk\u00e4llor. Hans mix av influenser fr\u00e5n MF Doom och Bob Dylan till Mac Miller, Outkast och Joey Bada$$ har legat till grund f\u00f6r hans unika rnb-sound med texter som st\u00e4ndigt driver honom fram\u00e5t\r\n\r\nDen 15:e Juli spelade Dugglo suppport till Robert Plant p\u00e5 Gr\u00f6na Lund.\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/8688d2fe-ec7e-45e9-8e5c-138b58aa1eaf_media_Dugglo - Africa.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/ea13231c-6ed7-419a-9cbd-d0cf1ca2730a_media_Dugglo.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Bobby Sant","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Karlstad","text":"Following frequent touring in his native country Sweden, prolific folk artist Bobby Sant in January 2013 embarked on a three week\u2019s promotional tour in USA prior to the release of his second album MY DEAD TOWN. Stage appearances, co-writing sessions and industry meetings were performed in Austin TX.\r\nLater that year Bobby went on Japan tour.\r\n\r\nBobby Sant is now working hard on his third album... He locked himself up for over a year... but he\u00b4s coming to Live At Heart.\r\n\r\n\r\n\u201dI thought, let\u2019s just face the dark, embrace it and tranform it to\r\nsomething beautiful.\u201d\r\n- Bobby Sant.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/4d113aa7-019c-4e21-85b0-ea79e1cf4f02_media_Blackbird.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a0ad496f-9afa-4f72-a176-5819f1f429f7_media_IMG_7189.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Rubini","musik":"Visa","place":"Oslo","text":"Rubini er en norsk artist med mange sider! Hun jobber alene og i grupper, med jazz like som house musikk og har samarbeidspartnere i bla. Sverige, England og Brasil. Denne gangen blir det nedstrippet- to gitarer og hennes stemme er det som b\u00e6rer opptreden p\u00e5 denne festivalen!\r\n\r\n\r\nKom \u00e5 bli grepet av gode tekster og varierte melodier 5 sep! \r\n\r\n\r\nRubini is a norwegian artist of many faces! At Live At Heart she will stripp it down and bring the sweedish guitarist and producer Daniel Sengenbjerg on stage! Rubini works in groups and solo, sings jazz and soul as well as house- even released a rap song with good responses! \r\n\r\nCome and enjoy good lyrics and stripped-down material the 5th of september in \u00d6rebro! ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6691044f-fbb6-4a34-a2a5-b7dd25073ebc_media_WaterfallMp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/1ffcd68d-eafc-4bf9-96bf-a10d978cecfd_media_FacebookArtist1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Renate Rubini","musik":"Jazz","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Write a short presentation of your band here.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/a3f0d52b-0ec6-49bf-b1b3-f68051087009_media_SunparadeMp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/658e112a-9749-44b3-827a-66de7ee45179_media_6U7B4912 (1).JPG.jpg"},{"title":"The String Contingent","musik":"New acoustic chamber folk","place":"Sydney","text":"Renowned acoustic chamber-folk trio The String Contingent are headed for Scandinavia and the UK for the summer of 2015. Australians Chris Stone (violin) and Holly Downes (double bass), with Scotsman Graham McLeod (guitar), have reached \u2018the upper echelon of instrumental exploration, arrangement, composition and performance\u2019 (Tony Hillier, Rhythms Magazine), and are now expanding their geographical horizons.\r\n\r\nThe String Contingent have performed multiple times at all of the major folk and world music festivals in Australia, and have toured extensively in Australia, New Zealand and the UK. 2015 promises to be their biggest year yet, with over one hundred concerts planned in five countries. On the prospect of performing in Europe this coming summer, Chris says, \u2018We\u2019re all big fans of the Scandinavian string music traditions, and have drawn great inspiration from the subtlety and nuance of the traditional music from that part of the world. We've been lucky enough to meet and play with some of their best exponents of the exploratory side of traditional music, and the chemistry has been fantastic!\u2019\r\n\r\nThe String Contingent combine diverse musical backgrounds in Celtic, classical, jazz and pop into melodic, evocative and timeless musical discussions. Their music \u2018brings to mind the bluegrass records of Yo-Yo Ma and Edgar Meyer \u2026 with elements of Bach, Kronos Quartet and sometimes a splash of Philip Glass ... they are incredibly skilled ...\u2019 (Ulf Torstensson, Lira Magazine). Through their three albums \u2013 2010\u2019s self-titled debut, 2012\u2019s TSC II, and 2013\u2019s Talk \u2013 Chris, Graham and Holly have consistently challenged the traditional roles of their instruments. Their compositions explore a myriad of musical textures through a balance of arranged and improvised material. This approach has resulted in a musical ethos that showcases the individuality of each musician and eclipses genre, featuring bowed bass melodies, percussive violin and tight guitar grooves. The String Contingent\u2019s live performances are a joyful combination of precision, refinement and beauty, balanced with visceral energy and drive.\r\n\r\nThe String Contingent\u2019s latest album, Facets, is a collaborative expansion of this ethos, creating new music with some of Australia\u2019s most revered performer-composers. The resultant arrangements showcase the skills of their guests and the stylistic flexibility of The String Contingent. Facets seamlessly shifts through baroque, classical, jazz, Indian, Celtic and Balkan elements to create a truly contemporary sound. Now the ceaseless hunt for new and exciting musical challenges has spurred Chris, Holly and Graham on to Europe this summer \u2013 Chris enthuses, \u2018There is so much vibrant new music being made, which we feel mirrors our own explorations outwards from the various traditions that each of our playing stems from. We can't wait to present our music to such a broadminded and sympathetic audience!\u2019\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/2ef99d1b-189b-4fb5-a8d2-b89d17d91f6f_media_The String Contingent - Talk - 01 Waterlily Small MP3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/2f1d21c2-a819-4595-a965-7e67c68b4f87_media_The String Contingent Press Image.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Anders Wall\u00e9n & band","musik":"Pop","place":"Nora","text":"Anders Wall\u00e9n, en vismakare vars melodi\u00f6sa och v\u00e4ssade s\u00e5nger l\u00e4mnar avtryck och ber\u00f6r. Det \u00e4r s\u00e5nger fr\u00e5n ett h\u00f6rn av v\u00e4rlden, ett h\u00f6rn som fylls av v\u00e4rmande ljus samtidigt som det ger plats \u00e5t m\u00f6rka, evinnerliga skuggor. Dynamisk musik med texter som inte bara f\u00e5r dig att t\u00e4nka ett utan flera varv.\/Albin Str\u00f6m","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/397ed608-7749-4087-9d84-6b28e638901d_media_Mot saturnus ring.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/d8205652-49db-46ec-92d1-bc24c29b508f_media_1-DSC_0525.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Markus Hultcrantz","musik":"Americana","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"B\u00e4sta svenska folk\/singer-songwriter 2012 med l\u00e5ten Words At Silence (enligt ISC - International Songwriting Competition).\r\nInf\u00f6r Live at Heart aktuell med nya engelska \u00f6vers\u00e4ttningar av svenska visor i americana-tappning.\r\n\r\nwww.markushultcrantz.se","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9ea06f69-b2b3-43b8-94c9-b94262a6bd21_media_07 Words at silence.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/feb47fbe-a540-4250-832d-8f351ba45e1e_media_DSC_0010.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Twinleaf","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"Link\u00f6ping","text":"Twinleaf \u00e4r ett band som v\u00e4xt fram i Rimforsa, p\u00e5 Liljeholmen folkh\u00f6gskola, d\u00e4r vi samtliga studerat p\u00e5 Afrolinjen. \r\n\r\nV\u00e5rt ursprung pr\u00e4glas av 5 ungdomar med stark ambition. Twinleaf \u00e4r produkten av v\u00e5ra dr\u00f6mmar som musiker, att skapa pop-kulturell musik som alla kan delta i, som alla kan relatera och alla kan f\u00f6rst\u00e5 sig p\u00e5. Vi i Twinleaf vill s\u00e4tta en musikalisk pr\u00e4gel p\u00e5 popul\u00e4rmusik och sikta mot den breda publiken. Musikalisk \u00f6ppenhet samt samlade uttryck fr\u00e5n olika genrer ska f\u00e5 oss att uppfylla v\u00e5rt syfte, vi vill anv\u00e4nda oss av egenskaper fr\u00e5n alla v\u00e5ra medlemmar, och f\u00f6rmedla det till er.\r\n\r\nSom gemensamt m\u00e5l har vi alla att kunna f\u00f6rs\u00f6rja oss med det vi \u00e4lskar mest; musiken. Musiken \u00e4r det som driver oss och det \u00e4r det som f\u00e5r oss att vilja arbeta h\u00e5rt f\u00f6r att utvecklas. Att vara musiker \u00e4r en dr\u00f6m av h\u00f6g prioritet f\u00f6r oss alla i Twinleaf och det \u00e4r det som f\u00f6rt oss till varandra, och att g\u00f6ra detta tillsammans \u00e4r n\u00e5got som vi alla dr\u00f6mmer om. \r\n\r\nSen skulle Oskar vilja ha en hoppborg. Det \u00e4r en dr\u00f6m det.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/86bdbd54-94dd-4785-9b61-01aa1db63db1_media_Bother.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/b0b10fe1-1b2f-4c1b-bff7-a4b583c9d232_media_Loggo1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Jetbone","musik":"Rock","place":"Sundsvall","text":"Jetbone is a funky rock n' roll band from Sundsvall, Sweden with the roots in the good old 60s & 70s style. The band has existed since 2008 melting down their special brew of groove and southern rock. During their high school years they merged together with a mutual interest in good music and talented bands. By mixing their different influences they developed their own style with dancing guitars, wild drums, a screaming organ and a funky bass all topped with melodic vocals.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/933119b2-24d0-4790-bf26-3cfaa29f5b68_media_Ain't it a shame.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/92b48d02-f57b-40db-896a-7b6cb00886fa_media_JetboneGtld2015.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"MalvaKvartetten","musik":"Classic","place":"Stockholm\/\u00d6rebro","text":"Kl 21 den 4:e September fyller Malvakvartetten Nikolaikyrkan med toner och klanger av komposit\u00f6rerna Arvo P\u00e4rt, Samuel Barber och Astor Piazzolla. Varmt v\u00e4lkomna!\r\n\r\nMalvakvartetten bildades \u00e5r 2007 p\u00e5 Musikh\u00f6gskolan i G\u00f6teborg och har sedan dess bland annat studerat f\u00f6r professor Friedemann Weigle i Berlin. Nu ger de konserter b\u00e5de runt om i Sverige och i Tyskland. Under \u00e5ren har de hittat ett eget tonspr\u00e5k och tvekar inte att ta sig an nyskriven musik.\r\n\r\nF\u00f6r mer info bes\u00f6k g\u00e4rna:\r\nwww.malvakvartetten.com\r\n\r\nLyssna p\u00e5 oss:\r\nhttps:\/\/soundcloud.com\/malvakvartetten","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/013e460f-daa0-43aa-af1c-4c2649931334_media_Barber teaser halva sats 2 + 3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/115df7f7-b0b3-4723-84e5-59257eee10ad_media_Malvakvartetten trappa.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Fanny Holm","musik":"Americana","place":"Stockholm","text":"I've been singing since I was 3 years old, but I don't really see myself as a singer. I am a story teller.  \r\nI've been playing acoustic guitar for 20 years but I don't see myself as a guitarist. I am a story teller. \r\nI have been telling stories\/writing songs since I was 16, and will keep doing it until the day I die. \r\nIt's my escape, my safe place, and my deepest pleasure.\r\n\r\nFanny has been touring the UK and Wales frequently over the last 8 years, and also plays regularly at venues in Stockholm. \r\n\r\nSpotify link: https:\/\/open.spotify.com\/artist\/1QVQX77MGhIo10XAcFwPKf\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/0e74f73b-6a90-4c1a-b4c6-5f764667bc83_media_02 02 Counting My Options.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/e54e89b5-7ad0-4230-a594-2f4b3a4b1a37_media_fanny-holm-stampen.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Attic Sleepers","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"Copenhagen","text":"Four years ago, the two friends Mathias Barfod and Matias Knigge sat in the small Guatemalan village Lanquin and wrote folk songs. They decided to form the indie band The Attic Sleepers, and named their debut EP after the village Lanquin. Their first single Airport received massive airplay on Danish national radio stations P6 and P4 as well as German, Dutch and English radio stations. They have played at many festivals in Denmark including Roskilde Festival, SPOT Festival and Trailerpark Festival among others. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/997eee70-b771-42e8-a0ff-0b564182f257_media_Airport_1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/6ab424f1-7cbe-42b1-99da-1150e872680f_media_The Attic Sleepers 3.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Up Against The Phantom ","musik":"Rock","place":"Oslo","text":"Up Against The Phantom:\r\n\r\nNorwegian national radio station NRK P3 had this to say about the band:\r\n\"Euphonic, engaging rock with a touch of the (eighties and) nineties .Fans of My Bloody Valentine and Sisters of Mercy as well as fans of Briskeby\u00b4s poptunes will find plenty to like in this Osloband. They also got a new album on the way that we`re looking forward to.\r\nUp Against The Phantom creates walls of noisy guitar, dreamy melodies, pulsating basslines and hard-hitting drums with power and punkattitude.\"\r\n\r\nIn the spring of 2015, Up Against The Phantom has been noticed by the media and festival people. \r\nWith several radio plays of their songs and the booking to the Slottsfjellfestivalen, Up Against The Phantom are climbing fast in the music world. \r\n\r\nThe band consists of Melina Oz (vocals, guitar), Gunnar Kjellsby (vocals, lead guitar), Fredrik Ihler (drums) and Marius Ihler (bass).\r\n\r\nMusicvideo: \u201dFilthy Hands\u201d:https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=imsccmVteh0\r\n\r\nwww.upagainstthephantom.com\r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/soundcloud.com\/upagainstthephantom\r\n\r\nFacebook: https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/pages\/Up-Against-The-Phantom\/1463162973914166?sk=timeline\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/f9119981-8c0c-4f95-a0fd-de34a45335c1_media_Up Against The Phantom - Filthy Hands.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/07263f6c-069b-48e2-a0a6-b131681e53de_media_030-011.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"OurTime","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"INNERLIGT OCH PROFESSIONELT\r\n\u201dTrion OurTime l\u00e4mnar ingen ober\u00f6rd. Varenda slag p\u00e5 Loves trummor, varenda str\u00e4ng som sl\u00e5s an p\u00e5 Jonathans gitarr, och varenda ton Linda tar, k\u00e4nns s\u00e5 oerh\u00f6rt innerlig - p\u00e5 ett s\u00e4tt som inte g\u00e5r att v\u00e4rja sig f\u00f6r, hur jag \u00e4n f\u00f6rs\u00f6ker. \r\nSamspelet mellan dessa tre \u00e4r n\u00e5got jag s\u00e4llan sett, h\u00f6rt eller k\u00e4nt tidigare. De vet vad de h\u00e5ller p\u00e5 med, \u00e4r trygga och stabila vid sina instrument. \r\nOurTime f\u00f6rmedlar en stark k\u00e4nsla av att musik \u00e4r viktigt, och att deras musik \u00e4r n\u00e5got de g\u00e4rna f\u00f6rtrollar dig med.\u201d \/Lena Malmborg\r\n\r\n\r\nOurTime is a trio with the unique form: vocals, guitar and drums\/accordion. OurTime wants the music to speak for itself and put the lyrics and energy at front row.\r\nJonathan's musical feeling and thoughtful guitar playing adds a secure basis for Linda's delicate and delightful voice which is like balm for the soul! It all intensifies with Love\u2019s original and flowing drumplaying. \r\nOurTime\u2019s melodies are tasteful and tranquil, yet not too easily comprehendible which makes it all magical. \r\n\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/25fb3627-df20-403d-8f31-66b5d541fa96_media_02 NO HEART.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/78222a07-125f-4bc2-a947-9c01af919b72_media_Pressbild OurTime.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Sebastian Freij","musik":"Classic","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Sebastian Freij is a 28 year old cellist, arranger and composer.\r\nWith a background in classical music, Sebastian has performed in many different genres of music. Until today, Sebastian continued to develop his composing and performing with loop stations and also has workshops for musicians who want to start using the technology.\r\n\r\nWith harmonies & compositions that grows like trees, Sebastian blends genres as classical, blues, jazz, japanese and modern to create a unique sound.\r\n\r\n\u25baSoundcloud | https:\/\/soundcloud.com\/freijman\r\n\u25baYoutube | http:\/\/www.youtube.com\/freijman\r\n\u25baTwitter | http:\/\/www.twitter.com\/freijman\r\n\u25baHomepage | http:\/\/www.freijman.com\r\n\u25baFacebook | https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/freijman","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ef5f86b9-c859-4af8-b782-23b52002c4b4_media_The Friendly Stranger by Sebastian Freij.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/4bac1edd-4665-456a-95a1-167d37e5056e_media_seb_cello.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Anouschka","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Berlin\/Nairobi","text":"\"Marianne Faithful meets Joan Osborne, Shania Twain and Nora Jones\" \r\nAnouschka is an indie singer songwriter as featured in Song of the Year, Billboard World Song, International Acoustic Music Awards, John Lennon Songwriting. She studied songwriting and guitar at Berklee College of Music. Her multi-national heritage (half Swedish\/ half American) and nomadic upbringing leave a distinct mark; her songs travel through influences, moments and cultures. Home of Rock calls her \"A master of versatility.\"Swedish critic Rune H\u00e4ger, says she \"fills every song she does with intrigue... whether in the jazz, blues or rock.\" The latest album \"Shine (Angaza) \" takes Anouschka  from Nashville to Nairobi. 21st Century Artists, Hollywood, USA describe the album as \"A range from folk to pop to country with a hint of reggae perfectly thrown in\". More than a solid writer\/lyricist, she is a \"strong vocalist, but a surprisingly fine, subtle acoustic guitarist\" Music Conenction, USA and Home of Rock praises her with  \"A fantastic voice with the ability to phrase in a manner most pop stars can\u2019t.\" ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e147359d-4ec5-46b4-8294-692f7cdad372_media_06 Hey Day.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/6843b93e-b979-42ce-bcdb-b0206d3d5919_media_Anouschka-4-2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Sturle Dagsland","musik":"Advantgarde","place":"Stavanger","text":"\"An adventurous spirit, a unique sound and an irrefutable intensity... The music has a primitive and ethereal feeling. It's dark, disruptive, astonishing and groundbreaking...They cannot be categorized, because they sound like nothing that already exists.\" - The Wall\r\n\r\n\"Sturle Dagsland does not leave anyone feel indifferent, turning their concerts into a wild brutal apocalypse\" - Asociaci\u00f3n Cultural Somos Arte, Spain\r\n\r\n\"It's rare to find a song that sounds so different, so unusual and so appealing all at once. It occurred to me at one point that this might be what poking your head into an alien nightclub sounds like.\" -anewbandaday.com\r\n\r\n\"Combining a palette of electronics, instruments and most importantly a fierce, uncompromising, primitive and at the same time ephemeral vocal, they sound like nothing I've ever heard before. With his long blond hair and elvish good looks Sturle sings mythical songs that leaves no one feel indifferent.. And from his piercing eyes you can not hide even in the darkest corners of the room\" - Musecube,org, Russia\r\n\r\nSturle Dagsland consists of the Norwegian brothers Sturle & Sjur. They alternate at playing on an array of instruments and electronics, harmonically creating an expressive-progressive ever-changing soundscape dominated by Sturle's unrestrained innovative vocals ranging from ravening ferocious screams to virtous angelic chanting. His distinctive voice, large vocal range, multilingual lyrics and unique approach to songwriting and composition is only some of the reasons why you should not miss his performance at Live At Heart 2015. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/52c2c54b-f8e6-4ba7-99d5-661b5f429cb4_media_Sturle Dagsland - Mok\u00e8l\u00e9-mb\u00e8mb\u00e9.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Emelie Irewald","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"Write a short presentation of your band hereEmelie Irewald is a swedish artist that just released her first Ep \"D\u00e4r och d\u00e5 med dig\".\r\nSince her participation in this years Melodifestival everything has moved fast. She has been signing a record label contract with Sony music, recorded her Ep and now released it.\r\nEmelie is a fabules singer that really moves people with her singing. Her lyrics and her performing tell you a story and its hard not to be totally swept away.\r\nThe music goes from very small to big arena-pop. This is swedish pop that touch your heart! Sweidish music at its best!\r\n\r\nlisten at spotify:\r\nhttps:\/\/open.spotify.com\/album\/64Fkb0OGN1qkFlQOvlx9uh\r\n\r\nyoutube clipp:\r\nhttps:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=sJmojjvYG0Y\r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=ICm5zQ0aRFg\r\n\r\nClipp from the melodifestival you can find at svt.se","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/59d2f61f-ecb9-4c7d-a17f-4877ffa7ec85_media_D\u00e4r och d\u00e5 med dig (edit) mix 3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/3658a50e-5f17-4348-a2d4-bd1f5a8f3604_media_Emelie Irewald71357.IIQ.p 2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"EN DR\u00d6S POETER","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"STOCKHOLM","text":"EN DR\u00d6S POETER                                                                                                                                                     \r\n\r\nDet hyllade indiepopbandet EN DR\u00d6S POETER signade skivkontrakt med Little Ego i v\u00e5ras och gav sig ut p\u00e5 Sthlm-turn\u00e9 i samband med debutsingeln \u201dKr\u00e4ver aldrig n\u00e5got av STHLM\u201d. \r\nAllt har g\u00e5tt i en rusande fart, i maj var de en av akterna p\u00e5 stora scenen p\u00e5 P3 \u00c4LSKAR bland artister som Joy, Amason, Sabina Ddumba och Lilla S\u00e4llskapet.\r\n\r\nI sommar har de gigat p\u00e5 diverse h\u00e5ll, bla tagit f\u00e4rjan \u00f6ver till Gotland f\u00f6r gig och intervju p\u00e5 P4. N\u00e4sta vecka blir det Lasse i Parken i Hornstull, sen b\u00e4r det av till Live At Heart-festivalen och till alla blivande och redan h\u00e4ngivna fans kan vi meddela att nytt material \u00e4r p\u00e5 g\u00e5ng. H\u00e5ll \u00f6ron, \u00f6gon och hj\u00e4rtan \u00f6ppna i sensommaren och den annalkande sp\u00e4nnande h\u00f6sten 2015 med En Dr\u00f6s Poeter\r\n\r\nwww.facebook.com\/endrospoeter\r\n\r\nVilma Colling - s\u00e5ng\r\nUlrika Bremberg - piano\r\nWilma Wall - trummor\r\nOlle Adell - bas \r\n3 st cellister i full s\u00e4ttning\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/636c73d0-b104-4a04-98d7-919bc265ae43_media_Kr\u00e4verAldrigN\u00e5gotAvStockholm.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/6e13ce95-a1b1-4c49-8f13-a7cb034f5c0b_media_150513_DSC8007-Redigera_EnDrosPoeter.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Spunkmeyers","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"2014 markerade en nystart f\u00f6r The Spunkmeyers. \r\nBandet kunde under \u00e5ret h\u00f6ras p\u00e5 s\u00e5 vitt skilda st\u00e4llen som SVT och Behrn Arena, och i november sl\u00e4pptes gruppens f\u00f6rsta album, The Spunkmeyers, p\u00e5 Spotify, I-Tunes och diverse \u00f6vriga digitala kanaler.\r\n2015 \u00e4r \u00e5ret d\u00e5 The Spunkmeyers tar sin energifyllda musik ut till publiken med start p\u00e5 Live at Heart i \u00d6rebro.\r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/www.facebook.com\/spunkmeyers\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c72c0c2d-4166-400d-8dd1-f0306ec67fd2_media_I dont like.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/1abe83a9-ed9c-440c-b9b3-1abf451655d3_media_1779116_341221599385230_7600636018620612852_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Leah Nobel","musik":"Folk","place":"Nashville","text":"Mesmerizing audiences with her somber and subtle artistry, award-winning singer\/songwriter, Leah Nobel, fuses pop and folk to create a timeless and cutting-edge sound. A Phoenix, Arizona native, Leah currently resides in Nashville, Tennessee and works as a musician, actor and model.\r\n\r\nA songwriter for nearly a decade, Leah finds inspiration in love, relationships, joy, loss and fear \u2013 focusing on making music to communicate and connect with people from all ages and backgrounds.\r\n\r\nHer music career began with playing quiet solo acoustic shows at coffee houses and wineries, eventually forming a backing band and playing larger venues in 2013.\r\n\r\nLeah's single, Joshua Tree is now available on iTunes, along with her EP, Strangers Again.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/96ee8a80-45b8-44a5-861d-4c0a00248444_media_ Joshua Tree.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/4c81d97a-5326-4cc3-ad84-9a599995959c_media_leahnobel(21of28) 2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Jesus Chr\u00fcsler Supercar","musik":"Hard rock","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/5a0b4b91-1af6-4841-a6d9-e96216b88307_media_03.Death Anxiety.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/73ce2666-08f4-40c4-b4d4-7cc86f976986_media_11027968_834323863314859_2195411039313970299_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Feel Freeze","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"Copenhagen, Denmark","text":"Feel Freeze is a danish duo catching the duality between melancholy and whimsical joy in what danish radio station DR P6 BEAT sentences as 'warm musical hugs and totally catchy art pop.' \r\n\r\nFeel Freeze released their debut-EP 'Future Emotions in a Digital Heart' in 2014 from which the single 'Give Me Your Heart' was made 'Canon of the Week' on national Danish radio station DR P3. \r\n\r\nSince the debut Feel Freeze played Danish and Belgian music industry-festivals SPOT Festival & Play! Festival, supported Thomas Dybdahl (N), Cymbals Eat Guitars (US) and Owlle (F) and toured Asia in October 2014.\r\n\r\nAs a live band Feel Freeze delivers 'so much musical energy, that they can barely contain it' according to danish music magazine GAFFA, who headlines a concert-review 'excellent Danish electropop.'\r\n\r\nThe duo consists of Mathias Vinther and Raymonde Gaunoux who met up in high school and have created a unique, warm and likable universe based on melodically pop songs in whimsical and grandiose arrangements. Their attitude and performance invites the audience into an embracing listening experience based on the influence of artists like Sigur R\u00f3s, Jens Lekman and Michael Jackson.\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/546eae26-fa07-45db-a6b6-584f6bac7516_media_01 Give Me Your Heart (Radio Edit).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/2ebbb3bf-65c8-4673-8603-d790d0793c6e_media_FeelFreeze_Pressefoto.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Akosia","musik":"Reggae","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Akosia bildade sitt 9 manna band efter en Ghanaresa 2007 och har sedan dess spridit gl\u00e4dje, energi och eftertanke p\u00e5 m\u00e5nga spelst\u00e4llen, arrangemang och festivaler runt om i Sverige, \u00e4ven Ryssland och Island. Musiken har sitt ursprung i Rootsreggae men \u00e4ven Dancehall, Ska, Salsa, och V\u00e4stafrikanska rytmer f\u00e4rgar musiken. Akosias l\u00e5tar handlar om r\u00e4ttvisa, frihet, kamp, milj\u00f6, relationer och k\u00e4rlek. Genom sin musik uppmuntrar och p\u00e5minner hon om att vi alla kan g\u00f6ra f\u00f6r\u00e4ndringar, sm\u00e5 och stora s\u00e5 att livet i det lilla och i det stora f\u00e5r vara mer h\u00e5llbart. Akosia bjuder upp till dans och pratar och sjunger om viktiga saker med ett leende. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6f46b29f-2ce2-465c-95f8-fb672bcc998e_media_AKOSIA-Make me brave_Hey sister.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0ae40f33-a1a7-4edd-add1-d5e0e231fe9e_media_478690_351658161538658_1123148036_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Old Lost John","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Malm\u00f6","text":"Swedish folk-noir songsmith Tomas Thunberg records and performs under the moniker Old Lost John. He has released two albums and one EP, toured regulary in the UK and opened for artists such as Otis Gibbs, David Olney and Fairport Convention. With delicate guitar picking and a slight gravel to his voice, Old Lost John delivers quietly intense music with a dark undercurrent.\r\n\r\nBakom artistnamnet Old Lost John d\u00f6ljer sig svenske l\u00e5tskrivaren Tomas Thunberg. Han har sl\u00e4ppt tv\u00e5 album och en EP i akustisk folk-noirstil, turnerat regelbundet i Storbritannien och \u00f6ppnat f\u00f6r artister som Otis Gibbs, David Olney och Fairport Convention. Med finst\u00e4mt gitarrplock och en n\u00e5got v\u00e4derbiten r\u00f6st levererar Old Lost John stillsamt laddad musik med m\u00f6rka understr\u00f6mmar.\r\n\r\noldlostjohn.com\r\noldlostjohn.bandcamp.com\r\nwww.facebook.com\/oldlostjohn\r\nwww.youtube.com\/user\/TightGrain\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/fbe23455-1a42-4369-bddb-5667da06f39d_media_Old Lost John - Midnight Train.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/041cfd1c-1dba-4f03-8c60-84e00c755895_media_2 ed.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Neweva","musik":"Rock","place":"V\u00e4rnamo","text":"Neweva comes from the northern part of the world, a great stronghold for pop music. The Swedish Pop\/Rock band Neweva went official in May this year with the release of their debut single 'Hold Me Down'. In this short time they have been over to Liverpool and played at the world famous Cavern Club. They've also played at the biggest festival in Croatia, INmusic festival.\r\n\r\nThe members have been musicians in bands since 2006 and have tons of live experience.\r\n\r\nwww.newevaband.com","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/8c12ccc0-0798-4b7b-a2b6-db43c81c2931_media_Neweva - Hold Me Down.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/e6968ffb-4892-42dc-baf2-e44f168c3980_media_neweva profile.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Taiwaz","musik":"Hard rock","place":"Uppsala","text":" fb: taiwaz (Uppsala)","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/85ccd080-d552-4031-b5ef-2050cf784e88_media_TAIWAZ - HUMAN HUNTER.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/97ee3ce2-a989-470d-b3bf-5a6166d277fd_media_DSC_0142-4.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Diona Fox & her Ragdolls","musik":"Pop","place":"Rotterdam","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/0d540ccd-cdcb-465c-92f5-4193b12af023_media_dionafox_makemesmile_48k_mix3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/68e03663-4fa0-4782-a1d6-2e194866a6b0_media_DSC_1102Diona Fox & her Ragdolls201401122.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"M\u00c4BE","musik":"Rock","place":"Str\u00f6mstad\/Uddevalla","text":"www.mabe.nu\r\n\r\nwww.facebook.com\/mabeofficiell\r\n\r\nM\u00c4BE - Mot Ingenstans och \u00d6verallt(cd 2014)\r\n\r\n\r\n\"... ett l\u00e5gm\u00e4lt, v\u00e4lproducerat m\u00e4sterverk som sticker ut i dagens musikv\u00e4rld.\" Betyg: 9 \/ 10 - Access:Rock\r\n\r\n\r\n\"...med \u00e4nnu b\u00e4ttre reklam s\u00e5 borde den h\u00e4r killen vara v\u00e4lk\u00e4nd i hela Sverige\u2026s\u00e5 pass bra \u00e4r hans episka rockmusik.\" - Skrutt.se\r\n\r\n\r\n\"...M\u00c4BEs klart b\u00e4sta skiva \u00e4n s\u00e5 l\u00e4nge. Jag hoppas folk tar sig tid att lyssna och uppt\u00e4cka M\u00c4BE. Ni kommer f\u00e5 er med n\u00e5got v\u00e4ldigt bra av den uppt\u00e4ckten.\" - Vakentimmar\r\n\r\n\r\n\"...M\u00c4BE imponerar med detta album som jag g\u00e4rna tar med mig p\u00e5 min resa mot ingenstans och \u00f6verallt.\" - Hallowed.se\r\n\r\n\"...helt enkelt den d\u00e4r m\u00e5lande bilden av \u00f6gonblicket, ni vet s\u00e5dana som v\u00e4rdigt \u00e5terber\u00e4ttas precis som M\u00c4BE g\u00f6r det!\" Betyg 4\/5 - Spader Ess\r\n\r\n\"Mot Ingenstans Och \u00d6verallt passer rigtig godt til en m\u00f8rk og kold efter\u00e5rs eller vinter aften, hvor man har t\u00e6ndt lidt stearinlys og t\u00e6ndt op i pejsen (hvis man har s\u00e5dan en).\" Betyg: 4 av 6 - Calles Rock Corner\r\n\r\n\r\n\"...Perfect music for the fall, and I really like it...\" - Hard Rock Info\r\n\r\n\r\n\"...F\u00f6r dom som bl\u00f6der \u00e4r en riktig stark modern visa. Fastnar \u00e4ven f\u00f6r den poppiga Maskerad som redan vid f\u00f6rsta lyssningen f\u00e5r en att sjunga med i refr\u00e4ngen. Den tunga Electric City blues \u00e4r en annan l\u00e5t v\u00e4rd att n\u00e4mna. F\u00f6rsta singeln Norrskensskimmer och solnedg\u00e5ng p\u00e5minner lite om S\u00e5 l\u00e4nge vi har varann med Ratata och Frida. Fin l\u00e5t det ocks\u00e5. Finns fler.\" - Artrock.se\r\n\r\nM\u00e4be Johansson - s\u00e5ng, gitarr\r\nG\u00fcnter Olsson - gitarr\r\nKent Andreasson - bas\r\nRasmus Carlsson - trummor\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/2bf01d16-be24-479d-8cf5-e22b711cfbda_media_M\u00c4BE - Norrskensskimmer och solnedg\u00e5ng.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/3fff51c3-37a0-498c-93da-2620b422973a_media_11215228_10152763138570474_1757736908_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Banditos","musik":"Americana","place":"Nashville, TN","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/8d18b8d8-6a47-44ed-a3e5-454004d6025c_media_Forever for always for certain.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/c42fbf1c-a448-435b-8425-145afcaab5ff_media_web.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Les Gordons","musik":"Pop","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Debutalbumet \u00e4r nu sl\u00e4ppt och har lett till h\u00f6g aktivitet f\u00f6r bandet. Sommaren har inneburit b\u00e5de festivalspelningar och en gatuturn\u00e9, d\u00e4r ett flertal svenska st\u00e4der bes\u00f6kts och bjudits p\u00e5 akustiska varianter av bandets l\u00e5tar.\r\n\r\nI oktober tar Les Gordons det st\u00f6rsta steget hittills i karri\u00e4ren n\u00e4r det \u00e4r dags f\u00f6r en USA-turn\u00e9. Bandet har bland annat blivit inbjudna till att spela p\u00e5 den stora festivalen Culture Collide, vilket inneb\u00e4r spelningar i b\u00e5de San Francisco och Los Angeles. \r\nDet \u00e4r med ett stort sj\u00e4lvf\u00f6rtroende, och rykande f\u00e4rskt material som bandet nu tar sig ut i v\u00e4rlden.\r\n\r\nLes Gordons \u00e4r bandet som alltid levererar till hundra procent. En livespelning med Les Gordons \u00e4r n\u00e5got du sent kommer att gl\u00f6mma!\r\n\r\n\r\nMer om Les Gordons hittar du h\u00e4r:\r\nfacebook.com\/lesgordons\r\nlesgordons.com\r\nsoundcloud.com\/les-gordons","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/505450e0-73ab-4dca-ac17-7a978f79750b_media_05 Backbeat.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/e2192e4b-29f9-42ff-ac1e-b0258977709b_media_Banner. Retusch.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"SoLBLoMMa","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"SoLBLoMMa is a wayward Swedish electro-pop singer. With her on stage she usually have her mannequin Miriam and six dancing sheep - but this year it will be trains on the stage. \r\nFor Sheep, Solblomma-dolls, Music, Art and videos: Solblomma.com\r\n\r\nSoLBLoMMa \u00e4r en s\u00e4regen svensk elektropop-s\u00e5ngerska. Med sig p\u00e5 scenen brukar hon ha sin skyltdocka Miriam och sex dansande f\u00e5r - men detta \u00e5r kommer t\u00e5g ist\u00e4llet. \r\nF\u00f6r F\u00e5r, Solblomma-dockor, Musik, Konst och Videor: Solblomma.com","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e7e28559-3844-4eae-a648-4633e913e768_media_01 Ko-KooN People.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/36f34f83-9b37-4b1c-9be2-e17e1881b930_media_OMSLAG-SHEEPontrack.png.jpg"},{"title":"My Quiet Companion","musik":"Americana","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"My Quiet Companion fr\u00e5n G\u00f6teborg spelar \u201cAmericana med skandinavisk edge\".\r\nTexter som kryper under skinnet, tre gitarrer, dobro, mandolin, stompboard och st\u00e4ms\u00e5ng skapar ett akustiskt och intimt sv\u00e4ng d\u00e4r du kan luta dig tillbaks och lyssna p\u00e5 s\u00e5ngernas ber\u00e4ttelser.\r\n\r\nPatrick Rydman, Sofia Ekberg och Henrik Cederblom m\u00f6ttes 2013, under inspelningen av Sofias debut-EP All the Small Details. Spelgl\u00e4djen var ett faktum, och sedan dess har de spelat och turn\u00e9rat tillsammans b\u00e5de i Sverige och utomlands. \r\nTrion har exempelvis spelat f\u00f6rband tiil Aoife O\u2019Donovan fr\u00e5n Crooked Still (Pustervik G\u00f6teborg) och h\u00f6sten 2014 gjorde de en gemensam konsert p\u00e5 Konstepidemin i G\u00f6teborg med Adam Levy (l\u00e5tskrivare\/gitarrist fr\u00e5n Norah Jones\u2019 The Handsome Band). Senast i april  framtr\u00e4dde de p\u00e5  Arctic Sounds Festival (Sisimiut, Gr\u00f6nland).  My Quiet Companion har \u00e4ven gjort konserter i otaliga gympahallar och skolaulor i S\u00f6rmland och V\u00e4stra G\u00f6taland d\u00e4r de ocks\u00e5 pratat l\u00e5tskriveri med h\u00f6gstadie- och gymnasieelever.  \r\n\r\nBortom My Quiet Companion frilansar Henrik som gitarrist\/ producent, har bla jobbat med Sofia, Carlsson, Freddie Wadling och Sofie Livebrant. Patrick har sl\u00e4ppt tv\u00e5 plattor i eget namn, frilansar i diverse musikteaterprojekt, \u00e4r en del av k\u00f6ren Amanda fr\u00e5n G\u00f6teborg. Jobbar ocks\u00e5 som producent och l\u00e5tskrivare f\u00f6r andra artister. Sofia har en bakgrund inom musikteater, och har deltagit i  produktioner p\u00e5 bla. Oscarsteatern och \u00d6stg\u00f6tateatern.  Hon spelar \u00e4ven en del i solo och sl\u00e4ppte sin debut EP, 2013. N\u00e4r hon inte spelar sj\u00e4lv driver hon singer\/songwriterlinjen, L\u00f6ftadalens folkh\u00f6gskola i \u00c5sa, Halland. \r\n\r\n\r\nMy Quiet Companion spelar just nu in sin debutplatta, med planerat sl\u00e4pp i b\u00f6rjan av h\u00f6sten 2015.\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/068a99e1-445a-4d37-8452-90a9532b346f_media_04 Let it slip away-2.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/456b7043-94a5-4b64-b8e2-f87b34815998_media_1039677_635256196524353_1886246566_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Le Maine","musik":"Rock","place":"The vast woodlands","text":"Le Maine is a dark world of tales, a beautiful and bittersweet story where good doesn\u2019t always prevail and where each feeling has its own sound.\r\nThe cinematic elements are significant to Le Maines trademark and focus lies on the narrative of storytelling - both in lyrics and in live performances.\r\n\r\nThe bands first single \u201dDaughter of a King\u201d was released in the fall of 2013 and was recognized by many international music websites. A fan-made music video accompanied the success and proved Le Maines distinct story-based concept through animation. \r\n\r\nIn preparation for the new release \"Resolution\" Le Maine partnered up with star photographer Karolina Henke and the multiple award winning design studio Stockholm Graphics. Together they have graphically created an enchanted world. The collaboration goes under the name of #ARTESTORIES and includes pictures that will be released this year. \r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/1397250a-fa53-4bb9-968e-0c7cc14e261a_media_Le Maine - Resolution.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/8779c648-ff70-4e9a-8c6b-46d05841e539_media_Orginal-The-Red-Queen_Small.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Lionfly Secrets ","musik":"Americana","place":"London\/Malm\u00f6","text":"Lionfly Secrets is composed of trio Erica Zandelin,Sebastian Fernstedt and Nikolai Hemmingsson. Erica has had successes as a solo artist and recently studied one year at the British and Irish Modern Music Institute in London. Sebastian works as a producer in Malm\u00f6. \r\n\r\nErica and Sebastian met when Sebastian produced Erica's first single in the singers hometown, and have continued to work together since. After having toured together they set out to make it official, and came out as Lionfly Secrets.\r\nIn 2015 Nikolai Hemmingsson became an official member after he played piano on the upcoming EP \"Hard times\".\r\n \r\n \r\nLionfly Secrets has created a new exciting sound. With Erica Zandelin on dark vocals, Nikolai Hemmingson on synth\/pads and Sebastian Fernstedt on Electric guitar they create a mix of \"elektro-indie\/rock\" music with influences from folk, and they make it sound like nothing else. \r\nIf you want to hear something new, Lionfly Secrets is the right choice!  \r\n\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9d1b9b3f-5752-4034-a14b-da784c158fd4_media_Darkdreams_LionflySecretsmp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/d860787f-af10-40d9-a32f-6f7060c4910b_media_DarkDreams_LionflySecrets_STN2015_bild kopia.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Orango","musik":"Rock","place":"Oslo","text":"Orango:\r\nKnown for their high-energy live perfomances, Orango has emerged as one of the most active, developed and sought-after bands for festivals, clubs and student venues throughout Norway. Their new album - Battles - has just been released in Europe (Stickman Records) , to rave reviews: \r\nA true masterpiece (Metal Underground)\r\nEin absolutes Hammeralbum (Hooked on Music)\r\nShockingly great (Metal Hammer Norway)\r\nThe band is determined to expand their reach to all locations in Europe.\r\n\r\nPurveyors of honest and straightforward blues-infused vocal harmony rock, the trio Orango have worked on their musical blend and live reputation through five albums and hundreds og gigs. The band consists of Karl-Joakim Wisl\u00f8ff on bass, Trond Sl\u00e5ke on drums and Helge Bredeli Kanck on guitars, and all are featured vocalists. Their music is of the long-playing format, never shy of a hefty guitar solo or jamming in general. The band members say they are inspired by good ol\u00b4rock\u00b4n roll, good new rock\u00b4n roll, good ol\u00b4 blues, and good new blues\", namedropping bands like Lynyrd Skynyrd, ZZ Top, Mountain, Led Zeppelin, Johnny Winter, Peter Green's Fleetwood Mac, Creedence Clearwater Revival, and Crosby Stills Nash & Young.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c26d46c2-2d4d-4df7-b9ce-576bf48386ad_media_orango_digginforpraise 2014.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a55b9601-fc34-4770-8c43-85f06fd50d47_media_5_orango_foto_stian nybru.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Bloakes","musik":"Rock","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/f84ed8db-2ef0-42a7-a438-c0a9b28acf37_media_Bhagavan.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5c024b5a-35bb-486f-9802-caaa2de02be5_media_bloakessoffa.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Folkt\u00e5get","musik":"Pop","place":"Nyk\u00f6ping","text":"Det ska sl\u00e5 ner som en komet! Det kommer k\u00e4nnas i magen, men det m\u00e5ste upplevas!\r\nFolkt\u00e5get \u00e4r \u00f6s, gl\u00e4dje, folkfest och en v\u00e4lriktad t\u00e5r! Pop\/rock\/hiphop\/soul eller vad man nu ska kalla musiken. Hur som helst s\u00e5 \u00e4r det bara att kliva p\u00e5 t\u00e5get och gunga med. F\u00f6rsta skivan \"Od\u00f6dliga\" turnerades f\u00f6rra sommaren med nedslag som Putte i parken, Kalmar Stadsfest, Nyk\u00f6ping Stadsfest mm. \u2028Den 30:e maj sl\u00e4ptes nya skivan \u201dSpringer f\u00f6r livet\u201d med dunder och brak. G\u00e4startister som, Robert W\u00e4rn, Tony Ejremar, Aaron Sterner och Caxton Njuki. Nu drar Folkt\u00e5get ut p\u00e5 sommarturn\u00e9 med stopp p\u00e5 bland annat Uport Festivalen (Ulricehamn), Folk- & rockfestivalen (Segmon), Musikfesten (Jogers\u00f6) och VOX Festivalen (\u00d6rebro) f\u00f6r att n\u00e4mna n\u00e5gra. I h\u00f6st planeras en omfattande klubbturn\u00e9 fr\u00e5n Norr till s\u00f6der. H\u00e4ng p\u00e5 t\u00e5get du ocks\u00e5!\u2028\r\n\r\n-\u201dL\u00e5ter helt fantastiskt Svenskt \u00e5 galet bra. F\u00e5r mig att vilja dansa genom hela sommarn!! MERA MERA har hittat en ny grupp f\u00f6r mig. Egotrippad som jag \u00e4r s\u00e5 \u00e4r vinsten min, f\u00e5r lyssna om\u00e5omigen;)\u201d  - Mats A, Nyvunnen Folkt\u00e5gare\r\n\r\n-\u201dSom en hybrid mellan Hoffmeastro, Winnerb\u00e4ck, Ulf Lundell och allt d\u00e4r emellan. Kan inte f\u00f6rklara det b\u00e4ttre, men det va j\u00e4vligt coolt!\u201d  Linda G, Nyvunnen Folkt\u00e5gare\u2028\r\n\r\n-\u201dElin (fronfigur) & Folkt\u00e5get har toppat varannan lista i succ\u00e9 i \u00e5r\u2026\u201d  - 1:a  p\u00e5 \u00e5rets kulturlista i tidningen Succ\u00e9. Anders Tegner. \r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/a6a5d8a8-952f-4469-9709-4f694b5829b2_media_VI SPRINGER F\u00d6R LIVET (live at heart).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/73e6c7bb-3ea1-4b63-94a8-295b8ae2f2b7_media_11102769_733297346767992_1684779110736243732_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Eva Stenstr\u00f6m Limited","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Eva Stenstr\u00f6m Limited har medverkat vid Live at Heart och Folk at Heart i flera \u00e5r och g\u00f6r musik inom flera genrer; \r\nsingersong, funky, tango, pop, etno, folk\u2026allt genomf\u00f6rt  i en groovig stil med endast gitarr, bas och s\u00e5ng.\r\nInstrumenteringen och arrangemangen varierar med u-base, klaviatur, dragspel, kastanjetter mm.\r\nAll musik \u00e4r skriven av Eva Stenstr\u00f6m som varit verksam musikaliskt i Malm\u00f6, Lule\u00e5 och nu \u00d6rebro i 15 \u00e5r.\r\nMagnus Sj\u00f6quist p\u00e5 basar och Daniel Bj\u00f6rnmo p\u00e5 gitarrer \u00e4r b\u00e5da verksamma musiker runtom i landet,  men bosatta i \u00d6rebro.\r\n\r\nMusik ska k\u00e4nnas.  Texter vill bli h\u00f6rda.  \r\nKom och upplev!\r\n\r\nFor English information, read below:\r\nEva Stenstr\u00f6m Ltd have had a number of concerts at Live at Heart and Folk at Heart the last years, and plays music from different genres\r\nsuch as singersong, funky, tango, pop, etno, folk\u2026all done in a kind of groovy style with just bass, guitars and vocals.\r\nThe arrangements has a lot of colorings with different instrumenting like u-base, castanets, accordion, etc.\r\nThere are three members of the band ; Magnus Sj\u00f6quist, bass. \r\n                                                               Daniel Bj\u00f6rnmo, guitars.\r\n                                                               Eva Stenstr\u00f6m, vocals and composer of the songs.\r\n\r\nThis is groove.\r\nCome and join the move!\r\n                                          \r\n  ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/5f51918b-a920-47bf-a7bf-2a86a7fb842d_media_preview-2.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/4b06d3af-29fc-4cbd-80d3-4accca50edcd_media_ES Ltd.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Lone Pine","musik":"Rock","place":"Gvarv - Norway","text":"The Lone Pine best\u00e5r av fem medlemmer som setter musikken i fokus.  Bandet har i flere \u00e5r jobbet med \u00e5 bygge opp l\u00e5tmaterialet og spille konserter. \r\nI 2013 og 2014 jobbet de med produsent J\u00f8rn Christensen. Resultatet ble debutplata \"Through The Waiting\".  Plata ble utgitt i mai 2014 og gikk rett til topps p\u00e5 iTunes sin norske albumliste. Live har bandet f\u00e5tt turnert sammen med Deep Purple vokalist Glenn Hughes og Rainbow vokalist Joe Lynn Turner i Norge, samt spilt flere konserter i Storbritannia.\r\n\r\nThe Lone Pine spiller rock med inspirasjon fra mange sjangre. Bandets medlemmer jobber hardt for at publikum skal f\u00e5 en konsertopplevelse fylt av god musikk, fra det rolige og s\u00e5re, til det harde og r\u00e5e. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/eb6d4ec0-35ab-43c6-8829-49f22f8d0764_media_10 Brad Don\u00a6t tell them my name (1).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a6fbe2b7-964d-432f-929c-a06a5ac7300b_media_1097210_670166036344829_456583425_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Thyra","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Stockholm","text":"Duon Thyra har p\u00e5 kort tid n\u00e5tt oerh\u00f6rda framg\u00e5ngar p\u00e5 streaming tj\u00e4nster som t.ex. Spotify och Deezer med n\u00e4rmre 15 miljoner lyssningar.\r\nDe har uppm\u00e4rksammats bl.a. i USA och England f\u00f6r deras fina och unika akustiska tolkningar av andras l\u00e5tar. \r\n\r\n\u201dAtt skapa egna versioner av l\u00e5tar andra skrivit \u00e4r n\u00e5got vi gjort i snart 20 \u00e5r. Det \u00e4r en utmaning att f\u00f6r\u00e4ndra och f\u00f6r\u00e4dla en redan bra l\u00e5t utan att f\u00f6rst\u00f6ra den. Det m\u00e5ste k\u00e4nnas eget, annars n\u00e5got som k\u00e4nns som ett nytt grepp annars \u00e4r det liksom ingen ide\"\r\n\r\nTack vare den uppm\u00e4rksammade version av Katy Perrys Firework och Robyns Dancing on my own har \u00e4ven lyssnarna f\u00e5tt upp \u00f6gonen f\u00f6r duons egna material. Den senaste singeln Since You've been gone har n\u00e5tt \u00f6ver en miljon streams.\r\nEn coverplatta sl\u00e4pptes i Maj och nu jobbar duon p\u00e5 en uppf\u00f6ljare med originall\u00e5tar.\r\n\r\nThis amazing Swedish Duo has in a very short time reached over 15 miljon streams on Spotify, Deazer and other streaming sites.\r\nThere unique soulful cover versions of major hit songs has made it on several international playlists and also opened a way for the listeners to find their original music. \r\nWith one foot in traditional american singer songwriter music and the other in \u201dOld School Soul\u201d  Thyra creates a unique retro sound that feels fresh and new.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/33f3cadc-3f6e-4f8f-a64f-00a0f0b0d7dd_media_Since you been gone-M.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/23206328-b52e-472f-90a1-1817b71ebaff_media_THYRA.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"ATLAS","musik":"Hard rock","place":"Karlstad","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/fc279849-df9f-45b9-97e7-46d11fe99e9c_media_Red Sage.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/7702be70-8869-45a5-be47-eb2521592155_media__DSC8934.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Rivertown Blues","musik":"Blues","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Rivertown Blues levererar bluesens avgrundssvarta tong\u00e5ngar blandat med det sexiga retrosoundet som h\u00f6r soulen till - en riktigt \u00f6sig och f\u00e4rgsprakande liveakt - missa inte det!","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/cb325683-d2d8-420a-bbef-e648fa11144b_media_3.Girl At The Coffeshop.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/c900ef89-2f9f-405d-a353-4204553f69df_media_rivertownbluesvitlogga.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Perry and The Travellers","musik":"Rock","place":"Karlstad","text":"\r\nThere isn\u00b4t a lot of bands that would stick together after living through what Perry and The Travellers have done the last decade. Setbacks seem to have succeeded each other with numerous of disastrous tour incidents, financial problems, personal failures and infighting. However, this band seems to be made of the right stuff and has somehow managed to stick together despite all the difficulties.\r\nSince the start in 2004 the band has developed from classic southern rock to a mature rock band with wide influences from 70\u00b4s rock, country, americana and more modern rock. With three albums in the back, more than 250 shows in Europe and the U.S. the band have made themselves a name in the underground rock scene, and have also managed to get attention from the country scene. \r\nLive shows are what the band enjoys the most and they prove again and again they\u00b4re a high-class live act playing prestigious festivals such as South By Southwest (US) and Sweden Rock Festival (S), among many others.\r\n\r\nThe fourth album, recorded in venerable Silence Studio by legendary sound engineer Anders Lind, is once again caught live on tape to get the ultimate feel. It is set to release during 2015.\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/a41701c6-d4ce-43fc-afd0-1d028b9c3a5c_media_B-Bender_mp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/2073e413-cb5f-457b-b0c6-50371746c600_media_PATT_presspic2_low.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Wolf & Moon","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Utrecht","text":"Wolf & Moon is a travelling band consisting of Stefany June and Talk Show Host.\r\nRight now we're in Stockholm to record our EP.\r\n\r\nWolf & Moon is a musical duo consisting of Stefany June and Talk Show Host. Somewhere between the folky sound of Angus & Julia Stone and the electronic influences of The XX, you can find the resonance of Wolf & Moon. Wolf & Moon is the longing for adventure and travel. That is why you can only find them using a minimal set up which they can easily take on a road trip. A travel guitar, a drum computer and mini keys plus their distinctive voices, that is all it needs to get you into the vibe of Wolf & Moon.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/66d65c51-86c6-4168-b745-9464d777d290_media_Wolf & Moon.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/b03771cd-7db6-43ce-a643-a6308ebb5486_media_artwork 2015.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Tyranex","musik":"Metal","place":"V\u00e4ster\u00e5s","text":" \r\nBIOGRAPHY\r\n \r\n \r\n TYRANEX is an energetic act from Sweden that sounds like the young bands from 85\u2019, like: Kreator, Destruction, Agent Steel, and Megadeth. Fronted and driven by female leadguitarist and singer Linnea Landstedt, backed up with great musicians, Johannes Lindstr\u00f6m, Per Lindstr\u00f6m and Nino Vukovic. \r\nTYRANEX is real, oldschool, speed metal with attitude!\r\n \r\n \r\nIt all begun\u2026\r\n \r\n...at a \"RAM\"-concert in Sweden 2005 where the first sculptures of TYRANEX took form.\r\n \r\nA complete line-up was put together in 2006 and TYRANEX could rehearse as a whole band.\r\n \r\n2006 - 2010 TYRANEX released a few demos and practiced playing live alot!! \r\n \r\n \r\n2011 TYRANEX got their first record deal. They released their debut album \r\n\u201cExtermination has begun\u201d at Infern\u00f6 Records (Fra) in 1000 CD copies. \r\nIn 2013 was the album released on Vinyl by Journeys end Records (Ger).\r\n \r\n \r\nIn January 2014 TYRANEX went into the studio to record their second album. \r\n\"Unable to tame\" was released the 10th of Ocotber 2014 at Black Lodge records (cd and vinyl). \r\n \r\nThe same year TYRANEX was, for the first time, played on air with their new album and interview at swedish national radio. \r\nNot much later they where nominated for swedish radio award P3 GULD (GOLD). \r\n \r\n \r\n \r\nDuring the years TYRANEX has toured in Sweden, Finland, Germany, Netherlands, Belgium, Spain and France. They\u2019ve played at big festivals like Metal Assault, Jalometalli, Steelfest and Taunus metal. \r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/eec95494-b4a9-4b74-89b9-470ee5cde1d3_media_02 Unable to Tame.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0104d836-e1e8-4d74-81b3-f57ae20ecad0_media_Tyranex promo 2015_photographer Style Magazine.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Osten af & Hyvlarna","musik":"Hiphop","place":"V\u00e4ster\u00e5s\/\u00d6rebro\/Norrk\u00f6ping","text":"D\u00e4r vissa andra svenska rappare blickar v\u00e4sterut och f\u00f6rs\u00f6ker pryda sina mellansvenska medelklassliv med p\u00e5klistrad gangstamentalitet, n\u00f6jer sig Osten af med att kolla ut genom f\u00f6nstret. \r\n\r\nOsten af har varit med ett tag. Men han forts\u00e4tter att hela tiden g\u00e5 sin egen v\u00e4g. Som n\u00e4r han sl\u00e4ppte musikvideon till \"Hiphophj\u00e4lten\" d\u00e5 han valde att ta hiphopen tillbaka till skogen ist\u00e4llet f\u00f6r att en video med sk\u00e4llande kamphundar. Han \u00e4r \u00e4ven k\u00e4nd f\u00f6r l\u00e5ten\/videon \"Farv\u00e4l \u00d6rebro\" som blev den f\u00f6rsta svenska officiella musikvideon p\u00e5 teckenspr\u00e5k.\r\n\r\nMed vardagsn\u00e4ra texter och total\u00e4rlighet \u00e4r Osten troligtvis den svenska rapparen som flest i landet kan personifiera sig med.\r\n\r\nTill Live at Heart kommer \u00e4ven Osten backas upp av livebandet Hyvlarna som redan \u00e4r bekanta i LAH sammanhang.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/03dbf176-1dcf-4eaf-8ed4-78ea9279aee0_media_Hyvlarna - SA JA! + Ordningsvakter.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/27ae1927-c4b0-4ae5-b9ed-67349ab71bde_media_Hyvlarna1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Close Quarters","musik":"Hard rock","place":"Vadstena","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/b5b3e5de-554a-408e-bf0a-ae8e77860a67_media_My Way Or The Highway .mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/d8156b20-f989-4e14-8181-d8a1b9eab82b_media_11169686_828986200470705_4660232869045612163_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Leion","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Norrk\u00f6ping","text":"Is there anything that can reach to your soul more than having your life put into words through a song? It was the ability to create this phenomena that drove Leion into start playing guitar and writing songs. The chance to capture life, in its smaller or wider context, and preserve it in songs. The lyrics are very painting and describing but then backed by a folkrock sound with heavy backing vocals, big dynamics and poweful melodies. \r\n\r\n\u201dThe first time I heard a song with Leion, the hair on my arms rose a little\u2026 It is not that often one gets that feeling. I think we will see and hear more from him in the future.\u201d\r\n\r\n- Ulf Bejerstrand, CEO Fantastiska N\u00f6jen vid Globen AB","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/27350907-d5e6-449b-adeb-0b4bef6072e0_media_Joakim Leion - Vid Skiljev\u00e4gen (mstrd).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/240c6b3a-a903-437f-bdde-2c068077aea5_media_Pressbild_3.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Driving Cassady","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"Driving Cassady is a soul\/pop\/rock\/jazz-band that formed in Stockholm. With members from Sweden, Italy and U.S.A the influences are widely spread but the music has its most apparent roots in the 60's-70's America. Having three main songwriters and vocalists contributes to the versatile repertoar and the retro vs new vibe, \"Think the Black Keys jamming with Jim Morrison and Sly & the Family Stone\" - The Mad Mackerel.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/067264a7-3038-4ad8-9df6-a8c8c79ee4da_media_Wonder.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/ff84e280-9ade-4026-8583-050aaa47e4d1_media_10464069_724422024271222_3682761241006506812_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Vargtegel","musik":"Folk","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"VARGTEGEL bildades 1974 av syskonen Str\u00f6mberg och trumslagaren Nisse Berg\r\nSedan dess har m\u00e5nga musiker, uppskattningsvis ett hundratal, passerat genom gruppen\r\nUnder 1980-talet har Pelle Wallden och Bo E-son tillkommit\r\n2013 tillkom Sebastian Wellander p\u00e5 gitarr\r\nUnder 2013-14 har gruppen f\u00f6rst\u00e4rkts med nya s\u00e5ngare och l\u00e5tskrivare som Elias Gustavsson och Marcus Pettersson\r\nSlagverksektionen har ut\u00f6kats med Emelie Sj\u00f6str\u00f6m och Linus Lundquist p\u00e5 congas, djembe och olika percussioninstrument\r\n\r\nMusiken \u00e4r inspirerad av fr\u00e4mst afrikanska rytmer och en stor del av repertoaren h\u00e4rr\u00f6r fr\u00e5n ett samarbete med den nigerianske saxofonisten och komposit\u00f6ren Chris Dele Okonkwo under 1980-talet\r\n\r\nDet finns dock inspiration fr\u00e5n all v\u00e4rldens folkmusik, till exempel fr\u00e5n de nordiska l\u00e4nderna och orienten\r\n\r\nVargtegels musik \u00e4r rytmisk och dansant, ofta med tydlig folkton, ibland mer afro beat jazzig\r\n\r\nVargtegel \u00e4r ett live-band som spelat runt om i Sverige genom \u00e5ren, p\u00e5 festivaler, musikf\u00f6reningar och klubbar samt vid m\u00e5nga allm\u00e4nna och privata fester\r\nVargtegel \u00e4r \u00d6rebrobaserade och har medverkat vid en av Europas st\u00f6rsta musikfestivaler, Liveatheart 2013\r\n\r\nVargtegel kan bokas genom\r\nMats Str\u00f6mberg\r\n019-145968\r\nBo E-son\r\n0762-526546\r\n\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/723b75dd-dfae-483e-b977-6dc46f88f2bb_media_06.Yabonza.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/1b93bd1c-a285-4733-8bf2-aca8cc717c80_media_Vargtegel Kulturhuset 141002 r\u00f6d.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Torpus & The Art Directors","musik":"Folk","place":"Hamburg, Tyskland","text":"Torpus & The Art Directors kommer tillbaka till Sverige f\u00f6r en ny Sverigeturn\u00e9 och bes\u00f6k under Live at Heart passar perfekt. \r\n\r\nEfter tre kritikerrosade album, signade av Tysklands st\u00f6rsta indiebolag Grand Hotel van Cleef. Med g\u00f6teborgska basisten Jenny Apelmo i bandet s\u00e4tter nu Torpus & The Art Directors kursen mot Sverige i september. Det Hamburg-baserade bandet \u00e4r kontrabas, st\u00e5lstr\u00e4ngade gitarrer, raspiga r\u00f6ster och fantastiskt energi p\u00e5 scen. Lyssna p\u00e5 senaste singeln \"In Hushed Tones\" och lyssna sedan vidare p\u00e5 Spotify och Youtube s\u00e5 hoppas jag vi ses p\u00e5 Live at Heart. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/07200ceb-072c-42f6-aaaf-20ae1ed61259_media_In Hushed Tones.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/37903b84-e7ce-4122-855d-07080774d8fb_media_TATAD2015-5 Credit Eugen Heimb\u00f6ckel.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Hege Brynildsen","musik":"Country","place":"Halden, Norway","text":"Hello there!\r\n\r\nMy name is Hege and I have been playing at the Live At Heart festival a couple of times before. Love \u00d8rebro! I have made two albums, and I am a Rootsy recording artist, a big thanks to H\u00e5kan Olsson. My first record HEGE came out in 2012, and my latest record TILL HARRY came  out last year in 2014. TILL HARRY is in Swedish by the way, and HEGE in English. I write my own material, and people describe it as coutry. I am from Halden, Norway and with me to \u00d8rebro I have a woderful guitarist named Omar, from Halden too. Looking forward to sing and dance  in \u00d8rebro in a few weeks! If you visit my homepage www.hegebrynildsen.no you`ll be able to listen to some of my music and maybe see a few live performances as well. Nothing fancy, though, but You`ll get the picture. You can also find me on FB and Instagram.  My two records, HEGE and TILL HARRY  is also on Tidal and Spotify. Hope to see you around in \u00d8rebro then. My favourite town after Halden. Hehe.\r\n\r\nTake Care.\r\n\r\nHege.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/3dd2f333-9395-454e-b8f0-c1793dba3be1_media_TV\u00c5 F\u00c5GLAR.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/1989175b-cfa9-48a6-9f3d-c930b9912ec1_media_Hege IMG_2290 copy_pp copy.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Kung Botes Kapell","musik":"Blues","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Kung Botes Kapell tar ut sv\u00e4ngarna, mixar traditionell blues med soul, ett st\u00e4nk jazz och pudrar med lite swing.\r\nIdel erfarna musiker, tillsammans mer \u00e4n 120 \u00e5rs erfarenhet av musik.\r\nOrgeltungt, sv\u00e4ngigt och hett.\r\n\r\nJanne Shuffle Hermansson - s\u00e5ng & elgitarr\r\nAnders Nordquist - trummor\r\nPO Larsson - Hammond XB3c\r\nPer Edlund - Silvertonebas","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/05a53151-6f2b-41a0-b0cc-d6233ac5cee5_media_Kung Botes Kapell - Walking My Devil.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/24b1fc02-844c-4751-ad3e-201152105d1c_media_Kung Botes Kapell.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Charlize Merighi Band","musik":"Americana","place":"Grebbestad \/ Stockholm","text":"\u201dS\u00e5 kommer det d\u00e4r tillf\u00e4llet i bokerskans tillvaro och n\u00e4rvaro n\u00e4r hon k\u00e4nner att hon st\u00f6tt p\u00e5 guldmalm. Ett mail mitt i natten med en l\u00e4nk. En l\u00e4nk till musik som ger rysningar. En musik som osar R\u00c4TT! Ni har kommit r\u00e4tt. Vi har kommit r\u00e4tt! Ni h\u00f6r hemma h\u00e4r. Vi \u00e4r i sluttamp av bokningar och m\u00e5ste trixa, flytta och f\u00f6rhandla. Men vi ska ha dom. Charlize Merighi Band.\u201d - Karin Forsling, Arrang\u00f6r Folk och Rock\r\n\r\nMed kraft och k\u00e4nsla spr\u00e4nger Charlize Merighi Band ny mark f\u00f6r akustisk musik. Deras nyskrivna musik plockar russinen ur bandmedlemmarnas favoritkakor. Det blir en n\u00e4rmast oplacerbar fusion av blues, americana, folkrock, och fransk, svensk och keltisk folkmusik.\r\nL\u00e4ngst fram p\u00e5 scen st\u00e5r Charlize, med sin r\u00f6st vill hon vara en motpol till idealet d\u00e4r kvinnor ska komma s\u00e5 h\u00f6gt upp i registret som m\u00f6jligt. Hennes r\u00f6st \u00e4r naturligt djup, och hon pressar hellre sin r\u00f6st ner \u00e4n upp. Hon har sin bakrund i metalband och p\u00e5 singer-songwriter scenen. Hon kliver p\u00e5 scen med en snus under l\u00e4ppen och \u00f6ppnar upp mot publiken texter som ger inblick i hennes inre sinnrika v\u00e4rld. En v\u00e4rld fylld av k\u00e4rlek, \u00e5ngest, hoppl\u00f6shet, galna \u00e4nkor, eufori och olyckliga sj\u00f6m\u00e4n.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c56ed53e-777f-4994-9924-7509dd7db9e0_media_Hold on 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5f25df57-055c-4ac3-80fa-d7b35710b758_media_11052499_965315286836084_6799501154287483317_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Kaskelott","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"\u201cSweden has done it again by giving the world some amazing music\u201d. That one review summarizes Kaskelott\u2019s simple yet ambitious vision: to create amazing music. We strive to make people dance and sing along with glassy eyes, smiling as they recognize pieces of their own life\u2019s story in the lyrics.\r\n\r\nKaskelott is a quartet that plays danceable yet thoughtful indie\/rock\/pop, hailing from Scandinavia\u2019s music capital of Gothenburg, Sweden. During the future band-members early teenage years, The Strokes album Is This It was played from start to finish every night before they fell asleep. This gave birth to a sincere affection of melodies and rock\u2018n\u2019roll, and their influences have been diverse ever since. The members of Kaskelott have continuously strived to go their own way, both musically and individually. Despite being from Gothenburg, Kaskelott never adopted the famous indie-sound that\u2019s associated with the city, but instead opted to explore different musical terrains. The new song Vagabonds deals with the band\u2019s ambivalence towards their exclusion from \u2018indiedom\u2019, and the simultaneous creative freedom that this has entailed. \r\n\r\nThe spark that ignited the band was a US-related quirk of fate which resulted in a gig at the legendary Wiltern Theater in Hollywood, which represented the first time that the band\u2019s singer sang live. As a result, he assembled the band. In 2013 the debut EP Retrospective was recorded in the darkness of Nacksving Studios, and released later that year. The release gig attracted \u201cthe greatest crowd pressure ever at Clooney\u2019s,\u201d according to Daniel Norin, club manager. Since then, numerous gigs have been performed around Sweden.\r\n\r\nDuring 2014, new music was recorded in Stockholm. The lyrical themes cover inclusion and exclusion, confessions on the tram, jumps from cliffs by the sea and ruins that should be left in the ashes. The stories take place during feverish summer nights, under the falling cherry blossoms in Tokyo and below t\u00ad\u00adhe moon in the west coast archipelago. They have the pulse of New York and the honesty of a personal diary.\r\n\r\n- \u201cOur ambition is to create music that, above all, is authentic and meaningful to ourselves,\u201d says lead singer Joakim. \u201cWe seek to discover great melodies, make music that\u2019s contagious without compromising our integrity, to think somewhat outside of the genre-box and to be very honest.\u201d\r\n\r\nThe first single from the recording session in Stockholm, Vagabonds, will be released in July. The second single, Pompeii, will be released later this fall \r\n\r\nFinally, we can reveal that the band has started recording even more new music at legendary Svenska Grammofonstudion. The band aims at releasing the songs that they\u2019re recording there in the near future... Stay tuned!","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e06c2d0a-f972-4347-b42a-21e713ce6e46_media_Stay together 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/f2db4497-1b1b-4319-b8b7-25c8f45af006_media_Kaskelott 2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Age of Woe","musik":"Metal","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Age of Woe fr\u00e5n G\u00f6teborg drivs av ett beg\u00e4r att utforska nya ljudlandskap i gr\u00e4nslandet mellan punk och metal. Kvintetten drivs av en DIY-etik och deras musik har unika kombinationer av m\u00f6rker, tyngd och sv\u00e4ng - f\u00f6r fans av organisk hardcore-inspirerad metal. Age of Woe \u00e4r trogna sin bakgrund inom punk och metalscenen.\r\nBandet har funnits sedan h\u00f6sten 2010 och har hittills sl\u00e4ppt en 7\" (2011), albumet Inhumanform (Suicide Records\/Give Praise Records, 2013), en split 7\" med 100 Years (Suicide Records\/Give Praise Records, 2014) och gjort fem europaturn\u00e9er, st\u00f6rre spelningar och festivaler. Det huvudsakliga m\u00e5let och motivation \u00e4r att vara ett aktivt band.\r\n\r\nLyssna\r\nSpotify: http:\/\/open.spotify.com\/artist\/1H8nBJwqABJVvxImgy3Ft8\r\nBandcamp: http:\/\/ageofwoe.bandcamp.com\r\n\r\nP\u00e5 n\u00e4tet\r\nhttp:\/\/www.ageofwoe.net\r\nhttp:\/\/www.facebook.com\/ageofwoe\r\nhttp:\/\/www.youtube.com\/ageofwoe ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/f523821b-2633-40a5-a936-c62eb0fb52ac_media_06 RED EYES.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/48afc4d7-5d32-46d7-888d-6c60e29e7c32_media_aow_press_2014_web.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"FU*K","musik":"Rock","place":"Fagersta","text":"FU*K or Fagersta Ukulele* Klubb is a mixture of odd fellows with a common interest. To play rock on ukuleles. The band has been active for 5 years and is playing all around Sweden but has also been playing in Finals and England. After all expenses have been paid the profit are given away to charity. This band plays everything from classic Swedish tunes to classics by Ian Kilmister and Rob Halford.\r\n\r\nFU*K eller Fagersta Ukulele* Klubb \u00e4r ett g\u00e4ng omogna m\u00e4n som spelar allt p\u00e5 Ukulele, fr\u00e5n trallv\u00e4nliga l\u00e5tar av Rune Wallebom till  Ukulele klassiker av k\u00e4nda grupper som Mot\u00f6rhead, Judas Priest, Pink Floyd, Bob Dylan, Neil Young mm.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/19c14fa6-a596-4499-90f2-e0aaea015646_media_FU_K Muren.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/4d424485-1203-41c8-a5e9-2286806b105d_media_\u00f6rebro_KJA7475.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Meadows ever Bleeding","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Efter att ha tackat nej till flera skivkontrakt s\u00e5lde Meadows debutskiva slut p\u00e5 en dryg m\u00e5nad. Men den hann \u00e4nd\u00e5 spridas till USA, Storbritannien, Tyskland, Skandinavien, Asien och Australien. \r\n\r\nBakom namnet Meadows ever Bleeding g\u00f6mmer sig l\u00e5tskrivaren Christoffer Wadensten. Under de senaste \u00e5ren har han turnerat flitigt p\u00e5 festivaler och klubbar, och har hunnit bygga upp en stor publik b\u00e5de i Norden, Europa och USA.  \r\nUnder 2014 och 2015 har Meadows turnerat f\u00f6r fulla hus i Tyskland och i \u00e5r sl\u00e4pps en ny skiva i samband med turn\u00e9er i Storbritannien, Skandinavien, Tyskland, USA och Australien. ********* \r\n\r\n\"Med en r\u00f6st som skulle kunna sm\u00e4lta volfram. [...] Den \u00f6dmjuka men \u00e4nd\u00e5 s\u00e4kra framtoningen bildar en kontakt med publiken som \u00e4r... l\u00e5t oss s\u00e4ga: Fantastisk.\" \r\n~ Nerikes Allehanda, Sverige ******** \r\n\r\n\"In the jungle of the many songwriters, he is an exceptional artist. He just knows how to captivate his audience.\" \r\n~ Oldenburg Internetzeitung, Tyskland ******** \r\n\r\n\"He did everything right. He involved the audience and played his last chords among us, the fans. Close enough to touch and very emotional\"\r\n~ Soundkartell, Germany ******** ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/2ccbe3a3-fd08-42ef-803c-8be65b42655c_media_meb_itsus.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/321e466a-0560-4663-9c2c-d91ef964240c_media_meb_sq_1050.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Maddox Street","musik":"Hard rock","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Maddox Street \u00e4r ett G\u00f6teborgsbaserat band bildat 2011 best\u00e5ende av fyra musiker som framf\u00f6r genuin 60-70-talsrock med influenser fr\u00e5n band som exempelvis Led Zeppelin, Deep Purple, Jimi Hendrix, The Doors och Pink Floyd.\r\n\r\nMed erfarenhet fr\u00e5n att ha vunnit Rockstage \u00e5r 2012 och fr\u00e5n diverse spelningar p\u00e5 G\u00f6teborgsscenen (Sticky Fingers, Pustervik, G\u00f6teborgs Kulturkalas, Jazzhuset, Manifest on Tour 2014 f\u00f6r att n\u00e4mna n\u00e5gra) jobbar Maddox Street f\u00f6r att g\u00f6ra varje livespelning unik genom improvisationsmoment, och att genom sina l\u00e5tar f\u00f6rmedla en k\u00e4nsla som n\u00e5r ut \u00f6ver scenkanten.\r\n\r\nS\u00e4ttningen best\u00e5r av gitarr\/s\u00e5ng, trummor, bas och orgel. Den 15 juni 2015 sl\u00e4pptes det sj\u00e4lvbetitlade debutalbumet via Berno Records genom ett samarbete med den meriterade producenten Berno Paulsson och finns att lyssna p\u00e5 h\u00e4r: \r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/open.spotify.com\/album\/0WRfl4HDL39XPioUlJ2Fft\r\n\r\nF\u00f6r mer information, f\u00f6lj Maddox Street p\u00e5 facebook:\r\nhttps:\/\/www.facebook.com\/maddoxstreet.swe\/","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/f225a394-ffa5-4979-949e-4da0f47b1fe3_media_You Had it Coming.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/25b3c637-7cd0-434a-9da6-224182a67e34_media_Maddoxstreetrep.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"East of Mars","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"Write a short presentation of your band here.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/33b5a7b9-f619-43b9-9266-b49430c064a3_media_E of M Wonderboat short.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/10a99272-ee84-4afb-b2bd-ba4f878b00b5_media_East of Mars (Hanna).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Thalamus","musik":"Hard rock","place":"Borl\u00e4nge","text":"Thalamus has been around for quite some time now, 2006 was the starting point for us. In 2007 we released our debut album and we did a re-release of the album 2015 with 8 bonus tracks. In 2011 Thalamus released Subterfuge that made it into the nr.6 spot on the Swedish sales chart. We followed up the release with gigs at Sweden rock festival, Peace & Love festival, Getaway rock festival and Rockstad:Falun. In 2013 we released Soul, the third album, an album that incorporated some soul and progressive elements. Now we are working on our next album and are taking a break to come to Live at Heart for the 4th time. Get ready to rock! we're coming with some new material!","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/7d1da830-89dd-48bb-8fdd-21ccb3b876ee_media_02 Thalamus_BruisedAndBrokenBoned-mstr.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/72189b88-4af2-486c-96eb-fcf86a8be122_media_196468_609313959092945_1858172500_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Broken Chakra","musik":"Hardcore","place":"London","text":"In late 2010 Jon put out a call for like minded musicians to join him and form a Rap \/ Rock Fusion band. It was Christian Bailey (Bass) Rolen Brandy (Drums) and Luke Morgan (Guitar) who answered that call and Broken Chakra was formed.\r\nMeeting in a studio based in London Bridge the band began to form their unique fusion of original music. \r\n\r\nBy 2013 Broken Chakra had been moving around the scene building up a fan base wherever they could. It was then the band started recording the EP Fractured which was released via the Jon Kennedy Federation and Sony Worldwide digital release distribution.\r\nDuring the Summer of 2014 Broken Chakra departed with Rolen Brandy and by mutual contacts found Oz Hassan who had come off a European tour with The Dirty Rich a few months earlier.\r\n\r\nWith Broken Chakra going from strength to strength the band got to work with new drummer Oz and started writing new material. They headed over to Pyramid Studios where they recorded the upcoming EP Circle of Truth which was Mixed, Mastered and Engineered by Dave Pemberton.\r\n\r\nSoon after the recording of the Circle of Truth EP and before its release on 11th September 2015 Broken Chakra underwent another change to the line-up, this time parting with guitarist Luke Morgan.\r\n\r\nWith the departure of Luke, it left the band needing a guitarist quick. It was then Oz called in his cousin Yusuf of female fronted metal band Nothing Gained who were currently on hiatus to pick up the guitar duties.\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/5c49b60b-4a62-4b42-9ffb-5345d0f7d724_media_Vipers Nest.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/47586cc8-657f-41e6-98cd-cb7c1f94aaff_media_11194652_379265952264398_7404114489396259609_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Summer Crowd Stereo","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Hamburg","text":"Summer Crowd Stereo is a sensitive songwriter, bearded poet and haunting singer. His songs take no detours. They aim for where it hurts the most beautifully: Right for the heart. That is what puts them into the tradition of the likes of Nick Drake or Elliott Smith.\r\nLoFi-Indie-Acoustic \u2013 that is what the Hamburg-based artist calls his music. Stripped down to its very basics his music totally focuses on the song. And, of course, the intriguing atmosphere he creates on stage: Pure sound. Pure emotion. Pure excitement.  \r\nSummer Crowd Stereo has shared the stage with the likes of Built to Spill, Timesbold, Bj\u00f6rn Kleinhenz, Thomas Dybdahl or Emily Jane White. He finds himself on a \u201cnever-ending-tour\u201d that has made him a very welcome, regular guest in many clubs throughout Germany and Europe.\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/563a2293-f10b-4aa5-b993-6a7db68a28ed_media_Summer Crowd Stereo - On the road again.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/35506534-6567-426d-8a29-aa0504a459de_media_Summer Crowd Stereo Picture large.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Carl Ewerth","musik":"Cabaret","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Stj\u00e4rnan som jag f\u00f6ddes under heter s\u00e5ng, och som den stj\u00e4rna jag nu tror att jag \u00e4r, sitter jag ofta i mitt luftslott och dricker drinkar av hembr\u00e4nt, l\u00f6gn och sanning.\r\nAlldeles sant \u00e4r att jag \u00e4r uppv\u00e4xt i den v\u00e4rml\u00e4ndska mytologin. Av Zarah Leander \u00e4rvde jag mina st\u00e4mband, Fr\u00f6dings galenskap tr\u00f6stade n\u00e4r hj\u00e4rtat ville brista och Selma Lagerl\u00f6f l\u00e4rde mig ta till flykten i fantasin.\r\n\r\nNu har jag ber\u00e4ttat allt och ingenting som i en v\u00e4rml\u00e4ndsk skr\u00f6na.\r\n\r\nCarl Ewerth","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e94d805b-fe14-4875-a649-8b4833ae7477_media_Nor nicht das Liebe.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0accdfe4-0edf-4658-a80f-cad4831b6895_media_ich bin ein star!.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Switchback","musik":"Americana","place":"Griffith","text":"Brian FitzGerald and Martin McCormack of Switchback have been playing their brand of Americana music for over twenty years. Brian and Martin play an exciting mix of mandolin, guitar, and bass. Their harmonies have won them comparisons to famous duos such as the Everly Brothers and Simon and Garfunkel. Music Connection Magazine said of Switchback: \"Their vocal prowess is as pure as it is unique...there is no denying the stunning vocal blends that are achieved by this duo.\"\r\n\r\nSwitchback provides a unique and exciting Americana show featuring many original songs with a distinct Celtic influence. Their concerts appeal to a wide range of audiences.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/78f12691-2e7e-4400-a63f-965c1705fb97_media_06 The Fire That Burns.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/03552f75-f1c3-4e1c-8ca4-d3bf6b321c1a_media_switchback_0183-v.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Tjikko","musik":"Hard rock","place":"\u00d6rebro\/Stockholm","text":"Tjikko is a fuse between Muse and Foo Fighters. A power-trio delivering heavy riffs, strong melodies and pumping crescendos! \r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/0908fdd5-dff5-4255-a0a8-6797fd292960_media_Allergic.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a90e2196-a043-4dd5-b11d-3fc210f4b72c_media_Tjikko(band+logga)(m).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Anni Kannika","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Stockholm","text":"Anni Kannika is an independent artist and singer\/songwriter based in Stockholm and Los Angeles.\r\n\r\nInspired by the wild nature she grew up in, her music is organic and truthful. She brings a unique flare to the singer- songwriter tradition by blending heartfelt vulnerability with the power of blues and rock. Her emotional vocals and blue mood takes you back to the old days of folk and rock music.\r\n\r\nIn 2013 Anni released a live EP titled \"Blue Heart\" recorded at the legendary EastWest Studios in Los Angeles. The EP was entirely funded by her fans through her indiegogo campaign.\r\n\r\nShe is currently recording her second EP titled \u201cInto The Dark\u201d with British producer Warren Huart (The Fray, Aerosmith, James Blunt) at Spitfire Studio in Laurel Canyon, LA.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/67cd7b2f-c85c-4cac-b8cf-a90b25fa5a17_media_Anni Kannika - Run Like A Man .mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5b902f8e-fccc-4094-8f7c-889af99d977e_media_27_DSC7324.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Grande Royale","musik":"Rock","place":"J\u00f6nk\u00f6ping","text":"Grande Royale \u2013 Swedens new Royalty\r\n\r\nHailing from the dark forests of southern Sweden Grande Royale emerges to deliver hard-hitting Rock  n\u00b4 Roll with face-melting riffs and an attitude spawned from Satan himself. With influneces rooted in the early seventies, mixed with heavy blues guitar licks, Grande Royale paves their music straight and hard like an interstate highway. \r\n\r\nGrande Royale is a garage rock n' roll band, started by Andy in the early 2013.\r\nThe band was originally started as a project by members of 3 different bands with the intent to fool around, write music and drink beer. Andy presented some old material that was modified to fit the band. Hampus, Gustav and Anton continued writing more material and it all resulted in an album. \r\nDuring this period, the result seemed so compelling that the Grande Royale decided to continue with the band but on a more serious level, still writing simple rock n' roll and enjoy having a great time.\r\nGrande Royale has replaced Anton with Marcus on drums and Hampus has gone from bass and lead vocals to only lead vocals. Calle has joined the band on bass to get Grande Royale a more groovy sound.\r\nAfter the success release of their debut album Cigne Noir the band will release their second album No Fuss in August 2015. \r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6b8e6247-361d-4ccf-938f-058c6b54303c_media_1 Shout it out.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/4bfb2e5a-9699-45ca-a904-6861e74f8c90_media_framsida.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Mohlavyr","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Mohlavyr - \u201dExperimentell akustisk pop i det f\u00e4ngslande gr\u00e4nslandet mellan fantasi och verklighet. Gripande l\u00e5ttexter och nyskapande arrangemang.\u201d\r\n\r\nAktiv sedan 2009 har Mohlavyr sl\u00e4ppt flera alster, producerat egna musikteaterf\u00f6rest\u00e4llningar, musikvideos, konstutst\u00e4llningar, turn\u00e9rat i Tyskland och Sverige och agerat f\u00f6rband till bland andra Lars Demian, Kajsa Grytt och Mikael Wiehe. I h\u00f6st \u00e4r hon aktuell med sitt andra album, ett full\u00e4ngdsalbum med l\u00e5tar p\u00e5 svenska som s\u00e4gs vara som att tjuvl\u00e4sa Mohlavyrs dagbok\u2026 Officiell release 25 september!\r\n\r\nMohlavyr musikvideo \"Krympta dr\u00f6mmar\": https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=qZfpb-OMEz0\r\n\r\nwww.mohlavyr.se","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ba243c1f-ce49-4d93-8db7-ff3ed7205b47_media_Mohlavyr - Krympta dr\u00f6mmar(192kbit).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/43fa2492-9d67-4260-ac69-26093c630996_media_Mohlavyr_profil_omslag.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Alyssa Jacey","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Nashville","text":"Solo! Internationally touring and local recording artist Alyssa Jacey plays acoustic guitar like a percussion instrument, therefore with her powerful yet airy voice accompanied by a rhythmic style on guitar that's all her own, she's a one woman band who you can't seem to keep your eyes off of. An extremely captivating performer (Nominated for last years 2013 Nashville Independent Music Awards for \"Best Live (Country) Performer,\" and has opened for Bruno Mars, Lisa Loeb, Shawn Colvin and more) she'll make you laugh with her witty sarcasm yet equally charming banter between songs just as much as she'll keep you focused on her voice and lyrics while singing. An amazing artist who only has great things for her future, including her 8th album release, \"Heart Breathe\" out on iTunes this Fall. Check out all seven of her self-released albums on iTunes and follow her on other sites like Facebook\/AlyssaJaceyMusic, Twitter @AlyssaJacey, Instagram @AlyssaJaceyMusic, Reverbnation\/AlyssaJacey, Pandora, Spotify and YouTube!","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e175c090-24f7-4a9a-889b-4c06f790aa71_media_02 Drowning Me mp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/506ea5bf-482c-471f-aa44-ceb1344b46b9_media_AlyssaJaceyListeningRoomCafeMarch2015.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Maria Leck","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Mockfj\u00e4rd","text":"Maria Leck \u00e4r en 23-\u00e5rig l\u00e5tskrivare och artist fr\u00e5n Dalarna. Senast aktuell som pristagare av P4:s specialnominering \"\u00c5rets Nykomling\" p\u00e5 Dalecarlia Music Awards 2015.\r\n\r\nDebutalbumet \u201dThe Big Storm\u201d sl\u00e4pptes under den egna labeln FLOSES den 1 September 2014, och har hittills f\u00e5tt fin respons av pressen;\r\n\r\n \u201dDet \u00e4r en mogen debut, i ordets b\u00e4sta bem\u00e4rkelse. Inte mogen, som i m\u00e4tt och d\u00e4st, utan som i att veta hur man ska \u00e5stadkomma det man vill. \/\u2026\/ Maria Leck har mutat in sitt eget h\u00f6rn i pianopopen. Tyngdpunkten ligger p\u00e5 s\u00e5ng och piano, men ibland smyger sig ytterligare instrument in. \/\u2026\/ Hon lyckas ofta hitta dynamiken i det lilla.\u201d  DT \u2013 2014-09-10\r\n\r\nLyssna h\u00e4r:\r\nhttps:\/\/open.spotify.com\/album\/3PdYvJtBVdTDuKDN7c6y8B","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/eee53eb2-7212-468b-922f-abe9e6a4bc95_media_04 BLACK EXPECTATIONS.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/7d807463-afe7-4ccf-b3b7-f77523345373_media_vind\u00f6 press mic.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Magnettes","musik":"Pop","place":"Pajala","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/52113cd8-8a86-4c62-bbfc-eebb82abc971_media_Bones Demo 150413.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/ec6b394d-57f0-42fc-909f-79671fd7774a_media_IMG_7363.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Wilhelm Blixt","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/38bc54a6-d39c-4ff4-93d5-36fc51d7e966_media_Wilhelm_Blixt_-_Carcrash.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5d9b9d6c-12c2-4381-87ea-6df6faaa63db_media_wilhelmblixt_gronland.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Bert Deivert & Copperhead Run","musik":"Blues","place":"Karlstad","text":"Bert Deivert & Copperhead Run (US\/SWE) This band merges juke joint blues, roots, and americana into an exciting new brew! Award-winning American blues mandolinist Bert Deivert has been performing for 41 years in 23 countries around the world, and recently released his 12th album, together with Copperhead Run, featuring some of the finest musicians on Sweden\u2019s vibrant blues scene. This summer's festivals find them in Ireland, Denmark, Holland and Sweden. \r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/86c599b0-5f94-47ee-a6d9-64ede7a70674_media_01 Baby Please Don\u2019t Go.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/269a7764-eeef-485d-af9f-b92e263760e0_media_300DPI BERT DEIVERT_Copperhead RUN color PROMO.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Trigger Gospel","musik":"Country","place":"Chicago","text":"Write a short presentation of your band here.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6e1b36af-6b63-41dc-972c-6af6eea489bf_media_04 Romance.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/7b1cc1af-4e1f-47c0-b133-6e50ae47371f_media_TG-BW-boxing.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"MAGNUSON","musik":"Rock","place":"Los Angeles","text":"MAGNUSON produces the the most musical mayhem ever created by a girl and a boy. Comprised of Los Angeles residents Greg and Kyrsten Magnuson, this dynamic duo switches off on drums and guitar all while maintaining beautifully intricate harmonies. Combining the sounds of Death From Above 1979, The Smiths, Black Sabbath, Muse and Porcupine Tree, Magnuson brings a unique blend of progressive rock, classic metal, and 90\u2019s alt rock to the music scene.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/a9023674-1b82-4d2b-aaa7-dd093b559008_media_03 BaAl.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/158bb347-a49d-443a-a2ed-fdda1687dd76_media_IMG_0004.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"HEYRA","musik":"Rock","place":"Stockholm","text":"Honest, vibrant clear and grand are the words that best describe the sound of HEYRA\u2019s slow rock. Beneath the influences of psychedelia, mellow rock and mystery lies the barren blues of the pale scandinavian winter.\r\n\r\nBehind HEYRA is Stockholm based songwriter\/singer\/guitarist Lovisa Hellsten, with guitarist Johan \u00d6sterg\u00e5rd, bassist Samuel Nilsson and Ola G\u00f6ransson behind the drums.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c9784fef-a3dd-4a70-a7c6-8102bd623a57_media_Dare To Go - demo.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/ca0532cf-010e-49aa-a045-1f65236badc4_media_2014_jan_heyra_1_13.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"A Hope for the Future","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"We are a 7-piece indie pop collective with 3 vocalists, based in Stockholm, Sweden.\r\n\r\nOur influences are of course broad with 7 band members, but we have based our sound around Belle & Sebastian, Fleetwood Mac & Cocteau Twins.\r\n\r\nWe met and formed in late 2013 in Barcelona, Spain and released our first two songs in 2014. We have now released our first 4-track EP \"Catalonia\", with songs based on our experiences of living in Barcelona. We have played on venues in Stockholm and music festivals in Sweden.\r\n\r\nHave a listen to our tunes below:\r\n\r\nSoundcloud: http:\/\/bit.ly\/SNDCLD-AHFTF\r\n\r\nSpotify: http:\/\/spoti.fi\/1PkRSpX\r\n\r\nFacebook: http:\/\/bit.ly\/FB-AHFTF","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/05a6523c-3456-4add-83b7-e6dd6be66f89_media_Loaded Heart.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/07defbb2-8692-41e5-a7c6-f27efb3d6a39_media_ahopeforthefuture2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Maskin","musik":"Rock","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Maskin plays a heavy galactic fuzz rock with a lot of gasoline.\r\n\r\nLast fall the debut album \"Storm\" was released. It's 8 songs spanning over 44 minutes and one hell of a ride!\r\n\r\nOn stage, Maskin is always a matter of energy, heaviness and love for the fuzz of rock.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/0002ed27-f332-4971-a614-b3cbcb26e650_media_07 screecher 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/2845a036-fa74-497a-97d7-17c1ab1a248b_media_14250_952583678090958_3738108053569586491_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"My heart is a metronome","musik":"Rock","place":"UPPSALA","text":"After earning the title as \"Sweden's best unsigned band\" in a national radio competition, My heart is a metronome became a band hard to ignore. Their debut-single \"The Whistler\" was a breath of fresh air for a Swedish music scene that for long had been dominated by electronic elements.\r\n\r\nRadio airplay was followed by a performance on national television (\"Musikhj\u00e4lpen\") and a praised gig at Sweden's biggest showcase festival \"Where's the music?\". Their follow-up single \"Turtle\" was released after signing with indie-label Substitute Music Group and My heart is a metronome's unique sound now got some well-earned attention overseas, receiving indie blog-praise throughout Europe and even landing airplay on French radio. The release was supported by a 10 day UK tour.\r\n\r\nNow the trio is back with their third single \"Feel > Think\" which was released on June 16th, a song that generated over 20 000 plays along with more than 200 shares through it's facebook-announcement - in just a couple of days. ||| \r\n\r\n\r\nOfficial website: www.mhiam.com ||| \r\nFacebook: www.facebook.com\/myheartisametronome ||| \r\nContact: myheartisametronome@gmail.com \/\/ +46730467800 ||| \r\nSpotify: https:\/\/open.spotify.com\/artist\/4aaBqtuCgkgQce4h3lZKDc","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/25ed7dbb-1847-42f5-b5ca-2d678f5f0714_media_01 - My heart is a metronome - Feel Think.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/2dfd5f78-6b9b-48b5-9f71-ccaeedd750f6_media_mhiam_promo1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Dan-Erik Sahlberg","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"\u201dLate bloomers\u201d brukar man kalla konstn\u00e4rer som debuterar i mogen \u00e5lder. Men \u00e4ven om S\u00e5nger fr\u00e5n andra sidan \u00e4r Dan-Erik Sahlbergs debut som soloartist \u00e4r det ingen musikalisk duvunge som sl\u00e4pper en skiva. Han har ett musikaliskt f\u00f6rflutet som keybordist och s\u00e5ngare med band som Hoppets Horisont, Terranova och spelade i m\u00e5nga \u00e5r tillsammans med Bengt Johansson. Som fl\u00f6jtiskt har han ocks\u00e5 spelat allt fr\u00e5n folkmusik till klassiskt och anlitats i m\u00e5nga sammanhang. Under m\u00e5nga \u00e5r har musiken f\u00e5tt st\u00e5 i bakgrunden f\u00f6r en framg\u00e5ngsrik karri\u00e4r som f\u00f6rl\u00e4ggare och projektledare i gr\u00e4nslandet mellan kyrka, kultur och samh\u00e4lle. F\u00f6r n\u00e4rvarande \u00e4r han programchef p\u00e5 Sigtunastiftelsen. Han bor i \u00d6rebro med sin familj.\r\nMen en sv\u00e5r infektion f\u00f6r n\u00e5gra \u00e5r sedan, som s\u00e5n\u00e4r hade kostat honom livet, blev startskottet f\u00f6r den kreativa process och musikaliska nystarten som nu resulterar i albumet S\u00e5nger fr\u00e5n andra sidan. I processen som f\u00f6ljde av att bokstavligen varit i \u201dd\u00f6dens v\u00e4ntrum\u201d kom musiken och s\u00e5ngerna starkt tillbaka i hans liv. \r\n- Jag f\u00f6rstod att jag m\u00e5ste st\u00e4lla in den inre kompassrikningen igen, ta tillvara p\u00e5 livet och g\u00f6ra \u201dr\u00e4tt\u201d saker i forts\u00e4ttningen och d\u00e5 var det som om musiken och texterna b\u00f6rjade fl\u00f6da fram inifr\u00e5n, ber\u00e4ttar han.\r\nHan best\u00e4mde sig ocks\u00e5 f\u00f6r att f\u00f6rverkliga en gammal dr\u00f6m om att l\u00e4ra sig spela gitarr och med det \u201dnya\u201d instrumentet i h\u00e4nderna kom s\u00e5nger och texter, reflektioner \u00f6ver de stora existentiella fr\u00e5gorna om livet, d\u00f6den, tron och k\u00e4rleken. P\u00e5 de flesta s\u00e5ngerna p\u00e5 skivan \u00e4r b\u00e5de text och musik skrivna av Dan-Erik men h\u00e4r finns \u00e4ven s\u00e5nger d\u00e4r han samarbetat med Maria K\u00fcchen, Martin L\u00f6nnebo och G\u00f6ran Sahlberg.  \r\nNu har Dan-Erik Sahlberg samlat en del av de s\u00e5nger han skrivit de senaste \u00e5ren, och tillsammans med Christoffer Wadensten (Meadows ever Bleeding) och ett g\u00e4ng rutinerade musikerv\u00e4nner spelat in dem p\u00e5 albumet S\u00e5nger fr\u00e5n andra sidan.\r\n- Titeln p\u00e5 albumet \u00e4r dubbeltydigt men syftar f\u00f6r mig p\u00e5 \u201dden andra sidan\u201d sjukdomen. Allt detta \u2013 l\u00e5tskrivandet och den musikaliska nystarten \u2013 hade f\u00f6rmodligen inte h\u00e4nt om det inte vore f\u00f6r att jag fick en ny chans att b\u00f6rja om igen, s\u00e4ger han.\r\nMan kan i Dan-Erik Sahlbergs musik h\u00f6ra influenser fr\u00e5n s\u00e5v\u00e4l svenska artister som Tomas Andersson Wij och Peter Le Marc som amerikanska singer-songwriters som Jackson Browne och James Taylor. \r\nMusikalisk lekfullhet och kvalitet i kombination med \u00e4rliga och starka texter om livets sk\u00f6nhet och sk\u00f6rhet \u2013 s\u00e5 skulle man kunna definiera S\u00e5nger fr\u00e5n andra sidan och Dan-Erik Sahlbergs musik.\r\n\r\nS\u00e5nger fr\u00e5n andra sidan - Sl\u00e4pps p\u00e5 CD och digitalt 21 augusti 2015 p\u00e5 David Media (DAVCD109)\r\nProducerad av Dan-Erik Sahlberg och Christoffer Wadensten\r\nInspelad och mixad av Christoffer Wadensten, Jymden Studio\r\nMastrad av Markus Nordlund, Dromedar Studio\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/1029a3f5-3ad2-4e18-ac5d-ece5b85be79e_media_DES_v\u00e5rs\u00e5ng.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5f3f6a52-387b-4374-86eb-bcf56832e919_media_danne7.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"One Step","musik":"Reggae","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"One Step is a reggae band from \u00d6rebro, Sweden\r\nThe band was formed in 2003 by guitar player Sunil Panawennage, keyboard- and trumpet player Mats Str\u00f6mberg, guitar player and singer Bo Cobra E-son, bass player Richard Sj\u00f6gren, drummer Henrik Jansson and saxophone player Jan Nirving, and has been playing different styles of reggae Music, for example instrumental traditional jamaican reggae and jamaican covers, african reggae with the great singer Laurent \"Bob Lau\" Walugaja (CD album One Love 2010), \r\nSwedish reggae with singers like Angelika Jeweren (2003-2008), John Bark (2005-2008), Cassandra Rinaldo (2012-), Elias Gustavsson (2014-), Marcus Pettersson (2014-), in 2014 One Step toured and recorded with the legendary jamaican singer and composer Naggo Dolphin Morris (2014- CD album Music Universal, planned to be released in 2015)\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e350c513-0449-49b2-b77c-90f77637ece6_media_1_8 A train on a track in a song V3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/87332e99-5bf8-427f-8e7b-6d924b1b4c83_media_One Step i Fjugesta 2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"King Albatross","musik":"Hard rock","place":"Borl\u00e4nge","text":"Born in the deep dark forest of the northern parts of sweden, four musicians formed King Albatross. King Albatross is a heavy energetic rockband with its roots in old-fashioned rock music. Last year they released a four song long EP who got featured in the swedish radiostation P3. They are curently working on their debut album called \"King Albatross\"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ba0f441e-a774-4252-b72c-38004574df5e_media_King Albatross - Let them wolves out (AlbaLive2014).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/43cf2255-d409-4da9-8859-43d15eb0b7c2_media_KingA_02_FB.SM.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Julia & The Basement Tapes","musik":"Blues","place":"Stockholm","text":"Julia & The Basement Tapes were formed in the end of 2012 when Julia Tingl\u00f6f (vocal) and Johan Borgh (guitar) had been writing songs together for a while and decided it was time to start a band. The best rhythm section available was contacted, consisting of Samuel S\u00f6derberg on bass and Johannes Sidenqvist on drums. The newly formed band participated in the band contest Spinnrocken, which they won. Shortly after that they recorded their EP \"The Basement Sessions\" with the help of producer Andreas Rydman. The EP was released in the end of May 2013.\r\n\r\nIn June 2013, they played a gig at an outdoor blues event with more than a thousand people in the audience, together with some of Swedens finest blues acts Clas Yngstr\u00f6m, Sven Zetterberg and Mats Ronander.\r\n\r\nThey have also gotten a lot of positive reviews from blogs around the world and their music have been played on several radio stations in Sweden, UK and the USA among others. The band is currently playing live shows and writing songs for their next release.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/835395bb-4122-4121-8545-bab4e4983a32_media_04 Crossroads.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a36ddf4c-0814-439e-a010-1f815715a218_media_1546379_554767894627778_3395626922005135306_n (1).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Magda Andersson","musik":"Visa","place":"Ume\u00e5","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/2086fee6-5e10-4893-adf9-eb720f9038cb_media_Kullersten.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5bfbb940-6585-47c2-9397-838ac1fb2b20_media_Pressbild-Korsa-gr\u00e4nser-1024-659x1024.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Ladida","musik":"Punk","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Ladida charmerar och provocerar med sin kaxiga garagepunk och galna liveshower. Bandet bildades 2009 och har under denna period sl\u00e4ppt en platta, flertalet singlar samt turnerat flitigt i Sverige, Spanien, UK, Tyskland och Dannmark. \r\nUnder v\u00e5ren 2015 har bandet haft flera singlar i rotation p\u00e5 radiostationer i Sverige och toppat flera radiolistor. Bandet har \u00e4ven f\u00e5tt med en l\u00e5t i en v\u00e4rldsomspinnande reklamfilm f\u00f6r makeup f\u00f6retaget Rimmel London, starring Mick Jaggers dotter, Georgia May Jagger. \r\nLadida har hypats av flertalet bloggar och musiktidningar v\u00e4rlden \u00f6ver och paralleller dras ofta till Yeah Yeah yeahs och tidiga Blondie:\r\n \r\n\u201cLaDIDas\u2019 sound may be the wildest, most unhinged I\u2019ve heard in recent memory.....Still at its heart is a proudly sexual narrator, who fearlessly gets what she wants, like a hunter. It\u2019s badass and sexy as hell\u201d\r\nWilliam Ruben Helms - Joy of Violent Movement Blog\r\n \r\n\u201cWith some great write ups, a commercial ad on the horizon and radio airplay, its easy to see why theyre getting so much attention.\u201d\r\nNordic Music Review - Nordic Music Review Blog\r\n \r\n\u201cBouncing, twitchy, rock n vamp, Doo-Wop New Wave from this Gothenburg-based polished-punk four-piece.\u201d \u2026\u201dwhen baby-doll punk, Bea LaDiDa, fires it up between her demonic grins, you can't help but shake, shake, shake and pogo 'til your Blondie wig falls off.\u201d\r\nJim - Getting Near Dawn\r\n \r\n\u201cAll the way from Sweden come Ladida! This Dadaist influenced band from Gothenburg Sweden produces songs that play with contrasting themes and music to produce something unique. Their versatility extends with such instruments as the Melodica, Stylophone, and Saw. It never feels forced and once heard you can\u2019t imagine then songs without those instruments. (Podcast link)\u201d \r\nUnclaimed Bands \r\n\u201cFor the first time in many years I found myself doing some exercise with the first cup of coffee of the day as the need to pogo overwhelmed the need for caffeine.... What a great start to the day.... The raw bleeding edges are exactly what LaDiDa are about.\u201d\r\nTim - Emerging Indie Bands blog\r\n\r\n\u201cHonestly, The LaDiDas sound like a Yeah Yeah Yeahs version of Blondie and - let's cross your heart and be honest - we've been waiting for this! Blondie is too mainstream and Yeah Yeah Yeahs tend to be overcomplicated. This quartet from Gothenburg makes excessive Pop tunes like \"Dance\" which makes you either want to randomly destroy things or dance like there's no tomorrow. \u201c\r\nReeperbahn Festival\r\n\u201cYou could say that they are a little like Shangri La's would be if they rehearsed in Joseph Fritzls Cellar\u201d\r\nG\u00f6teborg Nonstop\r\n\u201cFemme fronted Swede garage punkers with really witty\/silly lyrics\u201d \u201c...it's like The Yeah Yeah Yeahs meets X Ray Spex via Liliput and really early Blondie...yeah, great stuff. Punktastic. \u201c\r\nBugbear, London\r\n\u201cThe LaDiDas offer up playful and energetic punkpop. I suspect that the group, with the charismatic singer Bea at the fore, on a good evening can be sensational live. I hope we get more opportunities to see them soon!\u201d \r\nGaffa\r\n \r\n\u201cLaDiDas are a band that should be experienced live to really get the full experience\u201d \u201c..the singer Bea\u2019s voice takes the listener on a journey like an Alice in Wonderland for grown-ups, from sugar-sweet to the raw energy that borders on manic cockiness.\u201d \r\nMarita Isaksson - Kombi (Swedish music industry trade magazine)\r\n \r\n ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/3cfc835e-9b68-49ff-ab9d-788cb7dbbb22_media_Ladida - I want it master.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/e9ea394d-ef4a-49c5-896d-708640265836_media_LADiDA press photo.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Mathilda Wahlstedt","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Mathilda is a singer\/songwriter from sweden. She writes her own songs and plays usually by her self.\r\nNow she is up on the stage with new musicians to help her express her music in new ways.\r\nMathilda would describe her music as indie\/folk with a touch of other genres.\r\n\r\n-\r\nLive At Heart 2014\r\n\"Men \u00e5 andra sidan \u00e4r den 19-\u00e5riga Mathilda Wahlstedt en osedvanligt talangfull singer\/songwriter som har gr\u00e4nsl\u00f6sa f\u00f6ruts\u00e4ttningar att v\u00e4xa in i rollen som fullfj\u00e4drad artist.\" H\u00e5kan Pettersson, Nerikes Allehanda, 6 september 2014","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/faa718a6-ef49-4e58-84c4-ec82c96ccb96_media_01 Vid en blom\u00c3\u20acng.sp 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0e6945f1-e883-40d9-b5a9-082f5d120844_media_IMG_5306 (1).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Whaleheart","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Indie rock\/pop band that has been playing together for approx. a year.\r\nReleased debut EP in February, it is available on Spotify, iTunes and Bandcamp.\r\nCurrently writing material for a new EP.\r\n\r\nIndierock\/pop-band som har spelat tillsammans i ca ett \u00e5r. Sl\u00e4ppte precis v\u00e5r debut-EP som finns uppe p\u00e5 Spotify och vi jobbar just nu p\u00e5 uppf\u00f6ljaren. Har ett par spelningar i bagaget ocks\u00e5, liveklipp fr\u00e5n dessa finns p\u00e5 Facebook.\r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/www.facebook.com\/whaleheartband\r\nhttp:\/\/whaleheart.bandcamp.com\/\r\nhttps:\/\/open.spotify.com\/album\/7vQfEiz3qXzfDuTk5pQbqk","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/789808e6-dc22-4a96-867b-40534d3a9124_media_Rocket Science.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/9250f525-590e-4c72-b1b1-7c51a4016946_media_11043348_337479276457467_5863836428167436454_o.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Bagari-Hayes Project","musik":"Country","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"The Bagari-Hayes Project is a band whose music and lyrics is said by many listeners to remind them of works from some of the musical greats from the sixties, seventies and early eighties. The band's sound is very much its own however and is equally fresh and modern as it may be retrospective. The Bagari-Hayes Project's material is completely original and is definitely on a par with any of the established acoustic ensembles on the music scene at present...   ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/2e2953a9-5faf-4554-be50-39896bf4a569_media_Three Bananas.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/b4ecc94f-a805-4ed5-9147-8273141fa039_media_TBHP-press.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Jonatan Lindner & Kapellet","musik":"Pop","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Snart 30-a\u030ariga Jonatan Lindner bo\u0308rjade sin musikaliska karria\u0308r som frontman i This Morning Orchestra - ett talangfullt O\u0308rebroband som med vemodig akustisk musik stack ut bland ma\u0308ngden punkrock i O\u0308rebro i bo\u0308rjan av 2000. Innan orkestern lade ner sa\u030a hann de med att spela live i SVT's sto\u0308rsta ungdomsprogram och Arvikafestivalen - framga\u030angar som gav ett fo\u0308rlagskontrakt fo\u0308r den da\u030a tona\u030arige talangfulle la\u030atskrivaren.\r\n\r\nFo\u0308rlagskontraktet fo\u0308rvandlades snart till ka\u0308nslan av att vara a\u030asidosatt, vilket i sin tur ledde till att Jonatan sja\u0308lv ville ta sig ur kontraktet fo\u0308r att fa\u030a tillbaka inspirationen till att skriva musik- na\u030agot som skulle dro\u0308ja flera a\u030ar.\r\n\r\n2008 do\u0308k han a\u030aterigen upp pa\u030a riktigt. Dels som a\u030arets lokalartist pa\u030a den a\u030arligt TV- sa\u0308nda O Helga Natt-konserten i O\u0308rebro, dels genom en nyutgiven engelskspra\u030akig singel tillsammans med nya kompbandet \"The Chapel\". Ja\u0308mfo\u0308relserna med Kristofer A\u030astro\u0308m och Christian Kjellvander var snabbt ett faktum. Jona & The Chapel gjorde sedan ett antal liveframtra\u0308danden i SVT under 2009\/10.\r\n\r\nDe senaste 3 a\u030aren har Jona & The Chapel fo\u0308rvandlats till Jonatan Lindner & Kapellet och da\u0308rmed a\u0308ven blivit svenskspra\u030akiga. Jonatan har, ba\u030ade solo och med kapell, sta\u030att som support till svenskspra\u030akiga storheter som Janne Schaffer och Anna Stadling och da\u0308r ocksa\u030a hittat sin egen publik.\r\n\r\n30 januari 2015 sla\u0308pps sa\u030aledes debut-EP:n pa\u030a svenska - Med namnet \"Skuggspel\" inneha\u030aller den 5 la\u030atar som erbjuder vackra melodier med tra\u0308ffsa\u0308kra och efterta\u0308nksamma texter som definitivt drar paralleller till sa\u030ava\u0308l Thomas Andersson Wij som Mauro Scocco.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/0262405f-733f-418f-9c13-c5b5bb795ca6_media_Dr\u00f6mmen om att flyga.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/10a2a307-dced-4e3b-b2d4-877d2c36486a_media_Jonatan Lindner & Kapellet.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Rolf Carlsson Band","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Filipstad","text":"Rolf Carlsson firar 30-\u00e5rsjubileum som artist 2015 och i h\u00f6st kommer ett nytt album. Skivan \u00e4r inspelad tillsammans med delvis nya bandet, och singeln \"Goda m\u00e4nskor\" sl\u00e4pptes den 15 maj.\r\nMusiken - hans egna l\u00e5tar p\u00e5 svenska - r\u00f6r sig i gr\u00e4nslandet mellan rock, pop, soul och visa.\r\nF\u00f6rsta helt egna plattan kom 1997 och deltagandet i Melodifestivalen 2002 med balladen \"Tidig \u00e4r tiden\" innebar ett publikt genombrott som artist och l\u00e5tskrivare. Singlarna \"N\u00e4r t\u00e5gen g\u00e5r f\u00f6rbi\" och \"Maskrosbarn\" blev radioframg\u00e5ngar 2006\/2007 liksom \"Det \u00e4r du\", en duett med Idde Schultz, fr\u00e5n 2009. Senaste plattan \"Fina dagar\" (2012) breddade publiken och den blev hans hittills st\u00f6rsta skivframg\u00e5ng med bl.a. en f\u00f6rstaplats p\u00e5 Bengans Topp 100.\r\nRolf \u00e4r ocks\u00e5 verksam som f\u00f6rfattare och v\u00e5ren 2015 utkom hans andra roman \"Rosita Bitter\".\r\n\r\nwww.rolfcarlsson.net\r\nwww.facebook.com\/rolfcarlssonofficial\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/368dcd91-8b86-4abb-9d90-fde622c16444_media_Rolf Carlsson - Nittonhundra\u00e5tti.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5c72b54e-adee-42c0-b037-327bf374d255_media_Konsertaffisch_band_2015.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"femishayo afrobeats and the mighty mates","musik":"Reggae","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/a0e8e7cc-38a8-4a08-91f5-be74f0c681e5_media_07 Abuku lo ma kan.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/b75ae181-1428-4318-b7f3-f291ba12b9af_media_femi2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Bellaroush","musik":"Reggae","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"www.bellaroush.com\r\nwww.facebook.com\/bellaroush\r\n\r\n\u201cBellaroush\u2019s music ranges from emotive soul ballads to engaging, energy-laden uptempo hits, deeply rooted in reggae with an edge of electronica and hip-hop. The seven-piece band features no less than four singers whose powerful harmonies deliver hard-hitting lyrics about strength, weakness, love, solidarity, protest and revolution.\"\r\n\r\nBiography\r\nBellaroush was formed in 2009 mainly by lead vocalists Magnus Hagstr\u00f6m and Moa Jonsson L\u00e4nne who has been the creative leaders ever since. The band released their first EP \u201cGetting There\u201d in 2011 and it was followed by the EP \u201cFree\u201d in 2013.\r\nDuring 2014, Bellaroush has been working with producer Anders Lagerfors (Pale Honey, Obliq etc) in the making of their first full length release called \u201cB E L L A R O U S H\u201d. In the process, Bellaroush explored ways to challenge the reggae genre and blend the different musical backgrounds of the band members. The result is a non-stereotypical and multifaceted album with a foundation in the backbeat of reggae, although combined with electro beats, hip hop, soul, punk, pop etc.\r\n\r\nThe Swedish rapper Promoe from Looptroop Rockers and the Swedish dancehall artist Etzia are guest appearing on the album which was released by Swedish hip hop and reggae indie label called Swingkids.\r\n\r\nBellaroush has been touring mainly in Sweden and northern Europe, but they\u2019re also planning for their second tour in India.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9b33b0df-b4b9-4289-a9b4-efed7c1f4028_media_Bellaroush - B E L L A R O U S H - 03 Sun Goes Down (128 kbit).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/27d22920-f520-4873-b3c2-ddeae969e190_media_Bellaroush 2014 - photo Tildeh Hjelm.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Bullock Hearts","musik":"Rock","place":"\u00d6rebro\/J\u00f6nk\u00f6ping\/Stockholm","text":"Bullock Hearts started in 2013, and has released three singles. The band came in second place in the Swedish radio competition Svensktoppen N\u00e4sta in 2014, with the song Bells & Whistles. The same song has been played frequently on air in Sweden and was the second most played song on the biggest radio channel in Finland. This summer the band plays festivals in Sweden and Norway. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/809672d5-db26-4400-8080-7e9990988887_media_Bells & Whistles.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/affb0f6d-4931-4f01-a722-053b0a42ca53_media_Bullock Hearts Press 2015.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Evering","musik":"Folk","place":"London","text":"London based Scottish musicians that thrive on delivering strong harmonies laid over powerful yet warm tones, which are governed by intertwined piano and guitar. The combination of Chris and Dawn\u2019s wide ranging influences shines through in Evering's material, which is immediately engaging and superbly memorable.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ce543905-bc14-4df4-b412-813a7846b672_media_1 Running Circles.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/459ffaa9-dd1f-4996-86ef-f78b1dc7014a_media_Pic1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Among Lynx","musik":"Blues","place":"Uppsala","text":"AMONG LYNX (scroll down for english)\r\n\r\nEtt g\u00e4ng rockbohemer har \u00e4ntligen hittat hem. Med djupa r\u00f6tter i blues och soul experimenterar Among Lynx med rockoch American folk d\u00e4r resultatet blir en resa mellan western, urskog och storstadens smutsiga avenyer. Among Lynx r\u00f6r om i den annars v\u00e4ldigt homogena bluesgrytan. N\u00e4r gitarristen Moa Brandt, kontrabasisten Tove Brandt och munspelaren Elin \u00d6berg fr\u00e5n bluestrion Someone You Admire tr\u00e4ffade den f\u00f6re detta s\u00e5ngaren Evami Ringqvist fr\u00e5n h\u00e5rdrocksbandet Thundermother f\u00f6ddes id\u00e9n om ett sv\u00e4ngigt och sp\u00e4nnande band i en liten s\u00e4ttning. Med elektrisk\/akustisk slidegitarr, s\u00e5ng, percussion, bluesmunspel och kontrabas spelar Among Lynx efter devisen tungt, sv\u00e4ngigt och smutsigt.\r\n\r\nENGLISH: \r\nWith roots deeply engrained in soul and blues a gang of rock musicians has found their home. \u201cAmong Lynx\u201d experiments with rock and American folk in a way that takes the listener on a journey through the manifestation of many different roots styles into one. Between western back-roads and the dirty alleyways of cities \u201cAmong Lynx\u201d makes a huge step, sending waves through the otherwise homogeneous and generic sea of \u201cblues.\u201d When guitarist Moa Brandt, doublebass player Tove Brandt and harmonica player Elin \u00d6berg from the former blues trio \u201cSomeone You Admire\u201d met singer Evami Ringqvist from the hard rock band \u201cThundermother\u201d the musical project \u201cAmong Lynx\u201d was formed, giving birth to the idea of raw execution in a swinging and exciting new band. The sound of electric\/acoustic slide guitar, vocals, percussion, blues harmonica and contra bass will not leave you unaffected, that\u2019s for sure.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/69fe974d-e76d-4ee4-9ef7-421ad89143ad_media_A 01 MY TOWN.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0de7812b-c74a-449b-b58f-fb29b7e7dff3_media_Foto: Jakob Brandt.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Oh Hiroshima","musik":"Rock","place":"Kristinehamn","text":"Oh Hiroshima \u00e4r ett postrock\/indiepop-band som bildades i Kristinehamn \u00e5r 2007. Det som f\u00f6rst startade som ett soloprojekt, har med \u00e5ren vuxit till ett fullskaligt band, och 2011 sl\u00e4pptes debutalbumet \u201dResistance is Futile\u201d. Tack vare trogna fans har musiken sedan via forum, bloggar och hemsidor spridit sig \u00f6ver v\u00e4rlden och genererat nya lyssnare p\u00e5 varje v\u00e4rldsdel! \r\n\r\nF\u00f6r n\u00e4rvarande arbetar vi med att slutf\u00f6ra produktionen av v\u00e5rt n\u00e4stkommande album, d\u00e4r vi har tagit flera kliv fram\u00e5t! Melodierna \u00e4r \u00e4n mer sk\u00f6ra, den atmosf\u00e4riska s\u00e5ngen \u00e4n mer framtr\u00e4dande, samtidigt som det har gjorts stort utrymme f\u00f6r tungt emotionella ljudmattor och exploderande crescendon. Sammantaget skapas en dynamisk och f\u00e4ngslande helhet. En liveupplevelse du inte vill missa helt enkelt!","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/dcaadecb-5f47-4db0-bc8b-a3124e84ddce_media_Oh Hiroshima - Renescence.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5ce07c67-3e02-4d9e-b19e-fdfbb054f781_media_ohhiroshima.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Benesser","musik":"Progressive rock","place":"Falun","text":"F\u00f6r tv\u00e5 \u00e5r sen sl\u00e4ppte Benesser det mycket hyllade debutalbumet The Start of Something New, som bl.a blev kallat ett av 2000-talets m\u00e4ktigaste debuter i GAFFA och hyllades av Nicke Borg p\u00e5 Bandit. De spelar ruskigt tight rock med atmosf\u00e4riska, progressiva inslag som k\u00e4nnetecknas av en f\u00e4ngslande atmosf\u00e4r och den dynamik som n\u00e4stan blivit synonymt med Benesser. De \u00e4r ett f\u00f6rtrollande liveband som lirat ihop sen -98 d\u00e5 de b\u00f6rjade som nio\u00e5ringar, n\u00e5got som inte g\u00e5r att missa i det fascinerande, n\u00e4rmast organiska samspelet.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6656d44e-9b28-434e-b285-c86835962f28_media_Benesser - Where O Death 192kbps.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/8430d006-67ef-439c-bbb1-8c3a5fdf9ef6_media_benesser-frizon_RGB.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"JennyC","musik":"Rock","place":"G\u00e4vle","text":"\u201dMy first album \u201dSIGN\u201d, is a summary of my musical brain so far, which needs to be drained\u2026\u201d\r\nS\u00e5 sammanfattar sj\u00e4lv JennyC sin musik. \r\n\r\nDet h\u00f6rs tydliga influenser fr\u00e5n 60- och 70-talet, med en gnutta 80-tal. Melankolisk och rockig; \u00f6verraskande och hoppfull. Det \u00e4r upp till lyssnaren att kategorisera. \r\nJennyC har arbetat i Slowbeat Studio G\u00e4vle, och p\u00e5 Abbey Road Studios London, d\u00e4r producenten Alex sammanfattade \u201dSIGN\u201d med orden: Big epic sound!\r\n\r\nSpotify: Jenny C Sign\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\"My first album,\" SIGN \", is a summary of my musical brain so far , which needs to be drained ... \"\r\nThat\u00b4s how JennyC summarizes her music.\r\n\r\nClear influences from the 60s and 70s , with a touch of the 80s . Melancholic rock music; surprisingly and hopeful. It's up to the listener to decide.\r\nJennyC has worked in Slowbeat Studio G\u00e4vle , and at Abbey Road Studios in London, where the producer Alex summed up \u201dSIGN\u201d with the words : \r\nBig epic sound!","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/f9be187a-d7d5-4a4c-8634-5eb1f7577b95_media_08 Circus.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/d0f087ec-c34d-4535-a6cf-2c9d93f7a8a3_media_backdrop_jennyC2.1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"M & M's Honky Tonk","musik":"Country","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Kickass country in a duo format!\r\nVi kommer i \u00e5r till Live at heart med utvecklat sound, inklusive s\u00e5ng och g\u00e4stande musiker!\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/f630a4bd-8509-4dcc-b985-4e87ad795614_media_Jiffy Jam 192.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/00447af0-d171-439e-87e3-4d49dec23aae_media_M&MsFlyer3.0.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Joybells","musik":"Gospel","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Med ett rykande f\u00e4rskt album i bagaget bjuder Joybells till en h\u00e4rlig gospelkonsert. Joybells har funnits i stort sett lika l\u00e4nge som gospelmusiken funnits i Sverige. Trots att det g\u00e5tt \u00f6ver 50 \u00e5r sedan starten lever musiken \u00e4nnu.  Genom sv\u00e4ngiga medryckande toner och uttrycksfulla, stillsamma b\u00f6ner vill Joybells sprida det goda budskapet. \r\n\r\nJoybells \u00e4r en av Immanuelskyrkans akter. K\u00f6ren leds av Samuel Henning och Rebecka K\u00e4llner.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/328139b0-c832-4471-99ba-198ee0a675fd_media_Lift Him Up (Worthy To Be Praised) Sample.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/b47f4f04-0b2c-493b-9e48-17b10b1386c9_media_Joybells LiveAtHeart.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Dream Lake","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"Dream Lake is the Swedish dream pop duo comprised of the professional dancer and lead vocalist Isabella Sv\u00e4rdstam and multi-instrumentalist and music producer Niklas Willar Lidholm.\r\nTogether they create dreamy, melancholy music.\r\nWith their music they want to create a space where you can escape with your thoughts and dreams.\r\nTheir influences are artists like, Beach House, Fleet Foxes and The XX.\r\n\r\nDream Lake is currently working on their debut album...","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/eca8b9ac-160f-405e-b8ca-bbb1c1e64211_media_01 -  - World Of Dreams_44k_16b 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0d569858-99a3-4f0a-a5fa-6f8fc24f7054_media_DL 1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Atlantic Francis","musik":"Folk","place":"Stockholm","text":"With sincere and honest songwriting and dreamlike folk melodies, Atlantic Francis have a nostalgic beatlesque sound based around the genuine friendship between them.\r\n\r\nConsisting of guitarists Johan Macdonald and Victor Norberg, bassist Jesper Karlsson, and drummer Adrian Lefvert, the band formed in Stockholm, naming itself after the Atlantic Ocean and the mermaid Francis and not after a girl who lives far away in Australia. \r\n\r\nAs best friends, knowing each other from high school, they were busking around in the streets of different cities all over Sweden. Johan, who\u2019s dad took him busking when he was a kid, is the lead singer of Atlantic Francis although all of them handle vocal duties.\r\n\r\nWriting their own songs, they started playing gigs in Sweden, northern Europe and the States. Creating their own loyal fan base. However, where ever they went they couldn\u2019t resist putting out their instruments and start playing for the passing audience right on the streets.  \r\n\r\nThe guys enjoy spending time together, dancing lindyhop, jumping off cliffs and going on festivals. Traveling on their own to other continents is also a big part of the lives of all members of Atlantic Francis. Combining the best of four, Atlantic Francis\u2019 music is a mosaic of different world experiences and individuals. \r\n\r\n\u201cWe don\u2019t take us too serious. On stage, we are true to ourselves and people enjoy that\u201d, says Johan Mc Donald.\r\n\r\nAnd what people remember is the easy confidence the lead singer is able to convey by casually speaking to the audience as if he was speaking to the people watching him play on the streets of Stockholm.\r\n\r\nIn May their debut EP will was released, addressing the ocean and its broad expanses, old love - and the feeling when a girl dumps you. If was well received by for example Gaffa.se and Musikguiden i P3.\r\n\r\nSounds like: Morrissey meets The Beatles, Mumford & Sons and Fleet Foxes\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/be35ad5f-161f-4b87-8a3b-78172831ba18_media_01 Where Do We Run (SE4YR1500101).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/39ff212b-3e9d-4345-afd5-4ce7ac869751_media_AtlanticFrancis foto MatsLefvert4.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"HEADSTONED","musik":"Metal","place":"Kalmar","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/daa3bee0-1662-4cee-a7b9-c86861299611_media_Headstoned - Description.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/ea52e5e3-d22a-4c37-92ec-5b567daec570_media_Headstoned 2015.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Fluru","musik":"Americana","place":"Stockholm","text":"Norrl\u00e4ndskt vemod kombinerat med amerikansk folkmusik. G\u00e5r det? N\u00e4r man h\u00f6r Fluru spela inser man att det g\u00e5r alldeles utm\u00e4rkt. Namnet Fluru betyder \"rufsig i h\u00e5ret\" p\u00e5 j\u00e4mtl\u00e4ndska och b\u00e5de namnet och bandets grundare Malin h\u00e4rstammar fr\u00e5n J\u00e4mtland. Inspirerad av norrlands vyer med h\u00f6ga berg, djupa sj\u00f6ar och storslagen natur, och med en enorm k\u00e4rlek till amerikansk folkmusik och country, har Fluru ett helt unikt sound som b\u00e5de ber\u00f6r och l\u00e4mnar ett avtryck.\r\n\r\nF\u00f6rutom att spela live \u00e4r Fluru just nu i full g\u00e5ng med att spela in sin f\u00f6rsta EP som v\u00e4ntas sl\u00e4ppas under h\u00f6sten 2015. Den kraftfulla kombinationen av norrlands inland och den amerikanska s\u00f6dern samt m\u00e4ngder av vacker st\u00e4ms\u00e5ng \u00e4r tv\u00e5 ypperligt goda anledningar att uppleva Fluru.\r\n\r\nhttp:\/\/www.fluru.se","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/015f3036-7b27-4a0d-b0a3-84645b3f94aa_media_Fluru - Heading Home.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/9027ebd2-1fa6-45b0-a720-cec3e3c0aaf4_media_10632785_952147684815002_1927538381220224994_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Portland View","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"Askersund","text":"We are Portland View. We are an indie-rock group that have been playing together for about three years now. During that time we have played several shows in various locations around and in \u00d6rebro, recorded two EP:s (one released in 2013 and a brand new one scheduled to be released early this fall), and been on P3 radio's top 10 unsigned list weeks in a row with our single \"Rio\" from our first EP, Crystal Sea. \r\n   This year we have been on the down-low because we've been in the midst of recording our new EP, and all of our time and energy has been focused on that. But since things are wrapping up on that front we are ready to get out there and play live again, finally! Live at Heart will be our first stop for promoting this EP, so please come and check us out!  \r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/41216334-58e0-429d-9d7e-70ee4e82b372_media_Portland View - Architecture.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Astrakhan","musik":"Progressive rock","place":"Stockholm","text":"With big love for melodies and with strong influences of the classic 70s prog rock, swedes in ASTRAKHAN has a stunning and unique sound with similar blood lines to Led Zeppelin, Rainbow and Kansas. The difference is that ASTRAKHAN has spiced it up with some fresh and modern elements. ASTRAKHAN is a very solid band with former members of Pain of Salvation and Royal Hunt. Their songs are written with high quality that will appeal to an adult audience who demands technical skills, and with a new-old approach that generates groovy and heavy progressive rock.\r\n\r\nIn late 2013 their first album 'Retrospective' was released and got very good reviews(Sweden Rock Magazine gave it 8\/10 for instance).\r\nA year later they were ready to record their second album and it's set to be released in october 2015.\r\n\r\nASTRAKHAN gives you a exciting musical journey into something mysterious and deep. Unique arrangements as well as some individual extraordinary peak performances, singer Alex Lyckes emotional vocals and a blasting rhythm section move the songs forward to a level where you just want to close your eyes and fly away with ASTRAKHANS musical flow.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e78409e3-ab87-40e2-ad67-19ad630cdf80_media_Wisdom of massdestruction_Mix8.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a5aaad99-4e47-4f00-8979-c08dabd06767_media_astrakhan_band_promo_pic_1.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Renaissance of Fools","musik":"Progressive rock","place":"Falun","text":"Renaissance of Fools was found by former guitarist and composer of Pain of Salvation, Daniel Magdic, and Magnus Karlsson from Thalamus. They started to write material for their first album Fear, hope and Frustration which was released by Metalville in 2011. The album had a guest appearence by Per Wiberg of Opeth and recieved good reviews in the press.\r\n\r\nThe band has made some changes since then, and they released  their second album \"Spring\" in June 2015 (august 21st in the U.S.A.), with singer David Engstr\u00f6m (Silent Nation) and Linus Carlsson (Kamtchatka). The album also contains guest appearence by Kristoffer Gildenl\u00f6w (former Pain of Salvation bassist and former bandmate of Daniel Magdic). The album has recieved good reviews: \" The quality of composition and finishing, without fault or length, reached by Renaissance Of Fools in this \"Spring\" is impressive because the Swedes manage to offer a complex and expressive music, consolidated brilliant instrumental parts, while maintaining fluidity and ease of listening. \" (Musicwaves)\r\n\r\nThe music that Renaissance of Fools creates is inspired by classic seminal acts such as Black Sabbath, King's X, Rush, King Crimson, to the more contemporary sounds of Tool, Porcupine Tree, and Mars Volta. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/8ebefebc-c985-479b-b219-363c3c245480_media_Renaissance of Fools -Scars 160.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Sandra RuthLousie","musik":"Visa","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"S\u00e5ngerskan Sandra RuthLouise bjuder p\u00e5 egenkomponerad akustisk pop med influenser av jazz och visa.\r\nSandra skriver p\u00e5 svenska och h\u00e4mtar mycket av sin inspiration fr\u00e5n den svenska vis- och psalmskatten. H\u00e4r \u00e4r orden en lika viktig del i musiken som tonerna. Texterna rymmer b\u00e5de ljus och m\u00f6rker, det br\u00e4ckliga samsas med hoppet. Musik som ber\u00f6r och dr\u00f6jer sig kvar! \r\n\r\nSandra RuthLouise \u00e4r en av IMKs akter och framtr\u00e4der tillsammans med Daniel F\u00e4lt (Klaviatur), Oskar Borgenvik (Gitarr och Flygelhorn), David Salminen (Bas) och Erik Nilsson (Trummor och Saxofon).","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/11525280-e360-4c6f-bf10-e92fc7cfb3f2_media_Falla - Sandra RuthLouise (Sample).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/81ff087d-d3d9-402e-972f-b3a729eee1c0_media_SandraRuthLouise.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Junior Scully","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Port Talbot","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/d4c298af-206a-4771-af03-463424ae926b_media_Junior Scully - Be.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Karolina & the TREEROOTS","musik":"Country","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Bandet Karolina  and The TREEROOTS spelar countryinspirerad pop, f\u00e4rgat av b\u00e5de soul, rock och folkmusik. Vokalisten och l\u00e5tskrivaren Karolina Cederqvist s\u00e4tter nu ihop detta band best\u00e5ende av Samuel Olofsson (git), H\u00e5kan Cederqvist (bas), Erik Nilsson (tr) och Ulrika Arenius (k\u00f6r), \u00d6rebromusiker som alla n\u00e5gon period h\u00f6rt hemma i gospelk\u00f6ren Joybells. Detta blir deras debut i denna sammans\u00e4ttning. Det blir en blandning av egenkomponerad musik och covers. Karolina har skrivit m\u00e5nga l\u00e5tar till andra artister, men nu, med TREEROOTS kommer hon tillbaka till sina egna r\u00f6tter b\u00e5de musikaliskt och personligt. Detta \u00e4r en av IMKs akter.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/03d2c839-2334-4166-a71a-1d0d1b76a1a0_media_Vid tr\u00e4dets r\u00f6tter - Karolina & the TREEROOTS - Mastered.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/48fc0a11-5cfa-498b-9f50-548770ceb84e_media_Karolina & the TREEROOTS.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Golden Jubilee Quartet","musik":"Gospel","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Old School accapella gospel with cautious choreography. Louis Armstrong meets Neil Armstrong, so to speak. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/4cf310e6-b590-4b5c-a43a-da57a65da8cc_media_Oh Mary (GJQ).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/8ef09949-7e1c-46d9-83f4-d4f873f1d493_media_GJQ bild.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Spetsnaz","musik":"Electronic","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9f64a7aa-519b-4ced-a0e3-f8b9068eac3c_media_01 Nothing But Black.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Stratus","musik":"Hard rock","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ced0bc59-35d1-47e9-acd8-07adfbbf36f7_media_07. Commuter blast.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Island Minks","musik":"Rock","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/313dfa5f-6414-4962-a874-be40436a3e72_media_This Town 150622.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/c7eda30a-b492-4f90-9029-96525f5180d2_media_Island Minks.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Br\u00f6draskapet","musik":"Hiphop","place":"Bor\u00e5s","text":"Br\u00f6draskapet har hunnit med mycket sedan det hyllade debutalbumet \"Himmelriket\" sl\u00e4pptes f\u00f6r tv\u00e5 \u00e5r sedan. Den rappa hiphop-kvartetten har gjort ett flertal framf\u00f6rande i b\u00e5de P3 och P4 och har f\u00e5tt chansen att v\u00e4rma upp scenen \u00e5t b\u00e5de Ken Ring och Petter. I h\u00f6stas sl\u00e4pptes det efterl\u00e4ngtade andra albumet, \"Gehenna\", vilket fick ett varmt mottagande.\r\n\r\nAtt g\u00e5 p\u00e5 en spelning med br\u00f6draskapet \u00e4r att f\u00e5 en k\u00e4nga i nyllet i form av texternas bitterljuva teman, bli bjuden p\u00e5 n\u00e5got f\u00f6r att lindra sm\u00e4rtan, bli k\u00e4r p\u00e5 dansgolvet och vakna dagen efter med en gnutta hopp och knuten n\u00e4ve trots baksm\u00e4llan.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/0f08de2a-8db1-4544-be8c-056343a77ef8_media_Br\u00f6draskapet - 05. GEHENNA.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/406a02fc-69ce-4897-8c11-3465ca489f3f_media_br\u00f6draskapet-promo-2015(2).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Big Generation","musik":"Progressive rock","place":"\u00d6rebro\/Stockholm","text":"Big Generation was formed in \u00d6rebro in 1993 to play progressive rock inspired of Yes, Genesis, Dream Theater, It Bites and others. The band split up in 1996 when the members moved away from their hometown. Recently they got together to play some old songs and the thrill and enjoy was overwhelming. \r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/1d23fde0-5ceb-4102-b203-d12bf269fa40_media_Big generation - Wake up Call Ny.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/281d93c5-4aca-4f8f-b29f-2686d9e50529_media_Big Generation Booklet.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Pete and the Poets","musik":"Pop","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Pete and the Poets musik beskrivs ofta som melodi\u00f6s pop med inslag av episka instrumentala partier. Bandet har haft flera l\u00e5tar snurrandes p\u00e5 radions spellistor, senast \"In The Summertime\" och \"Merry Christmas\".\r\nP\u00e5 Live At Heart kommer vi spela l\u00e5tar fr\u00e5n skivan \"Shine\" blandat med outgivet material. \r\n\r\nWe're gonna play songs from our last album \"Shine\" mixed with some new material. As always when we play the music will be performed in one piece.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ff804eb6-e81d-4df7-853b-20574b98feea_media_Pete and the poets - If you were gone.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Miss Irenie Rose","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Glasgow","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/7f143210-710a-455b-9366-0e42fe5408c9_media_River.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Flora Cash","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/b1a86e21-5280-496d-a646-21554299b00d_media_01 Save Me 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Six String Yada","musik":"Folk","place":"\u00d6rebro\/Sthlm","text":"Krediterat med att ge den nya v\u00e5gen av Amerikansk folkmusik i\r\nSverige en rej\u00e4l skjuts fram\u00e5t under de senaste \u00e5ren h\u00e5ller Six String\r\nYada traditionen av hillbilly-musik fr\u00e5n de Appalachiska bergen vid\r\nliv, men samtidigt skapar de ocks\u00e5 n\u00e5got nytt. \r\nBasen kanske best\u00e5r av traditionell amerikansk folkmusik men det \u00e4r deras kryddning av\r\ns\u00e5v\u00e4l brittiska som svenska folktoner som g\u00f6r att detta blir en\r\nmusikalisk upplevelse som st\u00e5r ut \u2013 och att allt levereras med en\r\nr\u00e5gad nypa punkattityd.\r\nI allt fr\u00e5n covers p\u00e5 obskyra metal-band som ingen har h\u00f6rt talas om\r\ntill fioll\u00e5tar som ingen har h\u00f6rt talas om s\u00e5 g\u00e5r bandet under deras\r\nsj\u00e4lvutn\u00e4mnda motto \u2013 10% \u00e4r vad vi spelar, 90% \u00e4r hur man spelar\r\ndet.\r\nMed \u00f6ver 100 spelningar och tv\u00e5 album i ryggen s\u00e5 \u00e4r detta ett band\r\nsom garanterar att \u00e4ven den mest tystl\u00e5tna, tillbakalutade\r\nnorrl\u00e4nningen kommer stampa takten och sjunga med. \r\n\r\n\r\nSix String Yada best\u00e5r av:\r\nAgnes Brogeby \u2013 Fiol\r\nErling Bronsberg \u2013 Banjo\r\nSimon Nyberg \u2013 Gitarr\r\nJonas Bleckman \u2013 Cello\r\n\r\n\r\n\u201dJag l\u00e4gger mig platt f\u00f6r Six String Yada. Jag \u00e4r helt s\u00e5ld. Det h\u00e4r \u00e4r\r\nmusik n\u00e4r den \u00e4r som allra roligast. Sprallig, skicklig och spelglad.\u201d \u2013\r\nPierre Eriksson, Lira Musik\r\n\r\n\r\n\u201dSix String Yada \u00e4r ett liveband som kan s\u00e4tta en hel publik i brand\r\nmed sitt entusiastiska spel - precis som sina f\u00f6reg\u00e5ngare gjorde f\u00f6r\r\nhundra \u00e5r sedan.\u201d \u2013 Alexis Vos, KINDA Muzik, Holland\r\n\r\n\u201dEfter en makal\u00f6st intensiv 20-minuters konsert p\u00e5 ett hotellrum var\r\njag helt omtumlad och tvungen att kolla in showen halv tre ocks\u00e5.\u201d \u2013\r\nH\u00e5kan Olsson, VD Rootsy.nu\r\n\r\n\u201dDe f\u00f6ljer nu upp med ett explosivt debutalbum, d\u00e4r Appalachernas\r\nhillbilly- och oldtimemusic mixas med h\u00e4ftig punk och rock.\u201d -\r\nKenneth Hammargren Nerkies Allehanda\r\n\r\n\u201dTillsammans bj\u00f6d de p\u00e5 cirka 45 minuter gapig country, f\u00f6r ett\r\n\u00f6gonblick var jag helt s\u00e4ker p\u00e5 att jag drabbats av n\u00e5got kardiologiskt\r\nmiss\u00f6de men det var nog bara hj\u00e4rtat som inte visste hur det skulle\r\nreagera p\u00e5 den typen av fullt \u00f6s x 5.\u201d \u2013 Kerstin Westin, V\u00e4xj\u00f6 Country\r\nRoots Festival\r\n\r\n\u201dOm man inte smittas av den h\u00e4r gruppens energi och spelgl\u00e4dje s\u00e5\r\nblir man nog inte smittad av n\u00e5got. Det \u00e4r skickligt spel, spralliga\r\ntoner, p\u00e5 allvar men lustfyllt.\u201d \u2013 Korr\u00f6 Musikfestival\r\n\r\n\u201cSo, how does Swedish d-beat punk sound on the banjo? Damned\r\ngood, that\u2019s how! Six String Yada have slowed the song into a doomy\r\nbackwoods ballad that really works. They sure can sing, too.\u201d\r\n \u2013 I.S Islander, NoCleanSinging.Com","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e34db913-d227-4683-8153-79698c03971f_media_Banjo picking girl.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/07786d48-b50a-4e0a-958d-25f9f1cbea20_media_Six string Yada (2).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Emmecosta","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ea78c59e-9461-4b5f-8496-782804c2979e_media_01 Brontos 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Nelson-Westin Jazz Machine","musik":"Jazz","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Nelson-Westin Jazz Machine best\u00e5r av en grupp musiker baserade i \u00d6rebroomr\u00e5det, Musiken som framf\u00f6rs kan beskrivas som melodi\u00f6s och rytmisk rotad i traditionen fr\u00e5n 50-60-talets jazzmusikaliska guld\u00e5lder. Dock b\u00e4r den samtidens pr\u00e4gel utmejslad av komposit\u00f6rer som Steve Davis, Avishai Cohen, Chris Potter, och en av bandets medlemmar, Patrick Westin.\r\nHemsida: www.jazzmachine.net","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/3e64fbe1-a851-4fa1-a8a4-9329b3575a32_media_Nelson Westin - The Marshall.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/1b8d3b95-5392-4e42-9cbe-aed86eaf67ae_media_NElson Westin JazzMachine.png.jpg"},{"title":"Captain Crimson","musik":"Hard rock","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"It was the lead singer from the stoner rock band Blowback who started the band back in 2010. Since then, Captain Crimson has drawn their inspiration in the music from the sixties and the seventies such as The Grand Hogs, Blue Cheer, Emerson, Lake and Palmer, Jethro Tull and Cactus. If you take this influence and mix it the best of bands like Graveyard, Witchcraft or Blues Pills, you would be left with Captain Crimson.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/b9482b49-fa1d-435c-9331-4eb61b1acd83_media_03 Ageless Time.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Anja Lagerqvist","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Halmstad","text":"Anja \u00e4r en ung Singer-songwriter som trots sin unga \u00e5lder har en stor scenvana och har medverkat i b\u00e5de TV och radio. Hon skriver l\u00e5tar p\u00e5 svenska om det som k\u00e4nns viktigt och ber\u00f6r. Anja har bl.a. rest till Sydafrika och sjungit med Star for life, varit med i Hallandsfinalen av Svensktoppen n\u00e4sta och deltagit i Team Rickard i K\u00f6rlaget.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/617ab9f0-e2c2-4b5b-b5ae-134516990c24_media_Lever lyckliga slutversion mp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a5ff45d4-9c61-4a96-ba9c-fe46f7abcb1c_media_IMG_7562 kopia.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"V\u00c4G","musik":"Rock","place":"Stockholm","text":"GAFFA beskriver V\u00e4g som:\r\nTa Atomic Swing och kidnappa Florence Valentin, vira in allt i en mentalitet bev\u00e4rdigad den hos Kenta och Stoffe, h\u00e4ll bensin \u00f6ver alltihop och t\u00e4nd eld.\r\n\r\nMedverkande p\u00e5 skivan: Martin Hederos(Tonbruket, Soundtrack Of Our Lives), Bebban Stenborg(Shout Out Louds), Sarah Snavely(A Nighthawk, Dag f\u00f6r Dag) mfl. Producerad av Johannes Berglund(Mike Snow, Shout Out Louds, Jenny Wilson, The Knife)\r\n\r\nPromotion av Ebba Lindqvist","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/0b37cdda-7c42-49b6-a873-4806a30011b7_media_Hornstull.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"West of Eden","musik":"Folk","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"West of Eden \u00e4r ett svenskt folkmusikband som n\u00e5tt internationell uppm\u00e4rksamhet och framg\u00e5ng med sitt h\u00f6gklassiga l\u00e5tmaterial och unika sound med r\u00f6tterna i engelsk och irl\u00e4ndsk folkmusik. Traditionella instrument s\u00e5som fiol, dragspel och tin whistle samsas med trummor och gitarrer, och \u00f6verst skimrar s\u00e5ngerskan Jenny Schaubs kristallklara r\u00f6st.\r\n\r\n West of Eden har turnerat b\u00e5de p\u00e5 Irland, i Skottland  och ute i Europa, och har gett ut \u00e5tta skivor vilka m\u00f6tts av str\u00e5lande kritik i internationell musikpress. Bandet har bl.a. utsetts till \"The Best of contemporary folk\u201d av Irish Music Magazine och kallats \u201done of today\u2019s most innovative folk bands\u201d av Folkworld.\r\nSenaste skivan \u201dSongs From Twisitng River\u201d spelades in i Yorkshire och g\u00e4stas av namnkunniga musiker som Kate Rusby, Ron Block (Alison Krauss & Union Station) samt Michael McGoldrick (Mark Knopfler \r\n\r\n Genom \u00e5ren har man bl.a. spelat f\u00f6r uts\u00e5lda hus p\u00e5 G\u00f6teborgs Konserthus tillsammans med musiker ur G\u00f6teborgs Symfoniker och gjort ett flertal live-framtr\u00e4danden i TV och radio.  \r\n Bandet har ocks\u00e5 hunnit spelat p\u00e5 den v\u00e4lrenommerade festivalen Celtic Connections i Glasgow, turnera med showen Irish Heartbeat, samt i \u00e5tta \u00e5r arrangerat konserten \u201dCeltic Christmas\u201d d\u00e4r man upptr\u00e4tt tillsammans med musiker fr\u00e5n bl.a. The Chieftains, Wolfstone och Riverdance. Live-inspelningen fr\u00e5n Celtic Christmas beskrevs av Rambles som \u201dA masterpiece of Christmas Music\u201d. \r\n\r\n En konsert med West of Eden blir till en resa mellan akustisk historieber\u00e4ttande intimitet och glad, uppsluppen folkrock, alltid framf\u00f6rd med k\u00e4rlek och respekt f\u00f6r den keltiska musiken.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9e86378c-6634-4ed9-b5e7-592c6d7558f9_media_WEST oF eden 03 Safe Crossing 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/87c22216-d0cb-49d1-b42b-21a7a54b850d_media_MalinJohansson_WestOfEden_Webb.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Sex Dwarf","musik":"Punk","place":"Stockholm","text":"Noisepunk fr\u00e5n Stockholm","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/bed482e3-083e-497f-857a-796645dae8a8_media_Sex Dwarf - Deras Ord.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Shamrock","musik":"Folk","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/64b7ed3b-9d8d-4710-b664-c0efc3fc56ac_media_Johnny I hardly knew ya.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/errorimg\/imgbg.jpg"},{"title":"Brittsommar","musik":"Americana","place":"New York","text":"BIO:\r\n\r\nIn 2010, the then19 year old Sawyer Gebauer moved to a farm on the Swedish countryside creating an international band full of elaborate characters in the likes of lawyers, painters, scientists, engineers, thieves, nobodies and know-it-alls. All on the cusp of giving it all up and starting again through this project.\r\n\r\nFrom recording Brittsommar \u0301s first album \u201cDay Of Living Velvet\u201d in an abandoned synagogue in his home town of Madison, WI, to a warehouse in Berlin where the critically acclaimed \u201cThe Machine Stops\u201d was born, Sawyer returned to America to harness and rediscover his tongue where the root of folk, country, and music tradition breaths.\r\nTraveling coast to coast and south to north more than once, Brittsommar found the breeding ground for \u201cThe Mary Me E.P.\u201d at Bob Weir \u0301s TRI studios in San Rafael, California.\r\n\r\nWorking with a dynamic group of musicians such as Jason Crosby and producer Brad K Dollar, \u201cThe Mary E.P.\u201d is no re-write. It is a musical transformation cradling the ramble of blues, the pain of the American country, the known stories of folk, and the ever-changing pop of today. \r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/711a21e1-a4f7-46e7-805c-a363c68587bf_media_BRITTSOMMAR 01 Can't Breathe On My OwnAAC.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/7862eb4c-54c9-4b78-be5c-858d2fd9f50f_media_Brittsommar.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"NORAK","musik":"Electronic","place":"Borl\u00e4nge","text":"NORAK is a duo that create electronic music in all genres. Our live concept is innovative, different and contains dj-equipment, live vocals, percussion instruments and a high energy show. We are not limiting ourselves by putting a label on our genre, but are inspired by all types of music and that is what makes our sound unique. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/54423f4b-6358-4c0a-b85e-8203495c0d47_media_NORAK - Holding On.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/7cc04b8e-e158-4d1a-b022-08ee91881fa2_media_NORAK Pressbild (kopia).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Dimpker Brothers","musik":"Folk","place":"Edsbruk","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/79797ce1-d259-4fc3-94c9-c51aee985b0f_media_Dimpker Brothers - Home_V2_30-03-2015.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/c314dd78-724f-4617-9274-b37e313740f2_media_10408022_730815213634645_1740594274723711820_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Richard Lindgren","musik":"Americana","place":"Malm\u00f6","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/95a9cfad-e759-4fac-9906-a00f63d36045_media_07 I Used Up My Tomorrows.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/86edc665-9e82-4f0a-9498-e0d674f092a2_media_rl-sh.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Sibyl Vane","musik":"Rock","place":"P\u00e4rnu","text":"Trio playing exceptional mix of alternative rock and indie, led by guitarist and vocalist Helena Randlaht. In their music You can hear dynamics of System of a Down and the moodiness of Depeche Mode or The Cardigans along with sound associated with 30's jazz. Loud and energetic concerts became the key to their success and let them play shows all over Baltics, Scandinavia and Great Britain. Finnish Music Magazine NRGM wrote once: \"From all of the Estonian bands they are the one who can make international career.\" (by Asymmetry Festival, Poland)","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ac467543-bb35-4f7b-bf3b-60800c939f65_media_02 Get Out Of Town.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5065a89a-f1ed-4333-ba91-b078dddc8669_media_020a.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Tullamore Brothers","musik":"Folk","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Tullamore Brothers - Irl\u00e4ndsk folkmusik med hj\u00e4rta och attityd\r\n\r\nTullamore Brothers bildades 1988 i \u00d6rebro av bandets s\u00e5ngare Olle Unenge. Fr\u00e5n att i b\u00f6rjan bara ha spelat p\u00e5 den lokala puben har man utvecklats till att bli ett av Sveriges mest etablerade band i genren. P\u00e5 meritlistan finns bl a tv\u00e5 Irlandsturn\u00e9er, flera framtr\u00e4danden i radio och TV och m\u00e4ngder med spelningar i Sverige. Allt fr\u00e5n helt akustiska spelningar i ett vardagsrum, till stora festivaler. Inget \u00e4r fr\u00e4mmande f\u00f6r Tullamore Brothers!\u00a0\r\n\r\n2013 sl\u00e4pptes bandets tredje album \u2013 \"Still Going Wrong\" \u2013 som f\u00e5tt ett v\u00e4ldigt fint mottagande.\r\n\r\nTullamore Brothers bjuder p\u00e5 en f\u00f6rest\u00e4llning med blixtrande snabba instrumentaler och sm\u00e4ktande ballader uppblandat med de mest k\u00e4nda pubs\u00e5ngerna. Publiken rycks med i de oemotst\u00e5ndliga Irl\u00e4ndska tonerna och pl\u00f6tsligt k\u00e4nns det som om man befinner sig p\u00e5 Den Gr\u00f6na \u00d6n \u2013 Irland.\r\n\r\nTullamore Brothers \u00e4r:\r\nOlle Unenge leads\u00e5ng och akustisk gitarr, Mats Lindstr\u00f6m irl\u00e4ndsk bouzouki och s\u00e5ng, Thomas Gustafsson whistles, durspel, Digitala Uillean Pipes, munspel och s\u00e5ng, Kajsa Zetterlund fiol och s\u00e5ng, Simon Nyberg banjos, mandolin, gitarr och s\u00e5ng.\r\n\r\nCitat fr\u00e5n pressen:\r\nKonsert - \u201dEn hejdundrande folkfest\u201d - H\u00e5kan Pettersson (H\u00e5kans pop)\r\nKonsert\u00a0 - \u201dTotal succ\u00e9 f\u00f6r Tullamore\u201d - H\u00e5kan Pettersson (H\u00e5kans pop)\r\nStill going wrong CD 4\/5 \u201dImponerande samst\u00e4mmighet rakt \u00f6ver.\u201d\u00a0\r\n- Kenneth Hammargren (Nerikes Allehanda)\r\nStill going wrong CD 4\/5 - \u201d\u00c4kta gl\u00e4dje och djup melankoli.\u201d Bj\u00f6rn Reimers (Kulturdelen)\r\nKonsert 4,5\/5 \u201d - \u2026kompetens, gl\u00e4dje och utstr\u00e5lning\u2026\u201d Bj\u00f6rn Reimers (Kulturdelen)\r\n(\u201dStill Going Wrong\u201d finns p\u00e5 SPOTIFY)\r\nwww.tullamorebrothers.se\r\nwww.reverbnation.com\/tullamorebrothers\r\nwww.facebook.com\/TullamoreBrothers","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/f67954c5-e7ef-46a1-8048-15b924875e37_media_11 Rambles Of Spring.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a865a9fe-d1ff-4223-acc2-7018ca52b758_media_Slussen Musikrestaurang_3647.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Olle Unenge Band","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"\u201dDet kunde f\u00f6rvisso vara v\u00e4rre...\u201d\r\n... \u00e4r ett citat fr\u00e5n min underbara Mamma M\u00e4rtha. Och jag ser denna min f\u00f6rsta egna platta som en hyllning till henne - och till alla andra goa m\u00e4nniskor jag har haft och har omkring mej i Livet.\u00a0\r\nJag har \u00e4gnat mej \u00e5t Musiken p\u00e5 olika s\u00e4tt sedan tidigt 60-tal, d\u00e5 mina f\u00f6rsta egna s\u00e5nger f\u00f6ddes i Traneberg i Stockholm. Musiken har alltid funnits i mej och i min n\u00e4rhet, fr\u00e5n Bob Dylan och Evert Taube till Rolling Stones,  Corelli, Bert Jansch m fl. Och givetvis den Irl\u00e4ndska folkmusiken, som alltid varit funnits i mitt hj\u00e4rta - framf\u00f6rallt genom \u00d6rebro-baserade Tullamore Brothers.\u00a0\r\nMina s\u00e5nger \u00e4r p\u00e5 svenska - s\u00e5nger om m\u00e4nniskor i min n\u00e4rhet, om Grekiska \u00d6ar och s\u00e5nger och texter som kommer ur nyheter och h\u00e4ndelser i v\u00e4rlden runt omkring. Jag skriver av mej f\u00f6r att b\u00e4ttre f\u00f6rst\u00e5 och f\u00f6r att kunna forts\u00e4tta fram\u00e5t. Och man kan ju alltid citera Mamma M\u00e4rtha: \u201dDet kunde f\u00f6rvisso vara v\u00e4rre\u2026\u201d.\r\nOlle Unenge, \u00d6rebro. Juli 2015.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/48b565e1-bcdb-4d50-a2f2-05349188c93f_media_02 - Sk\u00e5l F\u00f6r Min Fader__44k-16b.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0e21e113-a2b8-4dd2-88e5-3ddb5c56f6e0_media_Det kunde... CD-Front.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Sunset Serenaders","musik":"Americana","place":"G\u00e4vle","text":"Sunset Serenaders create a warm atmosphere with a rootsy take on vintage Tin Pan Alley music, using tight vocal harmonies and a swinging acoustic groove.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/8cc33396-05db-49ad-a252-384d25fc0985_media_Sunset Teaser.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/337d680e-636a-4e58-b592-354dd2834838_media_sunset smile.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Dennis Kalla","musik":"Pop","place":"Lule\u00e5","text":"Om Jokern och Lorde hade ett band ihop skulle det l\u00e5ta som Dennis Kalla. V\u00e4lskrivna popl\u00e5tar med trasiga gitarrer, stora synthar, och texter som sk\u00e4r i hj\u00e4rtat.\r\n\r\nSedan starten November 2014 har Dennis Kalla sl\u00e4ppt tre singlar och turn\u00e9rat intensivt. Andra singeln \"Change Your Mind\" sl\u00e4pptes i februari och gick direkt upp p\u00e5 studentradiolistans topp 20, samt blev rankad som b\u00e4sta singeln i Norrbotten.\r\n\r\nNu \u00e4r Dennis aktuell med tredje singeln \"Good Night Bad Morning\" som gett honom festivalspelningar runt Sverige, samt fick GAFFA att utn\u00e4mna honom till \"Norrbottens nya pophopp\".\r\n\r\nK\u00e4llor:\r\nhttp:\/\/gaffa.se\/nyhet\/93428\r\nhttp:\/\/gaffa.se\/nyhet\/95630\r\nhttp:\/\/duonoje.se\/articles\/kolla-in-den-norrbottniska-singeltoppen\r\nhttps:\/\/www.facebook.com\/denniskallamusic","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e0fe0858-ebd2-476e-9b6d-8e3a77404548_media_Dennis Kalla - Good Night Bad Morning.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/9b601e67-6d2b-4b6b-8626-1279ee60faf2_media_denniskallapressbild3.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Don Darlings","musik":"Americana","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"\u201cLike a dying heart at the bottom of a muddy black hole, The Don Darlings pump forth grinding sorrow with a confident genuineness that would impress both Nick Cave and Tom Waits alike. This is a very successful hybrid of the blackest soul of country with the hardest genres of Central Europe from the 80\u2019s, with one foot in Dallas and the other in Berlin.\u201d\r\n\r\nThese words come from a review of the band performing at the Way Out West-festival. Roaring reviews for their debut album on AlleyCat Records, \u201cThe Shortest Straw\u201d propelled them out on several European tours.\r\nTheir self-titled second album was released last year was recorded in Berlin and mixed by\r\nDon Alsterberg (Graveyard, Junip).The Don Darlings has a signed a deal with acclaimed HepTown Records and released the single \"Electronic Man\" on Record Store Day 2015. To support the release the Don Darlings once more have hit the roads.\r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/0a06c7a8-0094-4733-94b4-b44a08700316_media_Electronic Man_ The Don Darlings.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/31d95ab6-294b-4273-a101-f76f7ce0e54c_media_TheDonDarlings15.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Tom Levin","musik":"Americana","place":"Stockholm","text":"In 2014, Tom Levin surprised listeners by releasing two related albums \"Them Buffalo\" & \"Them Feet\". Both albums are received warm welcome in North America, found their way into several Best of 2014-list and where one critique claims \"Them Buffalo\" is the finest album he\u2019s heard in 2014.\r\n\r\nFor more information please visit: www.tomlevin.com","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6d057439-626b-44ad-8f98-be0fc245fca4_media_Everyday - Tom Levin.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/16f13125-3e8e-41a1-b1e5-531f65637cdc_media_Tom Levin_TwoFace_web_2048x2048.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Tellus Children","musik":"Rock","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Is this old school? Is this the new order? It's hard to really get it as it smells so retro and tastes so funky. It\u2019s not 60\u2019s pop, it\u2019s not 70\u2019s rock, it\u2019s not surf and it\u2019s not spiritual - but at the same time it\u2019s all of the above. It's a blend of things we all may have forgotten. Except Tellus Children who got it in store.\r\n\r\nTELLUS CHILDREN started out as an acoustic duo but grew into a full-sized rock band in time for the recording of the debut album. This piece of music consists of 11 songs Miranda and Boris, the original children, have written together and the musical journey shows a great thirst for creating something new as well as a curiosity for taking the wrong turn. It\u2019s haunting, it\u2019s catchy and it\u2019s fresh!\r\n\r\nThe album was released through their own label Fongo Records on the 28th of February with a ceremonial mass in Gothenburg City, and now we are taking this session to anywhere and everywhere we can. So it's high time you get your ticket and your seat as this trip is about to roll out.\r\n\r\nGet your ticket, take your seat, this trip is rolling out. \r\nGet your trip, take your ticket, this seat is rolling out. \r\nGet your seat, take your trip, this ticket is rolling out.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/3e3bb2d4-b253-4b0a-b965-adeab3b19943_media_1 Mary Gone Mad.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/795ce935-c291-4a20-87f8-abb32fa3d44c_media_Svartvit_mot_textur.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Tommee Balukea","musik":"Folk","place":"Sydney","text":"Write a short presentation of your band here.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/86f296e3-3f24-45a9-8f21-0845e442f162_media_03 Kalembo Ade 1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/9130b05a-cace-43a2-90c3-eea382beca19_media_11122516_10153397064647299_982029995_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Destin Fragile","musik":"Electronic","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Electroniskt popband som sl\u00e4ppt debutplatta i \u00e5r","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/77ca7b83-070c-4542-a8d4-9f516f1e1775_media_Run Away.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/3e90d443-f016-419f-b81c-f0c8a74a56b9_media_dfcover.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Tranq","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"\u00d6rebrobandet The Tranq \u00e4r tillbaka med nya l\u00e5tar! Bandet har dragit fulla hus p\u00e5 Live At Heart f\u00f6rut, och i \u00e5r blir det livepremi\u00e4r av h\u00f6stens kommande singlar. Den h\u00e4r g\u00e5ngen har The Tranq bytt ut s\u00e5v\u00e4l sound som producent f\u00f6r att skapa ett r\u00e5are, hittigare material \u00e4n tidigare.\r\n\r\nThe Tranq spelar samh\u00e4llskritisk indierock och har tidigare giggat p\u00e5 bland annat Peace & Love-festivalen, Debaser Medis (Sthlm) och Jazzhuset (Gbg). Albumdebuten \"Loss Is For The Masses\" har uppm\u00e4rksammats av bloggare och media i bland annat USA, UK, Frankrike och Sverige.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/3332994f-6c7a-47df-abd7-2d14108e9cbd_media_The Tranq - My Heart Is A Yo-Yo (lowres).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/9862d282-a65b-42c6-b158-d5da20b0c45a_media_TheTranq_web_2000px_A1237036-2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Growling Bear & the Blues Juice","musik":"Blues","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Growling Bear (Bj\u00f6rn G\u00f6ransson) & the Blues Juice (Timo Tilli) har under \u00e5rens lopp spelat i m\u00e5nga olika bluesband. Nu sen ca 3 \u00e5r tillbaka har de f\u00f6renats i akustisk Countryblues. Lite Son House, Mississppi John Hurt, Cephas and Wiggins och \u00e4ven n\u00e5gon egen l\u00e5t.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/b8631e0b-1fa2-4625-a44f-0d9d0aff81e8_media_Growling Bear &amp BluesJuice - Action man.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/7a450054-6684-4339-84cd-85f5594faf3a_media_Growling Bear & the Blues Juice.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Disraeli","musik":"Garage","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Likt f\u00e5geln Fenix reste sig Disraeli ur askan fr\u00e5n uppl\u00f6sta band. Bandet har ett riktigt tight sound och spelar garagerock av det lite h\u00e5rdare slaget. Under ett par \u00e5r har bandet visat att de b\u00e5de p\u00e5 skiva och framf\u00f6rallt live f\u00e5r publiken att spastiskt skaka. Disraeli arbetar nu med nytt material till den kommande EP:n som f\u00f6rv\u00e4ntas komma under h\u00f6sten.\r\n\r\n\"\u00c4r du svag f\u00f6r rivig rock b\u00f6r du absolut l\u00e5na ett \u00f6ra eller tv\u00e5.\" - Jonathan Bj\u00f6rklund, Nerikes Allehanda\r\n\"Bandet har en riktigt stark scenn\u00e4rvaro och \u00e4r riktigt underh\u00e5llande att se \" - Johan Bergdahl, \u00d6rebroguiden","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e40f2447-4d64-44ed-b035-aced0156a64a_media_midas2 (online-audio-converter.com).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/c1c12919-551e-41a7-ba3e-3edffde11f20_media_Attachment-.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Maidavale","musik":"Hard rock","place":"Stockholm","text":"\"The musical quality keeps the highest class, the heavy riffs succeed each other and form a manageable psychedelic mess.\u201d - Christoffer Holmstr\u00f6m Musicstage.se\r\n\r\nDuring 2015 MaidaVale has played on one of Swedens biggest festivals, Sweden Rock Festival. They have had a busy summer playing festivals all over the country and has earned a reputation as one hell of a live band.\r\n\r\nHeavy riffs with vibes from the late 60\u2019s combined with round, bluesy tones that penetrates trough rocks and stones and a groove with a fresh touch from the 21st century that leaves no one untouched.\r\n\r\nMaidaVale will hit the studio later this fall and release a beast of an EP as soon as possible. Follow us on Facebook for more information.https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/maidavalesweden?fref=ts","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/947c7bd1-92aa-44b3-97e7-b81bee782f28_media_Maidavale - The Wanderer.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/d90bf86f-d610-4e21-989f-c74fbaf021ff_media_Maidavale pressbild.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Great Garb","musik":"Rock","place":"Stockholm","text":"Great Garb is an indie-rock trio from Garpenberg\/Hedemora, Sweden formed in 2010 by the three childhood friends Erik Hases, Dennis Filatov and Stefan S\u00f6derqvist. Inspired by bands such as The Who and Arctic Monkeys the band writes songs with indie-rock\/pop influences. In october 2014 the band released the EP Orange Shoes, which was recorded with the producer H\u00e5kan S\u00f6rle (Mando Diao, Miss Li, The Baboon Show). The songs are equipped with catchy pop-influenced melodies and have a raw sound with a certain edge to it. The EP was received very well and the band was mentioned as \u201cthe next thing\u201d by MI, the leading music industry magazine in Sweden. After the release of Orange Shoes the band was featured in several British blogs which made the decision to go on tour in the UK easy. After the successful mini-tour in England the band released the new single \"Conflicts\" in April 30th. \r\n\r\nFor more information: \r\n\r\nhttp:\/\/www.greatgarbband.com\/ \r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/www.facebook.com\/greatgarb \r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/soundcloud.com\/greatgarb \r\n\r\nhttps:\/\/instagram.com\/greatgarb\/","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/1cca72e2-51ca-4813-abfa-0dca4336a742_media_Great Garb - Conflicts.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/94d0353a-5e07-4a6a-97b3-397a1d3ed38c_media_Great Garb Pressbild.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Vera Vinter","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"Vera Vinter \u00e4r artist och l\u00e5tskrivare fr\u00e5n byn Stora Lapptr\u00e4sk i Norrbotten. Hon solodebuterade p\u00e5 Sony Music med albumet \u201dIdyll\u201d 2012 och sl\u00e4ppte 2013 en hyllad tolkning av Ulf Lundells klassiker \u201dSn\u00f6n Faller Och Vi Med den\u201d. Nu \u00e4r Vera Vinter aktuell med sitt andra soloalbum, musik inspirerat av sena kv\u00e4llar framf\u00f6r analoga monstersyntar p\u00e5 EMS-studion med viljan att sammanfoga de framdr\u00f6mda v\u00e4rldarna med r\u00f6sten, orden och melodierna. Resultatet \u00e4r melodi\u00f6st ornamenterat, submarint och saturerat. Albumet \u00e4r inspelat tillsammans med producenten Johannes Berglund (The Knife, Jenny Wilson och Amason). F\u00f6rsta singeln \u201dHuset\u201d snurrar redan p\u00e5 P3 och under h\u00f6sten v\u00e4ntar fler singlar och full\u00e4ngdsalbum. \r\n\r\n","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6a8bcb99-10ab-4810-8d5b-70db9de0ce7e_media_Huset MASTER2.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/8f332fc0-c9fb-4728-8359-21d905765cae_media_Vera, h\u00f6guppl\u00f6st.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"JACLE BOW","musik":"Rock","place":"Brussels","text":"Jacle Bow is a Belgian rock band founded in the spring of 2013, Brussels. \r\nOn the rise in the music scene with their refreshing mixture of fine melodic lead-vocals and a rollin' backing band, Jacle Bow reminds us of some of the best pop & rock music of the late 60's and early 70's. Seems like the rawness of the Stones meets the elegance of the Fab Four! \r\nProducer Mario Goossens (Triggerfinger\/Black Box Revelation) is a big fan and helped the band find their own sound to empower the strong songwriting material. After a USA-tour and the first recordings in the studio, Jacle Bow is now ready for take-off. \r\nKeep an eye on these boys, they might well become the next big thing!\r\nCheck their USA roadreport on: www.play-for-that-money-boys.com or like them on www.facebook.com\/jaclebow for a weekly update!","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/255e03bf-16ae-43ea-afef-a78442adb46f_media_JACLE BOW - Suit Yourself.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/fab5819f-1e74-4ae0-aae8-be0ef438a5a8_media_JB USA-166.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"O'Leary\/Nyberg\/Bj\u00f6rklund","musik":"Folk","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"Write a short presentation of your band here.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/95b3ed58-dc18-4bc6-a849-be70d95edfe2_media_09 Erin Gra Mo Chroi.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5154e10f-c9e1-4b40-8eba-3e096db33ce8_media_IMG_5138.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Factory Brains","musik":"Rock","place":"Stockholm","text":"Factory Brains \u00e4r en rocktrio fr\u00e5n Stockholm. Bandet sl\u00e4ppte sitt debutalbum \"Love Like Hours\" 2012 och har utm\u00e4rkt sig f\u00f6r sin explosiva scenshow. Musiken har beskrivits som en blandning av avgrundsblues och garagerock och influenser som brukar n\u00e4mnas vid namn \u00e4r Rolling Stones, White Stripes och Tom Waits. Factory Brains har under de senaste \u00e5ren arbetat p\u00e5 en uppf\u00f6ljare till deras debutalbum och under tiden har de agerat f\u00f6rband \u00e5t akter som Rival Sons, Graveyard, Sator, Brant Bjork m.m. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/efec2d08-4fd0-47f4-8eaf-72ff15d0db58_media_02 Dale Cooper.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/18b16985-6820-4ab3-9493-895d0e446d0e_media_IMG_4178 copy.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Oh Jonathan","musik":"Pop","place":"Pite\u00e5","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/885dc434-77c1-477a-bb56-1bd25aa813ef_media_Tala till mig- Oh Jonathan.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/779dfc15-2af9-4568-853e-b9ac045805dc_media_pressbild Oh Jonathan.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Pelle Pelle Pelle","musik":"Pop","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/1f34545f-5a24-4f65-9599-eb5b89b68f7b_media_sorry baby.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/69a5ef50-c1c4-48ff-9fc3-31b22ba26dfc_media_Pelle.png.jpg"},{"title":"Sara Eidevald unit","musik":"Soul","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/66350a6b-8284-4688-a88d-9d789ae686b8_media_Sara Eidevald - 4. Superwoman.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/26074260-1f06-42b9-8f9d-f264e337e1d5_media_Sara webb.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Aske Jacoby","musik":"Rock","place":"K\u00f6penhamn","text":"Aske Jacoby is a Danish singer\/songwriter\/guitarist who more than anything seeks to move you through his music. His style can be described as \"Folk\/Rock with a twist\" and his unique position in Scandinavian music as one of the best and most original musicians in his field is undisputed. His vibrant vocals and guitar playing goes straight to the heart of the listener.\r\nHe has done five solo albums so far, and his sixth is to be released on Sony Music Denmark early 2016. Like the previous one, it's recorded in Los Angeles with a couple of other world class players such as bassist Tony Scherr and drummer Jim Keltner.\r\n\r\nDiscography:\r\n\r\nNot Only For The Royalties\r\nClubbing\r\nTransfer Power\r\nThree at Last!\r\nChant","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/cc44b824-2a66-4307-ac32-b6ac9ad54b6c_media_01 Chant.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/09b3827f-c53d-47ad-9502-836282491383_media_askeman.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Like Swimming","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"Biography\r\n\r\nLike Swimming formed in late 2012 with Claes Carlstr\u00f6m on vocals and guitar, Ida Hedene on vocals and keys and Petter Wesslander on drums. The three piece band from Sweden forms a blend of whimsical joissance in rythm and melodies and heart breaking sincereness in lyrics and frustration that gives the music an interesting contrast.\r\n\r\nTheir debut album released in September 2014, STRUCTURES has received great reviews and appraisal from several magazines and blogs, such as MTV Iggy, Culture Collide, Renowned for Sound, Record of the Day, Kings of A&R and many more. They have over 2 million streams on Spotify and over 1 million views on YouTube, still growing by the day.\r\n\r\nIn the beginning of 2013 the band recorded their first songs in a cabin out in the woods north of Stockholm. The songs immediately got them a record deal with the american label Digsin, which released Like Swimmings first single, \u201cGod Knows\u201d, in May the same year. The single premiered on the american arts and culture magazine Blackbook and got attention amongst various indie blogs in the US. The second single, \u201cGo Buffalo\u201d, was released in August 2013. It was recorded and produced by Lennart \u00d6stlund (ABBA, Ramones, Led Zeppelin, Cardigans, etc) and mixed by Brian Malouf (Michael Jackson, Brian Wilson, Queen, Pearl Jam, Madonna, etc).\r\n\r\n\u201cGo Buffalo\u201d created a buzz around the band in media. MTV Buzzworthy described it as \u201cour latest obsession\u201d, Rockmafia called it \u201cprobably the most upbeat, morbid song you\u2019ll hear all year\u201d and USA Today wrote: \u201cSwedish band Like Swimming crafts sweet and bouncy indie pop tunes that pair well with sprinklers and sunscreen.\u201d UK based music website Sound of Confusion wrote: \u201cSo, if you\u2019d be so kind, could you point people in the direction of \u2018Go Buffalo\u2019 and Like Swimming in general so they can hear how catchy, radio\u00adready, irresistible and the commercial music can be made in a way that doesn\u2019t rely on the same horrible tricks and the same songwriters and producers for every bloody artist.\u201d\r\n\r\nLike Swimming followed up the single with a USA tour in October, playing at the Culture Collide Festival in LA, the CMJ Music Week in NYC and a couple of other shows in Nashville and Chicago. The band also recorded a session on music blog Daytrotter. Daytrotter later rated the song \u201cLet Go\u201d one of the 50 best songs that year, 26 out of 4800 songs.\r\n\r\nIn late December 2013 Like Swimming entered the RMV Studio in Sweden, recordin more songs for 2014 together with the studio manager Linn Fijal, who has an extensive client list including The Hives, Kate Ryan and swedish singer songwriter Lars Winnerb\u00e4ck, swedish Jazz guru Nils Landgren and swedish indie pop princess Frida Hyv\u00f6nen. The collaboration with Brian Malouf from \u201cGo Buffalo\u201d is planned to continue on these recordings as well.\r\n\r\n2014 started with the mega festival SXSW and the release of their first EP, with brand new song Let Go as title track. During the summer, the band released a remix EP on Go Buffalo, with remixes from Marc Stout (from PaperCha$ers) and others. In early September, the trio released their debut full length album, STRUCTURES, which received great reviews and appraisal from many blogs and magazines in the UK and US. The Music Spot called it a \u201cbrilliant album by a promising new band\u201d and Culture Collide gave the album 82 out of 100, labeling the band as \u201cmust-hear Swedish indie pop\u201d. Love is Pop called it \u201ceasily one of the year\u2019s finest releases of any genre\u201d and MTV Iggy made the band \u201cArtist of the week\u201d. With their latest single A Room of Her Own climbing the streams on Spotify, Record of the Day wrote: \u201cPlay this song just once today and it\u2019ll be in your head for the rest of the week, we guarantee\u201d. It\u2019s, according to Subbacultcha, \u201cdelightfully upbeat, chirpy and extremely catchy and who doesn\u2019t like music like that?!\u201d\r\n\r\nIn October 2014 the band head over to USA to tour, starting at the CMJ Music Marathon then cover NYC, Philadelphia, Middeltown, New Orleans, Hattisburg, Nasville.\r\n\r\n2015 stated with releasing the video of A Room of Her Own. The band also wrote music for a TV-serie that going to air later 2015. The band has entered the studio to do acoustic versions of the album STRUCTURES as well as recording a full new album to be released 2015\/2016.\r\n\r\nhttp:\/\/likeswimmingmusic.com","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ca85bd05-89c1-475e-bb89-ba0f4d7d7187_media_06 Lean On.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/d28b677c-1de0-42f9-961c-f0ba191af13d_media_LS_Structures_ghost.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"THE MIGHTY STEF","musik":"Rock","place":"Dublin","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/ceb3ada3-c7d7-45a9-b802-7459847c21dd_media_Ceremony Mix 2.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/8777248d-ba02-4534-b41a-3766c26ef764_media_Screen shot 2015-07-22 at 12.29.25.png.jpg"},{"title":"Dead Man","musik":"Rock","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/86ecdcf9-c5c9-4e8a-8998-93cca56c548e_media_Dead Man - Purgatory (demo) 2 (1).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/64693f5e-9308-462e-9820-3b9b60bf55c4_media_DM.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Crash n Recovery","musik":"Country","place":"Forsed","text":"With their roots in the deep woods of northern Sweden, Crash n Recovery's original music has brought them wings. Nominated for Best European Act by British CMA Awards 2014 and winners of Sveriges Radio's Svensktoppen N\u00e4sta V\u00e4sternorrland. Their honest and heartwarming music has been played on radio all over the world and they've been featured on a local TV show in Nashville on several occasions. Three of their single's have done very well on the European Country Chart Top 40 with a peak at #10.\r\n                                                                                          \r\nCrash n Recovery create a perfect fusion of traditional\/alternative Country Music and contemporary Americana. To stay connected to their own roots, their Scandinavian heritage is also thrown into the mix through folk music, contributing to their signature sound.   \r\nCrash n Recovery's greatest strength, would be as a live act; giving their all on stage; sharing  joy, sorrow, passion and sweet melancholy with the audience. The band like to keep it raw n real, hence the use of live, acoustic instruments on stage; upright bass, banjo, acoustic guitars, fiddle, mandolin, accordion and drums (and an occasional pedal steel or dobro)... and they do all the writing, arranging, recording, producing and performing themselves. Since the band started out in 2012 they've been busy touring in Europe, playing mostly at festivals, sharing stages with artists such as Leann Rimes, Buffy Sainte Marie, Doug Seegers, The Kilkenny's, Tupelo, Bob Wayne, Ten Years After and many, many more. \r\n\r\nCrash n Recovery have released an EP called \"The Word\" and their debut album \"Post the storm\" in 2012 and in September this year they will be releasing their second album \"Deep in the woods\" in a collaboration with Rootsy.\r\n ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c404443b-fde9-4a41-9825-b691bf3a6506_media_TAKE ME BACK.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/567ea4e5-6b2d-4e39-a7b1-5d7afd5953fd_media_bandbild(1).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Happy Hippo Family","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"O\u0308rebrobandet som bildades pa\u030a O\u0308land 2008 har gjort sig ett namn pa\u030a den svenska och utla\u0308ndska livescenen under de senaste a\u030aren. Med turne\u0301 i japan, Europa och spelningar pa\u030a Sveriges sto\u0308rsta festivaler som Peace & Love och Bra\u030avalla sa\u030a har bandet byggt upp en stor resume\u0301 som tagit steget till de stora scenerna i Stockholm (Debaser) och Go\u0308teborg (Sticky Fingers). Efter att ha sla\u0308ppt sitt debutalbum 2011 i Sverige och Japan jobbar nu bandet pa\u030a sitt andra album som fo\u0308rva\u0308ntas komma ut under 2015. Bandet vann O\u0308rebros prestigefyllda musikpris \u201dMillencolin Music Prize\u201d fo\u0308r sina prestationer under 2013. Nu \u00e4r bandets nya album klart efter en lyckad Crowdfunding som gav bandet en budget p\u00e5 100 000kr. Bandet letar nu samarbetspartners kring release av albumet. Kontakta Martin p\u00e5 martin@jacquelinemusic.com eller 0708-543934 f\u00f6r mer info. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/5534b183-457e-4263-956d-a87ba3731abc_media_That's What She Said PREVIEW.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/45b66ded-92d4-4c8f-91aa-5de1b56d290f_media_THHF_press3print_Omne_fix.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Sarah Macdougall","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"Whitehorse","text":"Described by the magazine Rootstime in Belgium as \u2018One of the greatest talents of our era\u201d, and listed as the \u201c2nd best gig\u201d by the major UK newspaper The Independent, becoming the #1 most played artist on Canadian Galaxie Folk\/Roots radio, Western Canadian Music Award winning artist Sarah MacDougall is getting known for her honest and poetic songs, passionate performances, and unique voice. Born in Sweden, Swedish magazine N\u00f6jesguiden declared her \u201cOne of Sweden\u2019s best singer\/songwriters\u201d.\r\n \r\nSince the release of  award-winning The Greatest Ones Alive in 2011, Sarah has been touring Canada and Europe endlessly, taking time to work on songs and record between tours. Last winter, she hunkered down under the Northern Lights in Whitehorse and put the final touches on the sonically rich album which was to become Grand Canyon. The album, co-produced by Sarah and Caleb Stull (Field Study, Dominique Fricot, Language Arts), which was recorded in Toronto and Vancouver, features 8 songs and guest appearences from Erika Angell (Thus:Owls), Rose Cousins, Jesse Zubot (Tanya Tagaq, Dan Mangan), Peggy Lee, and Leah Abramson (Abramson Singers). Stepping outside of traditional folk and flirting with sounds reminiscent of The Postal Service or Kate Bush, Grand Canyon keeps the acoustic guitar but infuses the sound with heavier drums and richly textured strings and synths.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/cd6a70dd-7efc-4c60-99a5-6f9f5d70d42c_media_01 I Want To See The Light (lost from our eyes).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/c25f9bf8-d09e-483b-8ed6-d583462b0e96_media_2277d227-0aa1-483c-8820-9265f1c4a43d_media_Sarah Macdougall (1).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Burning Saviours","musik":"Hard rock","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/adb03eee-c031-40dd-8eb6-b94e51e41dd3_media_Burning_Saviours_-_I_Am_Lucifer.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/c8df1fb3-feb3-4397-858c-f400fd60c5ce_media_Burning S.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Soleil Camara","musik":"Reggae","place":"Malm\u00f6","text":"Soleil Camara, \u00e4ven k\u00e4nd som Rootz One, \u00e4r f\u00f6dd och uppvuxen i Malm\u00f6 och har nyligen sl\u00e4ppt l\u00e5ten \u201cJag G\u00f6r Det\u201d tillsammans med albumaktuella Antonio D. Han har \u00e4ven g\u00e4stat producenten Ishi\u2019s debut-mixtape \u201dSpring Pieces\u201d med l\u00e5tarna \u201dGet My Money\u201d och \u201dFind Home\u201d. F\u00f6r n\u00e4rvarande jobbar han p\u00e5 sin kommande EP.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/09d55644-160e-4fec-837b-ffb54cea6b07_media_Get-At-Me-2.0-Soleil-Camara-iSHi.mp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/7caba751-7287-46bb-8ffa-d609b4b0b077_media_Soleil Camara pic.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Bahia","musik":"Soul","place":"London","text":"Bahia \u00e4r f\u00f6dd och uppvuxen i Malm\u00f6 men blev f\u00f6r\u00e4lskad I London efter att ha bes\u00f6kt staden f\u00f6r ett par \u00e5r sedan d\u00e4r hon nu verkar och bor. Sedan Boomtown festivalen har Bahia gjort skapat sig ett namn i Englands Hiphop och Dub-scen. Hon har bl.a. supportat Elliphant p\u00e5 Nottinghill Karnevalen d\u00e4r de var f\u00f6rband \u00e5t Damian Marley. Bahia jobbar f\u00f6r tillf\u00e4llet p\u00e5 sin EP-debut. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/2303c810-336a-4eca-9d11-6c4f298ae391_media_01 Feel (feat. Bahia).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/f7f97d42-736e-4835-8c2d-fe68d1ba6e02_media_Bahia.png.jpg"},{"title":"Untitled","musik":"Indie Pop","place":"Malm\u00f6","text":"Musik-duon Untitled best\u00e5r av s\u00e5ngerskan Nellie och producenten Martin Ren\u00e9 som samarbetat med bl.a. ADL, Medina, Anton Ewald och Molly Sand\u00e9n, f\u00f6r att n\u00e4mna n\u00e5gra. Deras sound k\u00e4nnetecknas av en mix av indiepop med urban-influenser. Duon \u00e4r snart aktuella med debutsingeln \u201cYayo\u201d som sl\u00e4pps inom ett par veckor. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9969ad69-e1ab-474f-864c-96ab54396fa8_media_beep1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/594fb37f-c243-4ea4-88a4-38d7bdf241bf_media_untitled.png.jpg"},{"title":"Andon Davis","musik":"Americana","place":"Chicago","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/8de9303e-e4cd-44bc-8681-701196f12703_media_01 You Ask Me Why.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/dcaa9c88-7a94-4358-ad39-1d2eaa7cf751_media_AndonDavis.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Janne Saaristo","musik":"Americana","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"Janne Saaristo obetitlade debutalbum har planerad release i slutet av september i \u00e5r. \r\n\r\nJanne Saaristo har tidigare spelat bas i altcountrybandet Hanif, som p\u00e5 00-talet gav ut tv\u00e5 kritikerrosade album och en ep. Det andra, Oh Lord Jesus Christ Baby fr\u00e5n 2006, producerade Janne tillsammans med bandets s\u00e5ngare och l\u00e5tskrivare Andreas Magnusson. \r\n\r\nSedan Hanif splittrades har Janne varit den ena halvan av duon Escalator to Nowhere, som hittills hunnit ge ut tv\u00e5 ep, varav den senaste, One way ticket home kom ut i Januari i \u00e5r. \r\n\r\nJanne Saaristo kommer att producera skivan sj\u00e4lv, men kommer att ha hj\u00e4lp av en del andra musiker, bland andra Gunnar Frick p\u00e5 steel guitar (tidigare med bland andra Weeping Willows, Ray Davies och Stefan Andersson) och Andreas Purv\u00e9n (tidigare med Kingston Airforce) p\u00e5 trummor. ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9bda6070-202a-4469-9803-903e3ba60707_media_The entrance.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0f52f542-c4f4-458c-9ca3-aadfa55cbc8b_media_Janne_Saaristo.JPG.jpg"},{"title":"Jagne","musik":"Hiphop","place":"Malm\u00f6","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/6f6fcc5b-7cf2-4218-9fc7-5bd4ccc80aae_media_01 \u00c4rru Skraj (feat. Soleil Camara) [Original].m4a","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/9b825f39-afd1-469e-9eb5-2b10e526f393_media_jagnemannen.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"The Glorias","musik":"Electronic","place":"Boden","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/586c9823-2000-4b2a-8f9b-0a13a53a025b_media_teaser-ljud.mp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/f41dc67f-e967-4cb9-9d56-91c42c8669ed_media_Glorias.png.jpg"},{"title":"Captain Crow","musik":"Hard rock","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/9d3de8c7-3464-4bf2-bc1e-ff48838d3b64_media_Captain Crow-Silence_LiH.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/578f1549-f9e7-47dd-ab4b-7a1f4337bc05_media_Crow.png.jpg"},{"title":"Mhina","musik":"Soul","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/c91ffb0f-04f0-45fc-9ae8-847c8f8e20bb_media_06 Can't Get Enough (Prod. By K.J).mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/0a06ef0a-e3a8-41dc-860d-8698ab49a6f1_media_Mhina.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"12th Letter","musik":"Hiphop","place":"Toronto","text":"XIIth Letter \r\n\r\nIn numerology, the number twelve represents a completed cycle of learning experience, and is subsequently considered a perfect number. For XIIth Letter, his experience as a musician in the Toronto music industry has spanned over a decade, starting in a group called All-City in the early 2000s and coming full circle as a solo artist in 2015.\r\n\r\nFacing a series trials and tribulations that followed him throughout his career, XIIth has developed a philosophy that promotes sacrifice and self-confidence to guide him to his new album, 10,000 Hours. Based on author Malcolm Gladwell's book 'Outliers' and the concept that of honing any craft requires a dedicated 10,000 hours to achieve, XIIth has created a second musical career with a versatility to adapt, grow and repeat. \r\n\r\nBeing able to understand the poetics of a rhyme and the dynamics of a deliver are characteristic\u2019s XIIth embodies, allowing him to flourish in the music that he creates. With his witty punchlines, vivacious lyricism, and a salient flow, XIIth\u2019s dynamic sound encompasses elements from the Golem Era of hip hop, but also incorporates new school elements that transcend varying hip hop diasporas and audiences.\r\n\r\nOn XIIth journey to the new album, XIIth has enlisted fellow Toronto native and Grammy-nominated producer Arthur McArthur to head the project sonically. From an executive production standpoint, Arthur McArthur has aligned his creative perspectives with XIIth\u2019s musical philosophy to bring cohesion to 10,000 Hours, and illuminate the compelling stories that showcase XIIth journey to today.  ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/b1d5a794-8a90-4921-9ee6-171b0b6a1c1e_media_beep1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/a33059d1-9aa3-48a2-a975-eaf04bc23534_media_12th Letter.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Evon","musik":"Blues","place":"Kampala","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/5e0ec57d-1dfd-4f20-9890-4907ae4c846f_media_Evon.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/4435544d-5f10-4cb8-9edd-1608a4089f24_media_EvonRedwithoutLogo.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Gunnar Danielsson","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"G\u00f6teborg","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/95194c19-8a14-4441-ac3e-e0ca4b022d5c_media_beep1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/4d65207d-57f1-41c6-acc7-451dc9a7b6ac_media_GD.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Adora eye","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"G\u00e4vle\/Stockholm","text":"Adora Eye - something dark, something bright, something schrewd.\r\nAdora Eye is the singer\/songwriter and drummer Jimmy J\u00f6nsson\r\nfrom Sweden. As a drummer, he's been on several tours, supporting bands\r\nlike WovenHand, Depeche Mode and Sisters Of Mercy.\r\nNowadays he's fully committed to his guitar and vocals.\r\nAdora Eye just got back home after three weeks of touring in Asia.\r\nDuring 2015 a lot of new Adora Eye songs will be released as \"2-track-singles\",\r\nand early 2016 his first full-length album will see the light of day.\r\nThe styles of Adora Eye songs are singer\/songwriter\/folk\/americana\/murderballads.\r\nBob Dylan, Tom Waits and Jeff Buckley are artists that's been mentioned when people been talking about Adora Eye.\r\n\r\nhttp:\/\/www.facebook.com\/adoraeye\r\nhttp:\/\/www.soundcloud.com\/adoraeye\r\nhttp:\/\/www.youtube.com\/adoraeyemusic\r\nalso on Spotify, iTunes etc.","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/5bc41c1d-0ff7-4d47-a878-efc779687545_media_Black Sunday Bird.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/31ec82bc-cdd8-412e-9d75-922826337e45_media_Adora.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"MARKUS","musik":"Singer  songwriter","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"\u00d6rebrosonen Markus \u00e4r en artist som ber\u00f6r. \u00c4n s\u00e5 l\u00e4nge \u00e4r han en v\u00e4l bevarad hemlighet och han har valt sina framtr\u00e4dande med omsorg. \u00c4ntligen \u00e4r tiden inne f\u00f6r klivet ut i den stora v\u00e4rlden. P\u00e5 de spelningar han har gjort har publiken h\u00e5llt andan, hyschat \u00e5t den som tappat en sked eller harklat sig. Man vill uppfatta allt, suga in det som h\u00e4nder, vara helt n\u00e4rvarande. \r\n\r\nSom tidigare publik p\u00e5 hans spelningar s\u00e4ger: \"Det var nog \u00e4rligt talat den h\u00e4ftigaste konserten jag varit p\u00e5 sedan evigheter\", \"Jag har aldrig blivit s\u00e5 tagen av en singer-songwriter\", \"Han \u00e4r s\u00e5 sjukt bra, finns inget att till\u00e4gga\". ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/22c2dde3-53c1-4838-9f6b-ca8ed0a57846_media_beep1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/1bd16c3c-7333-4e8f-bb06-e1a01cf73550_media_10424337_1517546911825791_2906070957066128996_n (1).jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Full of Keys","musik":"Pop","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/09a73718-f9e9-4bdc-bbb6-ba98d9cd0d5c_media_beep1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/2fae5b0f-6f0c-4545-b532-a8e9b0947b1a_media_1504116_606475612760767_1891587151_n.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Petunia & the Vipers","musik":"Americana","place":"Vancouver","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/2f909963-9d5f-4532-a4a5-7fffdd63df7f_media_beep1.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/fe3512de-a6c4-4d23-a34c-f0ad3eee815e_media_PetuniaTheVipers5Piece.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"NINA","musik":"Pop","place":"London","text":"NINA is a German synth pop singer-songwriter based in London, UK. Born and raised in Berlin, she began singing at the age of six and she moved on to classical training during her teens. NINA cites Depeche Mode as one of her early musical influences.\r\n\r\nNINA released We Are The Wild Ones in 2013, garnering her great media attention. The track was used in SyFy\u2019s US TV Series Being Human (Season 4), which exposed her music to millions of viewers and the official music video for this track was premi\u00e8red by Huffington Post, who described her music as \u2018Lana Del Rey meets Robyn\u2019.\r\n\r\nNINA\u2019s latest single My Mistake released in 2014, was included in HUGO BOSS\u2019 20 Years Compilation, available on all HUGO BOSS stores worldwide. The track was also used by Peccadillo Films on their trailer for \u2018Boys on Film 9\u2019 as well as independent cult film \u2018Bruno & Earlene Go To Vegas\u2019.\r\n\r\nNINA\u2019s first UK Tour was announced after a successful show at Liverpool Sound City 2014, as well as a US Tour supporting ERASURE (The Violet Flame Tour) in September, where NINA performed 7 dates around the East Coast.\r\n\r\nNINA made a live appearance on US morning TV Show \u201c6 In The Mix\u201d \u2013 NBC6 (Florida) performing her latest single \u2018My Mistake\u2019. After receiving great reviews, NINA performed at the legendary CBGB\u2019s Festival in NYC in October 2014 as well as the Pyramid Club, and she performed an exclusive acoustic session for City Winery New York.\r\n\r\nAt the end of 2014 NINA performed several shows around Europe including supporting Monarchy and The Levity in London, and touring with DE\/VISION as their support act in Germany.\r\n\r\nIn April 2015 Mercedes Benz featured NINA's song 'My Mistake' on their European TV and radio advert, which also appeared on several stadiums around Europe. The track reached #6 in the UK Shazam advert charts.\r\n\r\nBookings:\r\nGERMANY: jan@pluswelt.agency\r\nUK: laura@aztecrecords.com\r\nITALY: info@onemorelab.it","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e16468e3-fd3b-480a-97e0-50043eb2c0e6_media_01 We Are The Wild Ones_01.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/61976ec2-72db-4580-8c46-f591cd49ac17_media_nina.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"ADNA","musik":"Pop","place":"Berlin","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/fe2a91c7-ceba-476b-a9b9-1b3b2d037fe3_media_01. Intro-Berlin.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/42c09863-9319-4921-81c1-ad703d406c53_media_Adna2.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Juha Mulari","musik":"Visa","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/e4336e85-f06f-40d0-a6f9-cb669e01af06_media_01 Himlen och gud.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/e2ef87c3-8a5c-45e0-8bac-63a8a4084737_media_juhamulari03s.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Daniel Karlsson trio","musik":"Jazz","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/71dac499-7087-42b0-b2c1-a66e2efa613b_media_01 Chilly Chili.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/070cb55f-17d7-41dc-8cd0-c88a44b6d68d_media_thumb_Daniel_Karlsson_Trio_25_foto_Per_Kristiansen.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Sopot","musik":"Pop","place":"Banja Luka","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/3f9ded0c-2cbb-4629-954d-e74af1e47dca_media_SOPOT - Energetsko more.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/b3278027-28c7-424a-a01a-2a92ccd68c6c_media_22Sopot.jpg.jpg"},{"title":"Shadowquest","musik":"Metal","place":"\u00d6rebro","text":"ShadowQuest is here. With members from bands like Stratovarius Masterplan, Saint Deamon, Sinergy, Dionysus and Shining. Our aim is simple yet powerful: ShadowQuest is here to bring metal back into the hearts of all people. To bring unity, meaning and hope to souls all over our universe. We bring power! ","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/fcdb9c32-97ae-4f4f-a0a0-8b7b26d66ca5_media_04_Live Again.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/e714de1e-31d1-4ad7-a59d-0267bc7a073d_media_sqlgogogold.png.jpg"},{"title":"Kolonien","musik":"Folk","place":"Stockholm","text":"","mp3":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/songs\/99a619cc-3ddb-4dfa-a888-144d1ba21213_media_Allting St\u00e5r Stilla Mp3.mp3","image":"http:\/\/martenolsson.se\/lah15\/images\/5b4a0c66-e6f2-4bec-aa73-3884b0bfc352_media_Kolonien.jpg.jpg"}]}